NK034(ngi)006:0: phra yig can rin po che rlung gi pra khrid
NK034(ngi)006:1: bzhugs so rgya gar skad du rat+na b+ha yu ti
NK034(ngi)006:2: y+aa k+aa bod skad du rin po che rlung gi
NK034(ngi)006:3: pra khrid dpal mi 'gyur ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal
NK034(ngi)006:4: lo dad dang ldan zhing brtson 'grus dang ldan pa
NK034(ngi)006:5: rtag tu theg pa mchog la rab tu dad mi
NK034(ngi)006:6: 'gyur stong pa'i 'bras bu 'dod pa rnams mchog tu
NK034(ngi)006:7: gsang ba'i thabs 'dir su 'jug pa des ni mchog
NK034(ngi)006:8: dang thun mong dngos grub thob stong pa nyid la
NK034(ngi)006:9: dbang bsgyur nges pa thob sngags dang phyag rgya rnams
NK034(ngi)006:10: ni ma bsgrubs 'grub des na 'di la rtag tu
NK034(ngi)006:11: goms par bya gcig dang rim gyis 'bras bu de
NK034(ngi)006:12: 'dod pa 'di ltar lus ngag gcun pa mchog yin
NK034(ngi)006:13: no sarba pa pam kye ma rigs kyi bu dad
NK034(ngi)006:14: pa mchog dang ldan pa rnams rig pa mngon sum
NK034(ngi)006:15: gyi don la 'jug pa'i phyir gsang sngags kyi thabs
NK034(ngi)006:16: 'di lta bu la bslab par bya'o dang po thabs
NK034(ngi)006:17: sna tshogs kyis bla ma mnyes par byas la gsang
NK034(ngi)006:18: ba'i man ngag rnams tshul dang mthun par zhus te
NK034(ngi)006:19: rang gi blo la longs par byas la de la
NK034(ngi)006:20: yang nas yang du sgro 'dogs bcad de de nas
NK034(ngi)006:21: chos pa dang rang rkyen ma yin pa'i yul rab
NK034(ngi)006:22: tu dben zhing nyams dga' bar grogs lta spyod mthun
NK034(ngi)006:23: pa dang sdebs te 'bras bu 'di ltar bsgom par
NK034(ngi)006:24: bya'o gnas khang yid dang mthun par lus kyi gnad
NK034(ngi)006:25: stan bde ba'i steng du rkang pa rdo rje skyil
NK034(ngi)006:26: mo krung du bca' ba dang lus drang por bsrang
NK034(ngi)006:27: ste lag pa mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:28: dang mjing pa yid tsam dgye bar bya ba ni
NK034(ngi)006:29: lus kyi 'dug stangs so de ltar lus la rlung
NK034(ngi)006:30: gi man ngag bzhi bsgom pa ni phyi'i thig le
NK034(ngi)006:31: la bslab pa zhes bya ba ste rtag tu rlung
NK034(ngi)006:32: la goms shing 'dris pas tha mal rlung la dbang
NK034(ngi)006:33: bsgyur ba ni rlung ni gang na gnas pa ni
NK034(ngi)006:34: de dang de na snang ba ste snang ba rnam
NK034(ngi)006:35: pa gsum dag gi rnal 'byor pa yis ye shes
NK034(ngi)006:36: bsgrims gal te rlung ni zad pa na snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:37: nyid ni zad par gyur ci ste snang ba ma
NK034(ngi)006:38: zad na gzugs can rnams ni grol mi srid des
NK034(ngi)006:39: na rlung la goms pa gces rlung ni zad cing
NK034(ngi)006:40: stong pa'i thabs thabs 'di nyid la goms par bya
NK034(ngi)006:41: zhes pa rlung log nas ye shes skye ba'i man
NK034(ngi)006:42: ngag ni de yang 'di ltar ngos bzung ste bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:43: par bya'o rlung gi dbyibs la bslab pa dang kha
NK034(ngi)006:44: dog la bslab pa dang grangs la bslab pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:45: 'gro 'ong la bslab pa dang rlung bum par gzhug
NK034(ngi)006:46: pa'i man ngag la bslab pa'o dbyibs la bslab pa
NK034(ngi)006:47: ni lus gong ltar byas la rang gi dpral ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:48: smin ma'i mtshams su rlung sems 'dres pa'i thig le
NK034(ngi)006:49: zlum po shin tu gsal ba zhig la shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:50: gtad de mig kyang der gtad la bsgom ste de
NK034(ngi)006:51: rlung phar la song ba'i tshe hril li li bar
NK034(ngi)006:52: snang la song bar bsgom ste de'i tshe lus kyang
NK034(ngi)006:53: phar song bar bsgom shes pa stong sang sang bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:54: tshur sdud pa'i tshe hril li li rang gi dpral
NK034(ngi)006:55: ba'i steng du grang sing sing 'dug par bsgom de'i
NK034(ngi)006:56: tshe rnal 'byor pa grang ba che na de tsha
NK034(ngi)006:57: sing sing bsgom tshad pa'i ro'i tshad pa che na
NK034(ngi)006:58: grang bar bsgom de la gnas pa'i tshe na rang
NK034(ngi)006:59: gi lus sems bde sang sang pa la stong pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:60: rgyas btab cing bsgom mo de lta bu la yang
NK034(ngi)006:61: nas yang du yin ring por bsgoms pas phyi'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:62: su lus yod pa mi tshor ba dang 'bu srin
NK034(ngi)006:63: la sogs pa'i srog chags mi 'byung ba dang snang
NK034(ngi)006:64: ba gzhan la yid mi 'jug pa'o nang gi rtags
NK034(ngi)006:65: su de nyid grang bar bsgoms na lus kyi tshad
NK034(ngi)006:66: pa zhi nad dang bral ba dang tsha bar bsgoms
NK034(ngi)006:67: na grang rlung dang khrag dang mkhris pa'i nad dang
NK034(ngi)006:68: snying rlung la sogs pa 'don no gsang ba'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:69: ni de nyid brtan pa'i tshad yin te thig le
NK034(ngi)006:70: phar song ba'i dus su lus kyang bar snang la
NK034(ngi)006:71: phar yer yer song bar mngon te lus dngos su
NK034(ngi)006:72: bar snang la 'phags pa dag kyang 'ong nges so
NK034(ngi)006:73: de gnas pa'i tshe tsha bar bsgoms na lus thams
NK034(ngi)006:74: cad tsha mer gyis 'gro ba 'ong ste lus la
NK034(ngi)006:75: gos mi dgos pa 'ong nges so grang bar bsgoms
NK034(ngi)006:76: na lus thams cad grang sing sing 'ong ste dngos
NK034(ngi)006:77: su 'dar yengs pa 'ong ngo de'i tshe rlung gar
NK034(ngi)006:78: gtad pa'i sar mi 'phro bar sdod pa rnams ni
NK034(ngi)006:79: brtan pa'i tshad yin no +thii rab tu gsang ngo
NK034(ngi)006:80: de lta bu la blo ma tshud na 'di lta
NK034(ngi)006:81: bu la bslab par bya'o kha dog la bslab pa
NK034(ngi)006:82: ni rang gi lus gong ltar byas pa'i mgrin pa'am
NK034(ngi)006:83: lte bar rlung gi rdo rje kha dog sngon po
NK034(ngi)006:84: nas tsam zhig bsgom ste de la shes pa gtad
NK034(ngi)006:85: la rlung phar song ba'i tshe de yang sngo rgyang
NK034(ngi)006:86: rgyang ring por song bar bsgom tshur lus kyi nang
NK034(ngi)006:87: du thim thim song bar bsgom ste de'i shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:88: bde phril phril ba la rang rtag tu bsgom pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:89: rtags gong gi rtags kyi steng du brtan pa'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:90: 'di lta bu 'byung ngo phar song ba'i tshe shes
NK034(ngi)006:91: pa nam mkha' la bya sgro rlung gis khyer ba
NK034(ngi)006:92: ltar phyo phyo sang sang ba snyam byed pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:93: tshur rngub pa'i tshe bdag gi lto'i nang na rdo
NK034(ngi)006:94: rje de yod pa snyam byed pa'am lto ba mi
NK034(ngi)006:95: bde ba 'ong ste bdag nyid kyis de'i tshe zas
NK034(ngi)006:96: kyi 'du shes chod cing zas dang bral ba yang
NK034(ngi)006:97: zhag du ma 'ong ste de las yun ring du
NK034(ngi)006:98: 'gro ba 'ong mi srid do de ltar byung tsam
NK034(ngi)006:99: na snang ba thams cad stong par bsgom mo rgya
NK034(ngi)006:100: rgya rgya las can gcig dang 'phrad par shog +thii
NK034(ngi)006:101: kha dog la bslab pa gcig ni 'di ltar bslab
NK034(ngi)006:102: par bya ste rtsa'i 'khor lo dang po la brten
NK034(ngi)006:103: pa dang gnyis pa dang gsum pa dang bzhi pa
NK034(ngi)006:104: la brten pa ste rtsa'i nang na rang bzhin gyi
NK034(ngi)006:105: yi ge gnas te de dag ni kha dog la
NK034(ngi)006:106: bslab pa dang de yang +aa li k+aa li'i tshogs
NK034(ngi)006:107: kyi kha dog rtsa dang mthun pa la shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:108: gtad de bsgom pa dang k+aa li la bslab pa
NK034(ngi)006:109: dang +aa li k+aa li'i yan lag rnams la dmigs
NK034(ngi)006:110: pa gtad de bsgom pa'o de dag gi yi ge
NK034(ngi)006:111: dang kha dog ni rtsa gnas rin po che'i 'khor
NK034(ngi)006:112: lor shes par bya'o yi ge de dag kyang phar
NK034(ngi)006:113: 'gro tshur 'ong la bslab pa dang mi 'gul ba
NK034(ngi)006:114: la shes pa gtad pa gnyis kyis de'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:115: go i ti rlung gi grangs la bslab pa ni
NK034(ngi)006:116: skyes bu na tshod dar la bab pa zhig la
NK034(ngi)006:117: lus la nad med pa lus ngag sos dal ba
NK034(ngi)006:118: rgas pa rnams ni sos dal gzhon pa rnams rlung
NK034(ngi)006:119: myur te grangs mang du rgyu de'i tshad ni rgan
NK034(ngi)006:120: gzhon bar dar la bab pa zhig la nyin zhag
NK034(ngi)006:121: gcig la rlung nyi khri dang drug brgya rgyu ste
NK034(ngi)006:122: de nyid kyi grangs la rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis
NK034(ngi)006:123: bslab par bya ste de nyid bsgom pa'i tshe lus
NK034(ngi)006:124: gnad gong ltar bcos pa'i steng du mjing pa phyir
NK034(ngi)006:125: mi dgye bar bya ste mig bar snang la har
NK034(ngi)006:126: por gtad kha yid tsam gdangs te yid gzhan du
NK034(ngi)006:127: ma 'gyur bar bya ste rnal 'byor pas phreng ba
NK034(ngi)006:128: lta bu la phar song phreng ba gcig bzhag tshur
NK034(ngi)006:129: log gcig bzhag pas nyin zhag rlung gi grangs bzung
NK034(ngi)006:130: ste shes pa de ga la gtad pas rnam rtog
NK034(ngi)006:131: gzhan du mi 'phro ba'i ting nge 'dzin skye ste
NK034(ngi)006:132: de la yun ring du bsgoms pas rlung rgyu ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:133: grangs je nyung je nyung 'gro ste de nas nyin
NK034(ngi)006:134: zhag gcig la khri tsho gcig las gzhan rgyu ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:135: 'gro 'ong chad pa'i tshe lus kyang shin tu yang
NK034(ngi)006:136: ba zhig 'ong ste de'i dus su phar song ba
NK034(ngi)006:137: la yang ring bar gtong tshur rngub pa yang rang
NK034(ngi)006:138: gi lto ba mer mer btang bas nyiin mtshan gang
NK034(ngi)006:139: rung re la rlung gi rgyu ba phyed dang bcu
NK034(ngi)006:140: gnyis bcu gnyis chad do de ltar yang nas yang
NK034(ngi)006:141: du bsgoms pas tha ma rlung gi 'gro 'ong chad
NK034(ngi)006:142: nas shes pa gar gtad sar sdod pa ni rlung
NK034(ngi)006:143: la 'byongs pa'i tshad yin te las kyi rlung zad
NK034(ngi)006:144: pas na rnam shes rtog pa zad de ltar rnam
NK034(ngi)006:145: rtog zad pas snang ba zad pa ste snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:146: zad pas rnam par rtog pa'i yul zad pas na
NK034(ngi)006:147: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes 'ba' zhig la
NK034(ngi)006:148: gnas pa'o de'i phyir na snang ba zad pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:149: sangs rgya ba dus mnyam pa'o zhes bstan pa'o de'i
NK034(ngi)006:150: dus na rnal 'byor ba de yang chu la bying
NK034(ngi)006:151: ba 'ong mi srid do skabs su bar snang la
NK034(ngi)006:152: 'gro ba dag kyang 'byung ngo de'i tshe gal te
NK034(ngi)006:153: rlung 'byongs nas shes pa yengs yengs su song na
NK034(ngi)006:154: skabs su rtsa gnyid log gtim pas gsal la mi
NK034(ngi)006:155: 'phro bar 'gro ste de la blo bzhag cing bsgoms
NK034(ngi)006:156: pas grol ba yin no i ti rgya rgya rgya
NK034(ngi)006:157: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo gdams
NK034(ngi)006:158: pa 'di'i sngon 'gro la rdo rje skyil krung rdzogs
NK034(ngi)006:159: sangs rgyas zhes pas lus skyil krung ngag gi yi
NK034(ngi)006:160: ge drug la sbyang bar bya yid shes bya gzhi
NK034(ngi)006:161: med du ngo sprod ngo bo rten med du ngo
NK034(ngi)006:162: sprod rang bzhin 'gyur med du ngo sprod lus lhug
NK034(ngi)006:163: pa ngag lhug yid lhug dus gsum du yi ge
NK034(ngi)006:164: a'i don dran par byas la rang lugs su bzhag
NK034(ngi)006:165: go spyi bo mgrin pa snying gar bcang rigs kyi
NK034(ngi)006:166: bu de gal te de la shes pa ma tshud
NK034(ngi)006:167: na 'di lta bu la yang bslab par bya'o rlung
NK034(ngi)006:168: gi 'gro 'ong la bslab pa ni rang gi snying
NK034(ngi)006:169: gi dkyil na yi ge a dmar po me'i rang
NK034(ngi)006:170: bzhin can cig yod de de la shes pa gtad
NK034(ngi)006:171: la bsgom ste rlung phar 'gro tshur 'ong byed pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:172: tshe ngag tu a +aa a +aa a +aa a
NK034(ngi)006:174: +aa a +aa a zhes yid kyis brjod de shes
NK034(ngi)006:175: pa a la gtad pas rang gi snying nang na
NK034(ngi)006:176: rang bzhin gyi rtsa ba'i yi ge a gnas pa
NK034(ngi)006:177: de las chu las chu lbur rdol ba'i tshul du
NK034(ngi)006:178: a re brjod pas a re thol thol byung ste
NK034(ngi)006:179: rlung phar song ba'i tshe bar snang la phar gcig
NK034(ngi)006:180: song gnyis song la nyi shu rtsa gcig rdzogs pa
NK034(ngi)006:181: dang rlung dar gcig bzung la a de rnams la
NK034(ngi)006:182: shes pa gtad la bsgom de yang tshur la gcig
NK034(ngi)006:183: byung gnyis byung ba la shes pa gtad cing bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:184: pas lus bde phril phril ba la shes pa yang
NK034(ngi)006:185: nas yang du bsgom mo de nas snying nang du
NK034(ngi)006:186: thim pa'i dus na yang a mang po rong nge
NK034(ngi)006:187: ba la shes pa gtad de dar gcig bsgom de
NK034(ngi)006:188: ltar khams kyis thub tshad du nyin mtshan du bsgoms
NK034(ngi)006:189: pas lus mi skye ba'i brdar nam mkha' la 'gro
NK034(ngi)006:190: ba snyam byed pa dang ngag mi skye ba'i brdar
NK034(ngi)006:191: gtam thams cad col thus su 'ong ba dang sems
NK034(ngi)006:192: mi skye ba'i brdar bsam pa'i rgyun 'gag pa 'ong
NK034(ngi)006:193: ste shes pa sna tshogs thams cad ni yang zhing
NK034(ngi)006:194: srab pa'o rtags gzhan ma ni gong dang mthun no
NK034(ngi)006:195: i ti rgya rgya rgya yang rigs kyi bu de
NK034(ngi)006:196: gal te shes pa de la ma tshud na 'di
NK034(ngi)006:197: lta bu la yang bslab par bya'o rlung bum par
NK034(ngi)006:198: gzhug pa'i man ngag ni gnyid kyi dus su sbyar
NK034(ngi)006:199: ba dang rnal 'byor pas nyin mtshan du bsgom pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:200: gnyid ni dus bzhi mnyam par sbyor ba bsam gtan
NK034(ngi)006:201: nyal ba'i 'khor lor blta'o nyin mtshan du bsgom pa
NK034(ngi)006:202: ni lus gong ltar bcos la rlung nang du bstims
NK034(ngi)006:203: la lto ba mer gyis gtang zhing shes pa rang
NK034(ngi)006:204: gi lte ba na rtsa gnas kyi yi ge ha
NK034(ngi)006:205: gnas te de la shes pa gtad cing bsgom mo
NK034(ngi)006:206: rang gi lto ba rlung gis sngo mer mer song
NK034(ngi)006:207: tsam na yang phar khad kyis song bar bsgom ste
NK034(ngi)006:208: bar snang la na bun yal ba ltar bun bun
NK034(ngi)006:209: song bar bsgoms pas shes pa yang yal yal bun
NK034(ngi)006:210: bun song bar bsgom mo de la yun ci ring
NK034(ngi)006:211: du bsgoms na shes pa bde stong du grol ba
NK034(ngi)006:212: dang lus duhkha las grol ba dang rig pa rnam
NK034(ngi)006:213: par rtog pa las grol ba gsum dus mnyam du
NK034(ngi)006:214: 'byung ngo rlung gi thig le bsgom pa ni zangs
NK034(ngi)006:215: yig can gyi rtsa ba na gsal lo i ti
NK034(ngi)006:216: gal te rlung bsgoms pa'i gang zag de bying rgod
NK034(ngi)006:217: dam sgom pa'i sel du gyur pa na bcos shing
NK034(ngi)006:218: brtan par bya ba'i thabs ni gal te bying na
NK034(ngi)006:219: ha ha'am phata phata ces drag po'i spyod pa rnams
NK034(ngi)006:220: so gal te rgod na rlung ci nas kyang nang
NK034(ngi)006:221: du bstim mo bying na lus kyi gnad du bcos
NK034(ngi)006:222: pa dang yan lag bskyod pa'o rgod na lus gnad
NK034(ngi)006:223: ni mgo phur ba dang khyim mun nang du 'dug
NK034(ngi)006:224: pa'o gal te spyi bor song na rnal 'byor pa
NK034(ngi)006:225: shes pa 'gyur ba dang smyo ba lta bu 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:226: ste de'i tshe lus la yang thor ba dang sha
NK034(ngi)006:227: la thig le dang skabs su sems 'thoms pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:228: mtshogs ma bu chung gi mtshogs ma ltar slob pa
NK034(ngi)006:229: dag 'byung ngo de la kha zas bu ram dang
NK034(ngi)006:230: dang 'o ma dang mi zhun dum re bsres la
NK034(ngi)006:231: bkol la btung sems bar snang du mda' gang du
NK034(ngi)006:232: gzung la mjing pa thur la dgug rlung yar la
NK034(ngi)006:233: brdar te phag pa'i skad lta bur nus tshad du
NK034(ngi)006:234: bshor drag par bya'o de nas yang gong ltar bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:235: mo de ltar byung re tshe de bzhin du bya'o
NK034(ngi)006:236: gal te rlung sha mthongs bar du shor srid na
NK034(ngi)006:237: lus skya sbobs sam nag sbobs sam dmar sbobs su
NK034(ngi)006:238: song ste lus la sems can 'gul ba snyam pa'am
NK034(ngi)006:239: thor chung mang po tsem tsem pa byung na kha
NK034(ngi)006:240: zas ni mu zi dul ma dang sbrang rtsi dum
NK034(ngi)006:241: re bsres la bza' lus gan rgyal du nyal te
NK034(ngi)006:242: rlung 'gram pa la brdar te phu phu zhes nus
NK034(ngi)006:243: tshad du byas pas de nyid las grol te de
NK034(ngi)006:244: nas yang gong ltar bsgom mo gal te rlung de
NK034(ngi)006:245: don snying la zhugs na ni lus 'dar skabs su
NK034(ngi)006:246: 'bog cing brgyal bar byed yang na lus rengs shing
NK034(ngi)006:247: yan lag tu mnye skol du mi rung mgo 'dar
NK034(ngi)006:248: mig dkar khrul khrul bar 'gro lag pa'i bya byed
NK034(ngi)006:249: mang kha skom smin ma'i tshags 'khrul rtsa rnams phyi
NK034(ngi)006:250: nang med par bkra lam gyis 'ong ste de la
NK034(ngi)006:251: kha zas bu ram dang sbrang rtsi dang rus pa
NK034(ngi)006:252: brdungs pa'i khu ba rnams rtag tu brten pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:253: sha yi ba ma'i khu ba dang lo mar gyi
NK034(ngi)006:254: khu ba yang dum re btang chang spang de'i tshe
NK034(ngi)006:255: rnal 'byor pa las su rung gre ba la brdar
NK034(ngi)006:256: te kha nas drangs te ig ig ces nus tshad
NK034(ngi)006:257: bgrangs pas grol lo phyis gtan 'ong mi srid do
NK034(ngi)006:258: de dag bsgom pa'i dus su shes pa myos shing
NK034(ngi)006:259: gnyid du song na lus kyi gnad gcer bur byas
NK034(ngi)006:260: la langs la yan lag bgrad de kha dang mig
NK034(ngi)006:261: gdangs te bsgom mo de dag ni gal te rlung
NK034(ngi)006:262: ma chun pa rnams kyi gdams pa'o i ti de'i
NK034(ngi)006:263: tshe rnal 'byor pa de la lus nad dang gdon
NK034(ngi)006:264: gyis 'byung ba dkrugs nas tshe'i 'du byed gyur nas
NK034(ngi)006:265: bar do 'byung ngam mi 'byung rlung gis dang phyi
NK034(ngi)006:266: rol gyi lus brtag pa ni de'i tshe rlung rab
NK034(ngi)006:267: tu rgod cing 'phro na yin rlung 'gyu ba skyen
NK034(ngi)006:268: na yin rlung de skabs su dal zhing skabs su
NK034(ngi)006:269: myur bar brtseg mar 'gyu na lus la 'byung ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:270: nad dam gdon zhugs pas de'i tshe lus kyi gnad
NK034(ngi)006:271: rnams su rlung gi mdangs yal lam ma yal brtag
NK034(ngi)006:272: pa ni snga dro nyi ma rtse shar la kha
NK034(ngi)006:273: shar phyogs su bltas la rang ngam gzhan la rtogs
NK034(ngi)006:274: kyang rung 'di ltar brtag go yang de'i tshe dbugs
NK034(ngi)006:275: yang yang rnam par rgod na zla ba drug na
NK034(ngi)006:276: 'gum par 'gyur ro de'i rtags su lus kyi 'gram
NK034(ngi)006:277: pa'i tshigs rnams yon por 'ong sna'i rtse mo la
NK034(ngi)006:278: rlung gi mdangs med na de'i rtags su sna sngon
NK034(ngi)006:279: pas yo bar 'ong ste de ni zhag bdun na
NK034(ngi)006:280: 'gum pa la the tshom med do mig la gsal
NK034(ngi)006:281: byed rlung gi mdangs yal ba'i rtags su mchi ma
NK034(ngi)006:282: mi thub pa ste de ni zhag lnga na 'gum
NK034(ngi)006:283: pa'o 'gram pa g.yas nas las rlung mgon po'i rgyu
NK034(ngi)006:284: byed chad pa ni 'gram pa'i sha rnams shong gi
NK034(ngi)006:285: 'gro ste de ni zhag gcig las mi 'atsho'o rna
NK034(ngi)006:286: ba'i drag po rlung gi sgra yal ba ni rna
NK034(ngi)006:287: ba leb leb por 'gro ste de ni rlung sum
NK034(ngi)006:288: stong rgyu ba'i bar las mi thub bo lce la
NK034(ngi)006:289: dran byed kyi rlung chad pa ni lce la thig
NK034(ngi)006:290: le nag po sngon med pa 'ong ste de ni
NK034(ngi)006:291: zhag gcig na nges par 'gum mo rngub pa'i rlung
NK034(ngi)006:292: ni stobs chad pa'i rtags ni so 'thams pa ste
NK034(ngi)006:293: de ni zhag drug na 'gum mo mi rtog pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:294: rlung rgyud la zha ba'i rtags ni rtse chung gi
NK034(ngi)006:295: phyi rol gyi rtsa nyid mi 'gyur te de ni
NK034(ngi)006:296: zla ba phyed na 'gum mo zhi gnas kyi rlung
NK034(ngi)006:297: bag la zha ba'i rtags ni brang gi lhen sna
NK034(ngi)006:298: zhom gyis 'gro ba ste de ni zhag bcu drug
NK034(ngi)006:299: las mi 'atsho'o 'byung ba'i grong khyer rgyun chad pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:300: rtags su sen mo'i bkrag shor te de ni nyi
NK034(ngi)006:301: ma drug na'o de ltar na 'chi ba'i rtags bcu
NK034(ngi)006:302: drug po phyi rtags te gzhan gyi lus la brtag
NK034(ngi)006:303: go de dag la bslu ba'i thabs bcu ston te
NK034(ngi)006:304: gal te rang ngam gzhan bsrungs kyang dbugs rgod pa
NK034(ngi)006:305: la ni 'gram pa'i steng du a dkar po bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:306: zhing rlung sems de la gtad do bsrungs pa'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:307: 'gram pa yo ba bsrangs so sna'i rtags byung ba
NK034(ngi)006:308: la sna'i rtse la h+aum dkar po bsgom ste rlung
NK034(ngi)006:309: sems der gtad pas bzlog go rtags de dag mngon
NK034(ngi)006:310: par bzlog pa'i thabs ni thams cad la'o mig gi
NK034(ngi)006:311: rtags phyung ba la ni mig gi steng du ha
NK034(ngi)006:312: dkar po bsgom pa'o 'gram pa'i rtags la ni as
NK034(ngi)006:313: bya'o rna ba'i rtags la phata kyis bya'o lce'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:314: la ni +aa li'i tshogs kyis bya'o so'i rtags la
NK034(ngi)006:315: ni k+aa li'i tshogs kyis bya'o rtsa ba'i rtags la
NK034(ngi)006:316: ni h+r+aihs bya'o brang gi rtags la ni +amo gyis
NK034(ngi)006:317: bya'o sen mo'i rtags la ni ka k+aa ki k+ai
NK034(ngi)006:318: la sogs pas bya'o de dag gi dus su ngag
NK034(ngi)006:319: tu yang yi ge de dag bzlas so bzlas pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:320: grangs ni nyi shu rtsa gcig shes pa de rlung
NK034(ngi)006:321: sems kyi thig le la gtad do sgom pa ni
NK034(ngi)006:322: rlung dang bsres la bsgom mo yi ge dang rlung
NK034(ngi)006:323: bsres pa'i man ngag gal che'o i ti 'di ni
NK034(ngi)006:324: rlung gi man ngag mchog tu gyur pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:325: rab tu zab bo 'di la rtag tu goms pa
NK034(ngi)006:326: ni mchog dang thun mong dang dngos grub thob 'bras
NK034(ngi)006:327: bu stong pa nyid kyang thob rlung gi pra khrid
NK034(ngi)006:328: ces bya ba thig le phyi ma bslab pa chags
NK034(ngi)006:329: bral gyi 'bras bu'o i ti las can gcig dang
NK034(ngi)006:330: 'phrad par shog ces gter nas gter du btsas pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:331: rdzogs so gsang ba yi ge ma ru'i yang tig
NK034(ngi)006:332: bzhugs so yang gab sbas du ma zer rgya gar
NK034(ngi)006:333: skad du sa b+he ka la sa ma y+yam s+ya
NK034(ngi)006:334: tu sa mi lam lam ti ka n+aa ma bod
NK034(ngi)006:335: skad du nyams len bsdus pa'i sna khrid yang gsang
NK034(ngi)006:336: sbas pa'i ti ka gsang ba yi ge dmar ru'i
NK034(ngi)006:337: yang tig bcom ldan 'das gab pa thams cad mngon
NK034(ngi)006:338: du 'byin la phyag 'tshal lo brgyud pa'i rtsa ba
NK034(ngi)006:339: shes rab kun gyi dngos rnam rtog bcings pa'i dri
NK034(ngi)006:340: ma 'joms mdzad rje sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:341: rgyud 'chang ba rim brgyud dam pa sangs rgyas rnams
NK034(ngi)006:342: las kyang rtsa ba'i bla ma nges don skal bzang
NK034(ngi)006:343: ba dam pa dri med ye shes mdo sogs la
NK034(ngi)006:344: bdag gis lus sogs rab tu shugs phyung nas sbyang
NK034(ngi)006:345: dka' 'khor ba'i bag chags sbyang ba'i phyir lus ngag
NK034(ngi)006:346: yid kyi rab tu gus byas la nges don bla
NK034(ngi)006:347: ma brgyud pa rnams la yang bdag gi spyi bos
NK034(ngi)006:348: rab tu btud nas ni gsang ba'i yang bsdus nges
NK034(ngi)006:349: pa'i tshad dbab phyir bka' brgyud dag pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:350: gal che la dad pas 'jug pa'i skal ldan nges
NK034(ngi)006:351: lung can 'jug sgo gsal zhing rig pa'i tshad 'dzin
NK034(ngi)006:352: pa'i lung dang ldan pa'i skyes bu de kun gyi
NK034(ngi)006:353: blo yi the tshom rab tu bsal ba'i phyir nges
NK034(ngi)006:354: pa'i snying po gnad kyi man ngag rnams mun pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:355: nang du sgron me snang ba ltar bdag gis 'di
NK034(ngi)006:356: nyid du ni gsal bar 'bri snod mchog ldan pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:357: skal ldan sems kyi bu dad pa yangs shing snying
NK034(ngi)006:358: stobs brtson 'grus can shes rab ldan zhing 'phags pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:359: nor gyis phyug bla ma mchod cing 'jig rten chags
NK034(ngi)006:360: pa chung 'di ni skal ldan snying gi bu yin
NK034(ngi)006:361: pas 'di ltar 'byung ba'i gang zag gcig dang gnyis
NK034(ngi)006:362: gsum las mang na mkha' 'gro'i chad pa 'byung de
NK034(ngi)006:363: yi phyir na gsang ba'i man ngag 'di rnal 'byor
NK034(ngi)006:364: ldan pas sems la gnas par bya 'jig rten bskal
NK034(ngi)006:365: pa 'jig pa'i dus byung yang snying po byang chub
NK034(ngi)006:366: bar du khar mi dbyung rang gi sems la gnas
NK034(ngi)006:367: pa'i rgyas btab la 'di nyid bab col gang dgar
NK034(ngi)006:368: brjod pa med 'di ltar brnags pa'i sems la 'phur
NK034(ngi)006:369: ba yis nam zhig skal ldan sems kyi bu dang
NK034(ngi)006:370: 'phrad de la 'di byin snying la rgyas thob cig
NK034(ngi)006:371: 'di 'dra'i gdams pa bla ma'i khong gi snying bdag
NK034(ngi)006:372: gis bstan pa rig pa'i gnad du yang nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:373: len pa rnams kyis bcud 'di bkod de yi phyir
NK034(ngi)006:374: na nyams su len pa rnams yi ge 'di la
NK034(ngi)006:375: rtag tu 'dris par gyis 'di la 'dris nas rin
NK034(ngi)006:376: chen gter du sbos rigs min 'chol ba'i ngag zag
NK034(ngi)006:377: snod min la 'di nyid sus bstan dmyal khams me
NK034(ngi)006:378: yis tshig gdod nas ma thob nyes med mchog tu
NK034(ngi)006:379: dge des na rang gi rang la rgyas btab la
NK034(ngi)006:380: rang gi snying dang phung po 'bral med bzhin 'bral
NK034(ngi)006:381: ba'i skabs med bzod med sems kyis ni gsang ba
NK034(ngi)006:382: mchog gi yi ge 'di chongs shig &a&a&a'adira gsang ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:383: yi ge dmar ru'i don nyams su len par 'dod
NK034(ngi)006:384: pa'i skal ldan gnyis nas gsum gyis 'di ltar bslab
NK034(ngi)006:385: par bya'o skal ba dang ldan pa'i rigs kyi bus
NK034(ngi)006:386: bla ma la 'jig rten gyi bdog pa dang rang
NK034(ngi)006:387: gi lus kyis mnyes par byas la gdams pa 'di
NK034(ngi)006:388: zhu ba'i tshe gser gyi man+dala bla ma la dbul
NK034(ngi)006:389: bar bya ste mkha' 'gro rnams kyang tshogs dang gtor
NK034(ngi)006:390: mas mnyes par byas la gdams pa 'di zhu bar
NK034(ngi)006:391: bya'o bla mas gdams pa 'di kun bur bstan te
NK034(ngi)006:392: dpon slob rnams dus gcig la sangs rgya bar byed
NK034(ngi)006:393: pa'o dang po nyams su len pa'i skal ldan dpon
NK034(ngi)006:394: slob gsum nas bzhi po des lus ngag gi bya
NK034(ngi)006:395: ba gtang ba ni rab tu gces so de nas
NK034(ngi)006:396: dur khrod du slob ma de rnams khrid la zhag
NK034(ngi)006:397: gsum bzhi nas bcu tshun chad du lus ngag gi
NK034(ngi)006:398: bya ba ci yang mi byed par rab tu dal
NK034(ngi)006:399: bar gnas pa gal che de nas bla mas slob
NK034(ngi)006:400: ma la sngon du lus ngag gi zhen pa rnams
NK034(ngi)006:401: bzlog par bya ba'i phyir sngon du 'gro ba'i lam
NK034(ngi)006:402: rnams bslab par bya'o de yang de spros pa la
NK034(ngi)006:403: dga' na 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra la slob tu gzhug
NK034(ngi)006:404: spros pa la mi dga' na 'khor 'das ru shan
NK034(ngi)006:405: 'byed pa'i man ngag la bslab par bya ste de
NK034(ngi)006:406: yang lus kyi spyod pa'i man ngag bstan pa dpon
NK034(ngi)006:407: slob de kun dur khrod re rer nyams su len
NK034(ngi)006:408: par bya ste dros skad re re tsam mam nyi
NK034(ngi)006:409: ma phyed skad pa'i dur khrod re rer song la
NK034(ngi)006:410: bar chod zhi bar bya ba'i phyir mkha' 'gro ma
NK034(ngi)006:411: la tshogs dang gtor ma dang dge 'dun la ston
NK034(ngi)006:412: mo dang bla ma la yon 'bul zhing rten gyis
NK034(ngi)006:413: bdog pa thams cad 'khor gsum yongs su dag par
NK034(ngi)006:414: gtang bar bya'o de nas dur khrod re rer lus
NK034(ngi)006:415: kyi zhen pa bzlog nas 'khor ba'i lus gnyis ru
NK034(ngi)006:416: shan phye nas da 'khor ba'i lus la mi 'jug
NK034(ngi)006:417: par bya ba'i phyir lus kyi spyod pa rnams bla
NK034(ngi)006:418: ma'i gdams pa ji ltar gsungs pa bzhin bya'o de
NK034(ngi)006:419: nas zhag bzhi lnga nas bcu tshun chad du bla
NK034(ngi)006:420: ma dang slob ma gnyis ri'i rtse mo'am tshal legs
NK034(ngi)006:421: pa gcig tu 'phrad de bla mas bu khyod kyi
NK034(ngi)006:422: zhen pa log gam zhes nyams ci skyes pa dri
NK034(ngi)006:423: bar bya'o de nas slob ma des rang gi sems
NK034(ngi)006:424: la ji ltar byung ba'i nyams rnams bla ma la
NK034(ngi)006:425: bshad par bya'o de nas lus kyi zhen pa log
NK034(ngi)006:426: pa'i rtags su lus la chags pa med pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:427: lus med pa snyam pa dang grang ba med pa
NK034(ngi)006:428: dang tsha ba med pa dang bkres pa med pa
NK034(ngi)006:429: dang skom pa med pa dang na tsha med par
NK034(ngi)006:430: 'byung ste de'i bar du de lta bu'i nyams skyes
NK034(ngi)006:431: nas 'dug na lus rnal du 'bebs pa zhes bya
NK034(ngi)006:432: ste sor chud pa'i don du yang dur khrod der
NK034(ngi)006:433: gtang ste lus dal bar zhag bcu nas zla ba
NK034(ngi)006:434: phyed du 'dug tu gzhug go gong gi nyams rtogs
NK034(ngi)006:435: med na yang dal bar zhag 'ga' 'dug tu bcug
NK034(ngi)006:436: la yang lus kyi spyod pa rnams bya'o de yang
NK034(ngi)006:437: bla ma la dris te rtags dang mi ldan na
NK034(ngi)006:438: bskyar bar bya'o de ltar gal te ma byung na
NK034(ngi)006:439: lan gsum na lus kyi rtags de mi 'byung mi
NK034(ngi)006:440: srid do de nas lus sor bcug rnal du dbab
NK034(ngi)006:441: pa'i cho ga bya'o rnal du phebs pa'i rtags su
NK034(ngi)006:442: 'jig rten gyi bya ba la gtan nas blo skye
NK034(ngi)006:443: mi srid do de ltar lus kyi spyod pa mthar
NK034(ngi)006:444: phyin cing lus rnal du phab pas rnal 'byor pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:445: lus kyi bar chod nye bar zhi zhing phyi lus
NK034(ngi)006:446: kyi zhen pa log nas lus mi srid pa'i dgos
NK034(ngi)006:447: pa bstan pa'o de ltar gtan la phab nas yang
NK034(ngi)006:448: slob ma de la ngag gi zhen pa bzlog pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:449: phyir ngag 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:450: la bslab par bya'o ngag gi gdams pa ji lta
NK034(ngi)006:451: ba bzhin du 'di ltar bslab par gyis shig ces
NK034(ngi)006:452: bslabs te dur khrod du btang la yang gong bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:453: nyams lta'o lan gcig la byung na dbang po rab
NK034(ngi)006:454: kyi yang rab yin no ma byung na yang lan
NK034(ngi)006:455: gsum tshun la mi yong mi srid do de ltar
NK034(ngi)006:456: yang dag gi ltas ni bla ma'i man ngag gi
NK034(ngi)006:457: go ba ji lta ba bzhin du rgyud la skye
NK034(ngi)006:458: ste kha nas kyang tshig tu 'byung ba yin no
NK034(ngi)006:459: ched du byas pa med par rang shugs su 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:460: ba yin no de ltar byung nas ngag sor chud
NK034(ngi)006:461: cing rnal 'bebs thabs zhag bcu nas zla ba phyed
NK034(ngi)006:462: tshun chad du ngag shin tu dal bar gnas par
NK034(ngi)006:463: bya'o rnal du phebs pa'i rtags ni gtam rnams thams
NK034(ngi)006:464: cad du smra snying mi 'dod pa ste 'di ltar
NK034(ngi)006:465: ngag gi spyod pa mthar phyin pas ngag la bar
NK034(ngi)006:466: chod mi 'jug cing ngag gi bar chod nye bar
NK034(ngi)006:467: zhi nas ngag gi zhen pa log ste ngag 'khor
NK034(ngi)006:468: ba dang ru shan phye nas phyis 'khor ba'i ngag
NK034(ngi)006:469: tu 'jug mi srid pa'i dgos pa yod pa'i phyir
NK034(ngi)006:470: ro ngag gi spyod pa la rtags thon nas mthar
NK034(ngi)006:471: phyin pa rab tu gal che'o de ltar ngag gi
NK034(ngi)006:472: spyod pa rdzogs nas yid kyis spyod pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:473: la bslab ste yang dur khrod du gtang ngo de
NK034(ngi)006:474: nas yang gong ltar bla ma la dris shing sbyang
NK034(ngi)006:475: bas de yang lan gsum la mi 'byung mi srid
NK034(ngi)006:476: do de'i rtags su sems gsal ba dang yang ba
NK034(ngi)006:477: dang 'khrul pa'i snang ba yid la 'byung mi srid
NK034(ngi)006:478: pa dang brod pa chen po skyed pa dang nyams
NK034(ngi)006:479: bde ba 'byung ste de ltar byung tsa na yang
NK034(ngi)006:480: yid sor chud par bya zhing rnal du phabs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:481: thabs zhag bcu nas zla ba phyed du yid dal
NK034(ngi)006:482: bar gnas par bya'o rnal du phebs pa'i rtags su
NK034(ngi)006:483: 'khor ba las yid 'byung ba dang gzhan gang la
NK034(ngi)006:484: yang yid mi 'jug pa dang rang bzhin gyis dal
NK034(ngi)006:485: ba skye'o de ltar byung tsa na yid kyi spyod
NK034(ngi)006:486: pa mthar phyin pas yid la bar chad thams cad
NK034(ngi)006:487: nye bar zhi zhing yid 'khor ba ru shan phyed
NK034(ngi)006:488: nas 'khor ba la gtan 'jug mi srid do de'i
NK034(ngi)006:489: phyir na yid kyi spyod pa rdzogs par bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:490: gces so de ltar lus ngag yid kyi spyod pa
NK034(ngi)006:491: sngon du bstan pa ni thog ma nas lus ngag
NK034(ngi)006:492: yid dang bral ma myong bas da lus ngag gi
NK034(ngi)006:493: rnam pa dang dbral ba'i phyir de'i sngon zhen pa
NK034(ngi)006:494: bzlog pa'i phyir spyod pa 'di dag la bslabs pas
NK034(ngi)006:495: lus kyi 'byung ba rang sar dengs ngag gi zhen
NK034(ngi)006:496: pa rang log sems kyi byung tshor rang 'gags nas
NK034(ngi)006:497: zag med du sangs rgya ba'i gnad du bstan pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:498: sngon du 'gro ba lus ngag yid kyi spyod pa
NK034(ngi)006:499: bstan pa'i yang 'byed sbas pa'i ti ka rdzogs so
NK034(ngi)006:500: rgya rgya rgya &&& bya bral rang bzhin ngang la
NK034(ngi)006:501: phyag 'tshal lo 'dir lus ngag gnad gsang ba'i man
NK034(ngi)006:502: ngag bstan par bya'o de ltar sngon du 'gro ba
NK034(ngi)006:503: lus ngag gi spyod pa 'byongs pa'i tshad la phab
NK034(ngi)006:504: nas da ni lus la rig pa gnas pas rnal
NK034(ngi)006:505: 'byor pa rnams lus kyi 'dug stangs kyi man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:506: gab pa rnams mngon du phyungs te bstan pa'o de
NK034(ngi)006:507: yang glang po che 'dug stangs kyis gzhi bca' ba
NK034(ngi)006:508: gces 'dug stangs 'di la gzhi ma bcas na lus
NK034(ngi)006:509: ngag rnal du mi phebs pas 'di la gzhi bca'
NK034(ngi)006:510: ba rab tu gces so drang srong gi 'dug stangs
NK034(ngi)006:511: kyis gnad ma gzir na lus mi chun pas drang
NK034(ngi)006:512: srong gi 'dug stangs la shes pa gzir ba gces
NK034(ngi)006:513: seng ge'i 'dug stangs la rtsal ma sbyangs na ni
NK034(ngi)006:514: rig pa mi chun pas seng ge'i 'dug stangs kyis
NK034(ngi)006:515: khyad par du mig gcun pa rab tu gces so
NK034(ngi)006:516: de kun la skyo na 'dug stangs de ma yin
NK034(ngi)006:517: pa rnams la yang lus sbyang bar bya'o de kun
NK034(ngi)006:518: gyis lus ma sbyangs na ye shes mngon du snang
NK034(ngi)006:519: bar mi nus te dper na sbrul la rkang lag
NK034(ngi)006:520: rdzogs shing mang bar yod pa yin yang lus ma
NK034(ngi)006:521: gcun gyi bar la mi gsal ba dang 'dra bar
NK034(ngi)006:522: lus la ye shes chen pos gang zhing rgyas nas
NK034(ngi)006:523: yod kyang lus kyi gnad ma gcun na yul la
NK034(ngi)006:524: snang mi nus so de'i phyir na sngon du 'gro
NK034(ngi)006:525: ba lus kyi 'dug stangs 'di rnams dang zhag du
NK034(ngi)006:526: mar sems sbyang zhing lus gcun pa ni rab tu
NK034(ngi)006:527: gces so de nas dus tshod cig nas lus la
NK034(ngi)006:528: nad med par 'agro'o gnas pa lus kyi gnad yig
NK034(ngi)006:529: yang tig gsang ba rdzogs so +thii &&& bde chen
NK034(ngi)006:530: mngon du 'byin pa nyid la phyag 'tshal lo da
NK034(ngi)006:531: ni nyams su blang ba dngos gzhi'i gdams pa yang
NK034(ngi)006:532: gsang gab pa'i ti ka gnad yig chen po bstan
NK034(ngi)006:533: par bya'o 'dir ni man ngag rim 'jug phyir las
NK034(ngi)006:534: can skyes bu gang zhig gis 'di ltar nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:535: len pa la 'di ni rnal 'byor skal ba bzang
NK034(ngi)006:536: skal bzang byang chub sems chen po 'di ni mi
NK034(ngi)006:537: rtog mya ngan 'das 'di nyid brtson par sus byas
NK034(ngi)006:538: pa rig pa lu gu rgyud nyid la rnam par
NK034(ngi)006:539: gnas pa kho na'o dbyings la brtan par bya ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:540: phyir snang ba kun la rang gzer gdab rig pa
NK034(ngi)006:541: brtan par bya ba'i phyir ngo bo nyid ni rnal
NK034(ngi)006:542: du dbab lta ba brtan par bya ba'i phyir rtag
NK034(ngi)006:543: tu lu gu rgyud la gzir shes pa brtan par
NK034(ngi)006:544: bya ba'i phyir rig pa dbyings su brtson du bzung
NK034(ngi)006:545: lus ni brtan par bya ba'i phyir 'dug stangs rnams
NK034(ngi)006:546: la rang lus sbyang ngag ni brtan par bya ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:547: phyir rtag tu lkugs pa lta bur gnas sems ni
NK034(ngi)006:548: brtan par bya ba'i phyir rtag tu lu gu rgyud
NK034(ngi)006:549: la blta snang ba 'khrul pa rgyun gcad phyir stong
NK034(ngi)006:550: pa nyid la goms par bya 'di ltar nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:551: len pa'i mi sangs rgyas rnams dang nye ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:552: de phyir 'di la goms par bya'o 'di ltar nyams
NK034(ngi)006:553: su len pa dngos ni las dang po pa'i gang
NK034(ngi)006:554: zag gis rkyen 'dzom dgos te rkyen ma 'dzom na
NK034(ngi)006:555: rig pa'i dwangs mi phyed pas thog mar rkyen gal
NK034(ngi)006:556: che bas rkyen gzung ba ni yul nam mkha' stong
NK034(ngi)006:557: pa ste nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba rab tu
NK034(ngi)006:558: gces pa'o sprin dang khu rlangs kyis bsgribs na rig
NK034(ngi)006:559: pa'i bkrag mi thon pas rkyen dag pa gal che
NK034(ngi)006:560: nam mkha' stong pa la rig pa snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:561: pas 'di ni yul stong ba la ngo bo stong
NK034(ngi)006:562: pa nyid rang dag cir yang gnas pa zhes bya'o
NK034(ngi)006:563: 'di ni thog ma nas stong pa nyid kyi snang
NK034(ngi)006:564: ba stong pa nyid du grol ba zhes bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:565: yul stong pa rig pa gsal bar shar bas gsal
NK034(ngi)006:566: stong dbyer med snang ba rang dag pa zung 'jug
NK034(ngi)006:567: gi dgongs pa zhes bya'o rig pa rdo rje lu
NK034(ngi)006:568: gu rgyud ni gsal ba rang shes kyi rgyal po
NK034(ngi)006:569: zhes bya bar ye thog ma nas bzhugs pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:570: te sangs rgyas pa'i snang ba dang dbyer mi phyed
NK034(ngi)006:571: pas bzhugs tshul la khyad med de snang tshul la
NK034(ngi)006:572: rgyun gyi khyad par gyis phye'o 'di ni dbang po'i
NK034(ngi)006:573: mngon sum du rig pa zang thal ba zhes bya
NK034(ngi)006:574: ste rig pa nyid du nyams su myong du yod
NK034(ngi)006:575: pa'o 'di nyams su ma myong na yid dpyod du
NK034(ngi)006:576: 'dzin pa'i lta ba rnams dang khyad cung zad kyang
NK034(ngi)006:577: med de shes rab kyi spyod yul du ni ma
NK034(ngi)006:578: yin no shes rab kyis ni yang dag par brtags
NK034(ngi)006:579: na phung po'i gting mi rnyed de rig pa ni
NK034(ngi)006:580: smos ci dgos rig pa ni dbang pos gtan la
NK034(ngi)006:581: ma phab na shes rab kyis gtan la phab kyang
NK034(ngi)006:582: yid dpyod kyi lta ba rnams dang khyad par ci
NK034(ngi)006:583: yang med pa'i phyir na shes rab kyis ni ma
NK034(ngi)006:584: yin no 'di nyid du ni phung po rnams dang
NK034(ngi)006:585: dbang po rnams dang khams rnams zad par ma byas
NK034(ngi)006:586: na sangs mi rgya bas 'di dag la zad par
NK034(ngi)006:587: bya rgyu logs na gcig kyang yod pa ma yin
NK034(ngi)006:588: no de'i phyir na 'di shes rab kyis zad par
NK034(ngi)006:589: bya bar nus pa ma yin pas /
NK034(ngi)006:590: dbang po dang rig pa ma 'brel na zad par
NK034(ngi)006:591: mi nus te dbang pos bltar yod pas de kun
NK034(ngi)006:592: zad par nus pa yin no des na 'di ni
NK034(ngi)006:593: shin tu zab pas na da lta nyid du gtan
NK034(ngi)006:594: la dbab tu yod pa'o 'di ltar gtan la phab
NK034(ngi)006:595: nas nyams su blangs pas rtags ni 'dod pa med
NK034(ngi)006:596: kyang rang bzhin du 'byung nges so 'di'i dus su
NK034(ngi)006:597: gnad du mi 'gul bar rnam pa gsum mchog tu
NK034(ngi)006:598: gces so lus ma 'gul bas mig rang sor gtan
NK034(ngi)006:599: la phebs mig ma 'gul bas rig pa nyid dang
NK034(ngi)006:600: 'bral ba med par gtan la phebs rig pa ma
NK034(ngi)006:601: 'gul bas snang ba dang gzer thebs te mi 'gul
NK034(ngi)006:602: ba'o 'di ltar ma 'gul ba gsum du bsdad pas
NK034(ngi)006:603: dmigs pa thams cad rang sar dag nas snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:604: rgya yis thebs 'khrul pa rang sar log ye shes
NK034(ngi)006:605: ma bu 'phrad pa'i nyams zhes bya ba yin no
NK034(ngi)006:606: 'di dag ni rig pa mthong ba'i gnad yig yang
NK034(ngi)006:607: dag pa'o lu gu rgyud rlung dang bral nas thig
NK034(ngi)006:608: le rnams smin pa'i tshe snang ba dum bu'i rnal
NK034(ngi)006:609: 'byor pa zhes bya ste thig le dang thig phran
NK034(ngi)006:610: du 'char bas 'di ni dum bu la goms pa
NK034(ngi)006:611: zhes bya'o 'di ltar brtan pa thob nas rig pa
NK034(ngi)006:612: rang ngo'i snang ba zab cing rgya che ba la
NK034(ngi)006:613: dpyad par bya ste dbyings kyi snang ba la goms
NK034(ngi)006:614: par bya'o des ni nyams gong nas gong du 'phel
NK034(ngi)006:615: bar bya zhing shes pa rang thog tu blta bar
NK034(ngi)006:616: bya ba'i man ngag bstan pa yin de yang gong
NK034(ngi)006:617: du mig gi de bzhin nyid shes pas chos thams
NK034(ngi)006:618: cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa shes par bya ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:619: don gyi skabs su mig ma bde na bcos pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:620: man ngag gis ji ltar bde ba'i lus kyi gnad
NK034(ngi)006:621: kyis bcos par bya'o thig le sran ma tsam du
NK034(ngi)006:622: shar ba dang 'od re lde'i rnam pa tsam du
NK034(ngi)006:623: snang ba'i tshe na tshad du phyin pa yin snyam
NK034(ngi)006:624: nas nyams len dang bral na 'di'i snang ba logs
NK034(ngi)006:625: nas bar ma do gnyis pa'i brtan pa yin te
NK034(ngi)006:626: der shes pa gal te ma tshud na rang bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:627: sprul pa las mi mthong bas 'di la bar ma
NK034(ngi)006:628: chad pa rab tu gces po de ltar nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:629: blangs pa las lus kyi rtags 'ga' 'byung ba la
NK034(ngi)006:630: rlom pa byas la gzhag par bya ba ma yin
NK034(ngi)006:631: no 'di yang snang ba ldog pas rtag tu nyams
NK034(ngi)006:632: su blangs pa gces so de ltar lus kyi rtags
NK034(ngi)006:633: byung ba'i dus su 'phang dur khrod gcig nas 'ongs
NK034(ngi)006:634: te tha ma la 'bul zhing rdzas yod pa rnams
NK034(ngi)006:635: kyang bla ma la dbul bar bya'o bla mas nyams
NK034(ngi)006:636: dris te yang de nyid la 'dris su gzhug ste
NK034(ngi)006:637: de ltar bla mas ni gdams ngag dus gcig la
NK034(ngi)006:638: ma yin te rim gyis slob ma'i shes pa'i nyams
NK034(ngi)006:639: dang sbyar zhing gdab par bya'o de ltar dur khrod
NK034(ngi)006:640: so sor bzung nas skabs su nyams bsdur zhing nyams
NK034(ngi)006:641: su blangs pas slob ma dang gu ru bcas pa
NK034(ngi)006:642: rnams dus gcig la sangs rgya'o //
NK034(ngi)006:643: yang 'od ni yul gru'i rnam pa tsam thig le
NK034(ngi)006:644: ni 'khar phor kha sbub pa tsam lus la yang
NK034(ngi)006:645: rtags su gnyer ma med cing zas dang gos kyi
NK034(ngi)006:646: 'du shes bral ba'i tshe lus gcer bur phyungs te
NK034(ngi)006:647: gangs sam rgya mtsho'i 'gram du nyams su blangs shing
NK034(ngi)006:648: yang rtags phra mo de kun la rlom pa mi
NK034(ngi)006:649: bya bar gong ltar nyams su blangs pa rab tu
NK034(ngi)006:650: gces so de ltar byas pas yang 'od ni yul
NK034(ngi)006:651: khams tsam thig le ni lnga lnga'i snang bar 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:652: te de'i dus na ngag dang sems 'dres pa'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:653: 'byung ste sngar mi shes pa'i chos shes pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:654: rang gi bla ma la gdung ba skye ba la
NK034(ngi)006:655: sogs pa 'byung ba'i tshe na yang dag rnam par
NK034(ngi)006:656: nges pa zhes byas te chos kyi gtam rang gcig
NK034(ngi)006:657: pus skad lhang lhang brjod pa gal che'o rtags de
NK034(ngi)006:658: kun la yang rlom pa ma byas par yang gong
NK034(ngi)006:659: ltar nyams su blang ba rab tu gces so 'di
NK034(ngi)006:660: ltar byas na ni 'od ni stong gsum tsam thig
NK034(ngi)006:661: le ni re re'i nang du sku re re 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:662: bas de'i tshe na rang gi lus mi snang bar
NK034(ngi)006:663: 'gyur te skabs su 'od kyi dkyil na rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:664: sor mo rnams bkram pa'i snang ba 'byung zhing lus
NK034(ngi)006:665: dang yan lag kun kyang rang gis rang mi mthong
NK034(ngi)006:666: ste skabs su ni 'od kyis lus mthong ba yang
NK034(ngi)006:667: 'byung bas de'i dus na rang gi lag sor 'od
NK034(ngi)006:668: kyi snang ba de la gtad cing nyams su blangs
NK034(ngi)006:669: pas myur du lus zad par 'gyur ba la the
NK034(ngi)006:670: tshom med do de nas lus zad par ma thug
NK034(ngi)006:671: pa la lus res snang res mi snang ba'i dus
NK034(ngi)006:672: na lus ngag yid gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:673: 'byung ste 'byung ba rnams la thogs pa med par
NK034(ngi)006:674: 'byung ba yin no rtags 'di kun kyang 'dod cing
NK034(ngi)006:675: byas pa ma yin te ye nas shes bya nyid
NK034(ngi)006:676: la babs kyis grub nas yod pas na de'i rtsal
NK034(ngi)006:677: du de snang ba yin no de nas rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:678: lus zad nas mi snang ba'i dus na rnal 'byor
NK034(ngi)006:679: pa nyams kyi dgongs pa gding du gyur pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:680: pas nyams su blang bya'i shes pa dang bral ba
NK034(ngi)006:681: zhes bya'o 'di ltar yun bag tsam gnas pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:682: no de ltar gnas pa'i tshe ni rig pa srang
NK034(ngi)006:683: la thebs pa'i dus te rig pa srang la phab
NK034(ngi)006:684: ye shes lam du drangs 'od snang la 'phel med
NK034(ngi)006:685: pa yin pas mi 'gyur ba'i gdeng skyes pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:686: no de ltar byung nas snang ba ci yang ma
NK034(ngi)006:687: yin pa'i ngo bor gyur te gnas pas chos thams
NK034(ngi)006:688: cad rang zad kyi thog tu bab pa zhes bya
NK034(ngi)006:689: ste gang gi ngo bor yang med 'di ltar yin
NK034(ngi)006:690: par grub pa med pa'i tshe na lus ngag yid
NK034(ngi)006:691: gsum gyi zhen pa zad de rig pa rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:692: ngo bo rdo rje lu gu rgyud chen por bzhugs
NK034(ngi)006:693: so 'dir ni sku gsum gyi zhen pa rang zad
NK034(ngi)006:694: sku las 'das pa'o 'di kun gyi dus na yang
NK034(ngi)006:695: 'jug pa la dbang thob pa dang skye ba la
NK034(ngi)006:696: dbang thob pa gnyis te sems can gyi don ni
NK034(ngi)006:697: ma 'gags bar rang bzhin gyis byar yod do de
NK034(ngi)006:698: ltar nyams su blangs pas zag med du mya ngan
NK034(ngi)006:699: las 'das pa'i man ngag mchog gi snying po zhes
NK034(ngi)006:700: bya ste rab tu zab pa'o +thii rgya rgya rgya
NK034(ngi)006:701: gal te skyes bu chen po de ni de ltar
NK034(ngi)006:702: nyams su len pa'i dus na bar chod kyi dbang
NK034(ngi)006:703: du gyur na yang 'di lta ste lus ngag gi
NK034(ngi)006:704: spyod pa sngon du 'gro ba 'khor 'das ru shan
NK034(ngi)006:705: 'byed pa'i dus nas song na skyes bu de ni
NK034(ngi)006:706: rang bzhin sprul pa sku'i zhing khams su dbugs phyungs
NK034(ngi)006:707: nas lo lnga brgya na bar ma do med par
NK034(ngi)006:708: sangs rgya ba la the tshom med do lus kyi
NK034(ngi)006:709: gnad gcun pa'i dus su bar chad na bar do'i
NK034(ngi)006:710: snang ba tha ma lhun grub rin po che'i snang
NK034(ngi)006:711: ba la thim lugs brgyad dang bcas te sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)006:712: ba yin no snang ba gong nas gong du 'phel
NK034(ngi)006:713: ba'i tshe bar chad na bar do gnyis pa ye
NK034(ngi)006:714: shes bzhi'i snang ba la sangs rgya bar nges so
NK034(ngi)006:715: rang rig pa nyid tshad la phebs ma phebs kyi
NK034(ngi)006:716: mtshams su tshe'i dus byas nas bar ma do dang
NK034(ngi)006:717: po tshom bu la nges pa thob ste zhag lnga
NK034(ngi)006:718: skad cig ma rnam par gsum gyi cha'i grol bar
NK034(ngi)006:719: nges so 'di ltar nyams su len par 'dod cing
NK034(ngi)006:720: zhugs nas tshe'i bar chad byung ba rnams de ltar
NK034(ngi)006:721: yin gyis 'di'i sgor zhugs pa'am tshig gi phyir spyod
NK034(ngi)006:722: pa tsam ni de ltar ma yin no phyi ma'i
NK034(ngi)006:723: lus bzang ngan len lugs ni thabs thun mong ma
NK034(ngi)006:724: yin pa'i sgo mthong ba'i dbang gis yod do mngal
NK034(ngi)006:725: gyi sgo 'grim pa ni ma yin no de'i phyir
NK034(ngi)006:726: na lus ngag gi bya ba gtan gyis tsher mar
NK034(ngi)006:727: mi 'gyur ba'i yul du nyams su len pa ni
NK034(ngi)006:728: rab tu gces so nyams su ma blangs par sangs
NK034(ngi)006:729: mi rgya ste dper na ma spyad par bzhag pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:730: gter dang 'dra'o 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'di nyid ma
NK034(ngi)006:731: 'gags par tshig gis dgag tu re ba ni rnam
NK034(ngi)006:732: pa thams cad du 'byung mi srid do tshig gis
NK034(ngi)006:733: grol na 'jig rten gyi gtam rgyud kyis kyang grol
NK034(ngi)006:734: bar 'gyur te rnam pa la grol mi srid do
NK034(ngi)006:735: dper na nor bu rin po che de la yon
NK034(ngi)006:736: tan rang rdzogs su yod kyang byi dor ma byas
NK034(ngi)006:737: par dgos 'dod phyir 'byung bar mi nus so de
NK034(ngi)006:738: bzhin du rig pa'i ngo bo la yon tan ma
NK034(ngi)006:739: 'gags par rang rdzogs su yod kyang nyams su ma
NK034(ngi)006:740: blangs na 'di nyid la rtsal rdzogs par nus pa
NK034(ngi)006:741: ma yin no rtag tu khyim med ri khrod bya
NK034(ngi)006:742: zhes pas rkyen ma yin pa'i yul du phyin te
NK034(ngi)006:743: nyams su blangs na snang ba 'di nyid la chod
NK034(ngi)006:744: nges so yang 'byed sbas pa'i nyams su len pa
NK034(ngi)006:745: dngos gzhi'i gnad yig chen mo rdzogs so +thii rgya
NK034(ngi)006:746: rgya rgya 'di min gzhan la spyod pa'i sgom chen
NK034(ngi)006:747: yi re chad de phyir bla ma'i man ngag gsang
NK034(ngi)006:748: mchog nges pa 'di nam zhig 'byung ba'i dus ni
NK034(ngi)006:749: byung ba'i tshe skal ldan snying gi bu dang 'phrad
NK034(ngi)006:750: par shog de dag gsang mchog nges pa 'di 'phrad
NK034(ngi)006:751: nas 'di yis rang rgyud grol bar byas nas ni
NK034(ngi)006:752: bstan pa'i snying po 'di ni rgyas btab nas yun
NK034(ngi)006:753: gyi btsas su 'di nyid sbed par shog bde gshegs
NK034(ngi)006:754: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis 'di la byin gyis rlobs bdag
NK034(ngi)006:755: gi snying po nges pa'i lde mig tu gnad kyi
NK034(ngi)006:756: don kun bsdebs nas 'dir bkod de phyi rabs skal
NK034(ngi)006:757: ldan rnams kyi don du ni rang gi nyams myong
NK034(ngi)006:758: bla ma'i man ngag dang rgyud kyi gzhung la brten
NK034(ngi)006:759: nas 'di ltar bris +thii phyi rabs 'jug pa'i skal
NK034(ngi)006:760: ldan nges pa can 'di la the tshom ma byed
NK034(ngi)006:761: tshad ma yin yid dpyod dang ni rang dga' ma
NK034(ngi)006:762: yin te rim gyis snyan khung brgyud pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:763: ni bla mas bdag la gtad de nyams blangs pa
NK034(ngi)006:764: 'di nyid steng du yang nas yang phab pas 'di
NK034(ngi)006:765: don mi 'gyur gnad kyi yi ge ru bla mas
NK034(ngi)006:766: gsungs shing bdag gis nyams blangs pa'i rang bzhin don
NK034(ngi)006:767: gyi gnad kyi man ngag 'di gsang ba'i yi ge
NK034(ngi)006:768: dmar ru'i nyams len la 'gyur dbang med par gnad
NK034(ngi)006:769: rnams bsdus nas ni phyi rabs 'di brten skal dang
NK034(ngi)006:770: ldan pa kun 'di ltar nyams su longs shig sa
NK034(ngi)006:771: ma ya zhes bye ma la mu tras gsungs te
NK034(ngi)006:772: mchims phu brag dmar dge gong du sgra rang 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:773: du mdzad nas chos rtags kyi rgya dang mkha' 'gro
NK034(ngi)006:774: ma'i rgyas btab ste sbas so +thii sngags kyi srung
NK034(ngi)006:775: mas srungs shig man ngag 'di rnams ni phyi ma'i
NK034(ngi)006:776: tshes la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' zhig gis
NK034(ngi)006:777: rnyed nas de'i 'og tu lag na rdo rje'i sprul
NK034(ngi)006:778: pa zhig gis dar zhing rgyas par byed do man
NK034(ngi)006:779: ngag mdo byang bsdus pa'i sgron ma bzhugs so mnyam
NK034(ngi)006:780: nyid ye shes rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo dag pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:781: snang ba chen po ni rnal 'byor don chen nyer
NK034(ngi)006:782: mtshon te 'di ni lung chen rnams kyi dam pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:783: bdag nyid gcig pur gnas pa'i tshe ri dwags lta
NK034(ngi)006:784: bur shes par bya dur khrod dag tu rgyu ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:785: tshe glang po lta bur shes par bya snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:786: nyams dang ldan pa'i tshe rgya mtsho lta bur shes
NK034(ngi)006:787: par bya rig pa tshad du smin pa'i tshe smyon
NK034(ngi)006:788: pa lta bur shes par bya rnal 'byor phung po
NK034(ngi)006:789: bor ba'i tshe dur khrod lta bur shes par bya
NK034(ngi)006:790: ye shes ma bu phrad pa'i tshe nyi zla lta
NK034(ngi)006:791: bur shes par bya shes pa dran med yal ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:792: tshe nam mkha' lta bur shes par bya 'di dag
NK034(ngi)006:793: shes pa'i rnal 'byor ni skye med gding chen khong
NK034(ngi)006:794: du tshud snang ba rnams la pha rol lo rgyud
NK034(ngi)006:795: kyi khong snying bcu bdun po sgom khrigs gcig tu
NK034(ngi)006:796: bsdebs pa ni lo 'dab rgyas pa'i sdong po 'dra
NK034(ngi)006:797: nyams len lag khrid bcu drug ni rig pa gcig
NK034(ngi)006:798: la bsdus pa ni mu tig rtsar la brgyus pa
NK034(ngi)006:799: 'dra debs kyi man ngag rnams gnyis kyis gtad pa
NK034(ngi)006:800: gnyis su bstan pa ni bang mdzod rgyas pa'i lde
NK034(ngi)006:801: mig 'dra ngo mtshar man ngag rnam bzhi ni rnal
NK034(ngi)006:802: 'byor gcig la tshang ba ni mig gi steng du
NK034(ngi)006:803: mdzub bzhag 'dra ya mtshan can gyi tshig bzhi yis
NK034(ngi)006:804: skal ldan snyan du bstsal ba ni lug rid rna
NK034(ngi)006:805: bar khu byug 'dra mthar thug gsang ba'i don bzhi
NK034(ngi)006:806: yis 'bras bu gnad du phab pa ni gnad nas
NK034(ngi)006:807: zin pa'i srog snying 'dra gsang ba'i rgyud chen bcu
NK034(ngi)006:808: bdun po rnal 'byor gcig gis shes pa ni phyug
NK034(ngi)006:809: po'i bang mdzod sgo phye 'dra de rnams don tig
NK034(ngi)006:810: bcu bdun po rgyud chen gzhung dang sbyar ba ni
NK034(ngi)006:811: glang chen sna nas dkyus zin 'dra bshad pa'i man
NK034(ngi)006:812: ngag rnam bzhi ni skyes bu'i blo la 'debs pa
NK034(ngi)006:813: ni ri rgyal kha nas rbab gtong 'dra khyad par
NK034(ngi)006:814: man ngag bcu bdun gyis gang zag gcig gi dbang
NK034(ngi)006:815: byas pa mun khung nang gi sgron me 'dra yi
NK034(ngi)006:816: ge 'phrul gyi sgro yig gis +aa li k+aa li'i
NK034(ngi)006:817: don bsdebs pa ka la ping ka'i sgra bsgyur 'dra
NK034(ngi)006:818: ka dag lhun grub rnam pa gnyis grub mtha'i sdebs
NK034(ngi)006:819: su byas pa ni btsan po mkhar du zhugs pa
NK034(ngi)006:820: 'dra smra byed mtshon cha rnams pa drug pha rol
NK034(ngi)006:821: rnams dang smra ba ni til mar ngar btags ral
NK034(ngi)006:822: gri 'dra thig le phyi nang pra khrid gnyis gang
NK034(ngi)006:823: gis goms par byas pa de rgyal pos dmangs la
NK034(ngi)006:824: dbang bsgyur 'dra thun bzhi dag gi man ngag gis
NK034(ngi)006:825: de nyid lam du slong ba ni bya ba btang
NK034(ngi)006:826: ba'i skyes bu 'dra bzhag thabs bzhi yi gdams pa
NK034(ngi)006:827: yis rnal 'byor rig pa'i gnas btsal ba mthon po'i
NK034(ngi)006:828: ri rtser phyin pa 'dra zhal chems rnam pa lnga
NK034(ngi)006:829: rnams la 'chi khar lam du byed pa ni thog
NK034(ngi)006:830: chen sa la ltung ba 'dra de dag 'dzom pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:831: skyes bu yis bya ba spangs nas blta ba ni
NK034(ngi)006:832: mi zad gter dang phrad pa 'dra de phyir yi
NK034(ngi)006:833: ge 'di dag ni rnal 'byor pa yis gsang zhing
NK034(ngi)006:834: spyad rab tu dben pa'i sa phyogs su ri dwags
NK034(ngi)006:835: dman pa'i tshul gyis 'dug 'du 'dzi spangs pa'i sa
NK034(ngi)006:836: phyogs su tha mal pa ni tshul gyis 'dug dgra
NK034(ngi)006:837: gnyen med pa'i sa phyogs su sprang po lta bu'i
NK034(ngi)006:838: tshul gyis 'dug yul dmigs med pa'i sa phyogs su
NK034(ngi)006:839: ci dgar spyod pa'i tshul gyis 'dug e ma ho
NK034(ngi)006:840: gzhi mthong ba la rtsa ba med chos nyid mthong
NK034(ngi)006:841: la sgom pa med rig pa mthong la man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:842: med snang ba mthong ba lta ba med don mthong
NK034(ngi)006:843: ba la snying rje med sems mthong ba la spyod
NK034(ngi)006:844: pa med skye shi mthong la dge sdig med dngos
NK034(ngi)006:845: po mthong la sangs rgyas med 'khrul pa mthong la
NK034(ngi)006:846: dmyal ba med nga rang mthong la thams cad med
NK034(ngi)006:847: nyams su len pa gsang ba'i debs man ngag kun
NK034(ngi)006:848: gyi mdo byang du sh+r+ai sing ha bdag gis bkod
NK034(ngi)006:849: man ngag gi mdo byang bsdus pa'i sgron ma zhes
NK034(ngi)006:850: bya ba thams cad kyi don 'grel chen po i
NK034(ngi)006:851: ti rgya rgya rgya sngags kyi srung ma e ka
NK034(ngi)006:852: dza t+ai dang zhwa'i mgon po dam tshig gi bdag
NK034(ngi)006:853: pos srungs shig gtad do las can gcig dang 'phrad
NK034(ngi)006:854: par shog bdag 'dra smyon pa lce btsun gyis gcig
NK034(ngi)006:855: pur ri khrod byas pas nyag gcig rtsa ba chod
NK034(ngi)006:856: 'du 'dzi g.yog 'khor spangs pas snang ba grogs su
NK034(ngi)006:857: shar man ngag nor phyir ma btsongs byin rlabs 'od
NK034(ngi)006:858: po che chos rnams zad sar bskyal bas lta sgom
NK034(ngi)006:859: gnyis dang bral sgra bzhi nyams su blangs pas 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:860: ba dgras mi tshugs man ngag gzhung bzhin spyad pas
NK034(ngi)006:861: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs grub da ni grol dang ma
NK034(ngi)006:862: grol gnyis su med do e ma hoh dmigs gtad
NK034(ngi)006:863: gsal ba'i sgron me bzhugs so rgya gar skad du
NK034(ngi)006:864: b+hang g+ha lang rma rma gi du yam bod skad
NK034(ngi)006:865: du man ngag gi rin po che'i debs dmigs gtad
NK034(ngi)006:866: gsal bar byed pa'i sgron me dpal sku gsum gyi
NK034(ngi)006:867: bdag nyid la phyag 'tshal lo rgya chad phyogs lhung
NK034(ngi)006:868: med pa'i lta ba dang snang ba rang sar dag
NK034(ngi)006:869: pa'i sgom pa dang zin pa bral ba med pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:870: spyod pa dang sgrub med rtsal sprug zin pa'i 'bras
NK034(ngi)006:871: bu'i don nyams blangs phyogs gcig dag tu bsdebs pa
NK034(ngi)006:872: 'di skyes bu yang rab rnams kyi don du bstan
NK034(ngi)006:873: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a pa y+ye kye ma
NK034(ngi)006:874: rigs kyi bu rnams kyis 'di ltar yid ches par
NK034(ngi)006:875: gyis shig rang gi rig pa nyid lhag mthong du
NK034(ngi)006:876: mthong bar byed pa'i man ngag gi lag khrid rin
NK034(ngi)006:877: po che'i rtsar phreng ni dang po rig pa gcer
NK034(ngi)006:878: mthong la yid ma ches na grub mtha' ngan pa
NK034(ngi)006:879: log pa 'byung dogs srid pas sngon du byang chub
NK034(ngi)006:880: sems sbyong gi man ngag la bslab par bya'o de
NK034(ngi)006:881: nas sems 'byongs pa'i drod rtags gtan la phebs pa
NK034(ngi)006:882: dang gsang sngags gzhan dag gi man ngag gis lam
NK034(ngi)006:883: du drangs te gang zag chags pa can dang chags
NK034(ngi)006:884: pa med pa gnyis su byas nas rtsa dang rlung
NK034(ngi)006:885: dang thig le la bslab par bya'o de ltar rtsa
NK034(ngi)006:886: rlung gi drod rtags gtan la phebs nas dran pa
NK034(ngi)006:887: rgyun gcod kyi man ngag gis rig pa nyid 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:888: ba las ldog par bya'o de ltar 'byung ba lnga
NK034(ngi)006:889: las bzlog nas sbas pa mig 'byed kyi man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:890: gis spyod pa sgom pa lta ba 'bras bu'i 'dug
NK034(ngi)006:891: tshul blta de ltar lta sgom spyi dang rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:892: 'dug tshul bltas nas spyod pa bsdus pa'i sgron ma'i
NK034(ngi)006:893: man ngag gi rang gi spyod pa bzhi skor du
NK034(ngi)006:894: gtan la dbab pa'o de ltar spyod pa'i drod tshad
NK034(ngi)006:895: rnyed nas da sems nyid ting nge 'dzin la dbang
NK034(ngi)006:896: thob par bya ba'i phyir sgom pa bsdus pa'i man
NK034(ngi)006:897: ngag gis sgom pa bzhi skor gyis sems la dbang
NK034(ngi)006:898: thob par bya'o de ltar sems la dbang thob par
NK034(ngi)006:899: byas nas da rang gi 'dug tshul gtan la dbab
NK034(ngi)006:900: pa'i phyir lta ba bsdus pa'i sgron me'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:901: gis sems rgyal sar 'don par bya ba'i phyir rang
NK034(ngi)006:902: gi lta ba bzhi skor gyis sems slar mi ldog
NK034(ngi)006:903: par bstan pa'o de ltar sems kyi rgyal sa zin
NK034(ngi)006:904: par byas nas da sems de mi ldog par brtan
NK034(ngi)006:905: par byed pa'i thabs su 'bras bu bsdus pa'i sgron
NK034(ngi)006:906: me'i man ngag gis rang gi 'bras bu bzhi skor
NK034(ngi)006:907: gyis sems dang rig pa ngo sprad par bya'o de
NK034(ngi)006:908: rnams ni sems gtan la 'bebs pa'i yi ge'o de
NK034(ngi)006:909: ltar sems gtan la phab nas de rang gi rig
NK034(ngi)006:910: pa gtan la dbab cing nyams su blang ba la
NK034(ngi)006:911: dngos gzhi'i man ngag gis rig pa dang dngos po
NK034(ngi)006:912: ngo sprad pa'i man ngag la bslab par bya'o dang
NK034(ngi)006:913: po man ngag gi che ba bstan nas gnyis pa
NK034(ngi)006:914: snod dang ldan pa'i slob ma la gdams shing snod
NK034(ngi)006:915: brtags nas gsum pa nyams su len pa'i gnas dang
NK034(ngi)006:916: dad pa dang ldan pa'i slob bu des bla ma
NK034(ngi)006:917: mnyes par bya ste gdams pa zhu bar bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:918: dang de ltar zhus nas rang gi blo la longs
NK034(ngi)006:919: par bya ste yi ge 'di gsang zhing sba bar
NK034(ngi)006:920: byas nas bzhi pa nyams su len pa'i dang po
NK034(ngi)006:921: sngon 'gro lus ngag gi spyod lam ji ltar bya
NK034(ngi)006:922: ba'i rim pa byas nas lnga pa lus kyi gnad
NK034(ngi)006:923: gzir nas drug pa rig pa dngos blta zhing mthong
NK034(ngi)006:924: bar bya ba dang bdun pa rig pa mthong ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:925: skyes bu de dpal kun tu bzang po dang mnyam
NK034(ngi)006:926: par bstan nas brgyad pa de nyams su blang ba
NK034(ngi)006:927: rim gyis shar ba la bslabs te nyams gong nas
NK034(ngi)006:928: gong du 'phel ba'i drod rtags brtan par byas nas
NK034(ngi)006:929: de dag kyang man ngag tshig gsum du bsdus nas
NK034(ngi)006:930: gang zag las can cig la bstan par bya bar
NK034(ngi)006:931: gsungs so de ltar nyams su blangs nas de'i don
NK034(ngi)006:932: la yid ches par bya ba'i phyir rig pa rgyab
NK034(ngi)006:933: brten gyi man ngag gis gtan la phab nas de
NK034(ngi)006:934: ltar rig pa de gtan la phab nas rang ngo
NK034(ngi)006:935: la yid ches bskyed de de nyon mongs pa'i dbang
NK034(ngi)006:936: du mi 'gyur bar bya phyir nyon mongs pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:937: dngos gzhi bstan pa'i 'gal ba bsdus pa'i sgron ma'i
NK034(ngi)006:938: man ngag gis nyon mongs pa de rnams ngos bzung
NK034(ngi)006:939: nas de ltar nyon mongs pa de rnams ngos bzung
NK034(ngi)006:940: nas gzhan dag gi 'khrul pa'i grub mtha' rnams dang
NK034(ngi)006:941: nyon mongs pa dang phyi rol gyi 'dod pa rnams
NK034(ngi)006:942: khyad med du 'dug par bstan pa ni gzhan 'dod
NK034(ngi)006:943: bsdus pa'i bcud phur gyi man ngag gis gzhan dag
NK034(ngi)006:944: gi 'dod pa ngo shes par byas nas rig pa
NK034(ngi)006:945: nyid la yid ches par bstan nas de ltar gzhan
NK034(ngi)006:946: gyi rig pa'i ye shes mi mthong bar bstan te
NK034(ngi)006:947: rang gi rig pa la yid ches par bya ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:948: phyir rig pa bsdus pa sgron ma'i man ngag gis
NK034(ngi)006:949: rig pa'i 'dug tshul bstan la phab nas rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:950: rig pa de sku gsum du gtan la 'bebs pa
NK034(ngi)006:951: ni sku gsum bsdus pa'i sgron ma'i man ngag gis
NK034(ngi)006:952: rig pa sku gsum du yid ches par byas nas
NK034(ngi)006:953: de ltar rig pa sku gsum du gtan la phab
NK034(ngi)006:954: nas rang gi rig pa de lta sgom spyod par
NK034(ngi)006:955: gtan la dbab pa ni lta sgom bsdus pa'i sgron
NK034(ngi)006:956: ma'i man ngag gis rig pa de nyid lta sgom
NK034(ngi)006:957: spyod pa yin par gtan la phab nas de ltar
NK034(ngi)006:958: lta sgom spyod par gtan la phab pa'i rig pa
NK034(ngi)006:959: de rang gi rig pa thig le nyag gcig tu
NK034(ngi)006:960: gtan la phab pa ni nyag gcig bsdus pa'i sgron
NK034(ngi)006:961: ma'i man ngag gis rang gi rig pa thig le
NK034(ngi)006:962: nyag gcig tu gtan la phab nas de ltar thig
NK034(ngi)006:963: le nyag gcig tu phab pa'i rig pa ste rig
NK034(ngi)006:964: pa de nyid las dge sdig thams cad las 'das
NK034(ngi)006:965: par gtan la 'bebs pa ni dge sdig bsdus pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:966: sgron ma'i man ngag gis rang gi rig pa de
NK034(ngi)006:967: chos thams cad du la bzla bar bya'o de ltar
NK034(ngi)006:968: man ngag gis don thams cad rnam par bsdebs nas
NK034(ngi)006:969: gang zag gcig gi cha rkyen du bstan pa ni
NK034(ngi)006:970: rin po che gser mig g.yu yis spras pa zhes
NK034(ngi)006:971: pa ste mchog tu zab par bstan pa'o de'i phyir
NK034(ngi)006:972: na man ngag 'di dag rnams shin tu zab pas
NK034(ngi)006:973: theg pa dman pa'i rigs la tshig zur tsam yang
NK034(ngi)006:974: brjod par mi bya'o gal te brjod cing bstan na
NK034(ngi)006:975: sems can dmyal ba las 'gro sa med 'jig rten
NK034(ngi)006:976: 'dir yang mig thang la 'brul kha nas khrag sgyugs
NK034(ngi)006:977: nas 'chi bar 'gyur ro de bas na rab tu
NK034(ngi)006:978: gsang ngo man ngag 'di dag ni yi ge nyung
NK034(ngi)006:979: la don mang zhing rgyas par bstan la gdams pa
NK034(ngi)006:980: 'di'i gnad ni shin tu 'dus par bstan pa'o dmigs
NK034(ngi)006:981: gtad rin po che gsal ba'i sgron me zhes bya
NK034(ngi)006:982: ba nyams su len pa'i sgom khrigs chen po rdzogs
NK034(ngi)006:983: so sngags kyi srung mas srungs shig man ngag 'di
NK034(ngi)006:984: rnams ni phyi ma'i tshe sa la gnas pa'i byang
NK034(ngi)006:985: chub sems dpa' zhig gis rnyed nas de'i 'og tu
NK034(ngi)006:986: lag na rdo rje'i sprul pa zhig gis dar zhing
NK034(ngi)006:987: rgyas par byed do i ti rgya rgya rgya gsang
NK034(ngi)006:988: ba chen po'i rtags kyi yi ge bzhugs so rgya
NK034(ngi)006:989: gar skad du he du war+na g+hu h+ya n+aa ma
NK034(ngi)006:990: bod skad du rtags kyi yi ge gsang ba zhes
NK034(ngi)006:991: bya ba bcom ldan 'das dus nges pa'i rgyal po
NK034(ngi)006:992: nyid la phyag 'tshal lo sangs rgyas rnams kyis nges
NK034(ngi)006:993: pa'i don gsungs snying po nges pa'i bka' gsang man
NK034(ngi)006:994: ngag ni gzhan dang mi 'dra man ngag gser gyi
NK034(ngi)006:995: rtsi snying po yongs bsdus 'bras bu'i bcud phyungs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:996: thabs chen gsang ba'i yang zhun 'bras bu rnams nyams
NK034(ngi)006:997: blangs phyogs gcig bsdebs nas 'di phyungs pa mang po
NK034(ngi)006:998: las ni yi ge nyung bsdus nas snying phyungs lag
NK034(ngi)006:999: mthil dag tu bstan nas ni mchog gi yang mchog
NK034(ngi)006:1000: zangs kyi yi ge can 'di don nyams su longs
NK034(ngi)006:1001: dang skal ldan bu rang gis rang bzhin yang nas
NK034(ngi)006:1002: yang bltas pas de yi 'bras bu'i dus tshod nges
NK034(ngi)006:1003: bzung nas yid ches rtags ni 'phrang bsgugs dgra dang
NK034(ngi)006:1004: 'dra mi 'gyur bzur ba'i sa med lam du phyin
NK034(ngi)006:1005: ye shes rnams kyi rang rtags lam du ston sa
NK034(ngi)006:1006: bon las ni myu gu lo 'bras rnams rim gyis
NK034(ngi)006:1007: dus tshod nges par 'byung ba bzhin goms pa las
NK034(ngi)006:1008: ni rtags rnams 'byung ba ste rjes 'dzin dad can
NK034(ngi)006:1009: yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir lam gyi khrid ka dus
NK034(ngi)006:1010: tshod nges pa'i rtags ci ltar 'byung ba'i rtags rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1011: gsal bar ni nga yis 'abri'o 'di la yid ches
NK034(ngi)006:1012: gyis 'bras bu'i rtags ni 'gyur ba ma yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1013: rgyu yi rtags ni 'gyur zhing brtan pa med lam
NK034(ngi)006:1014: gyi rtags ni 'di ltar nges pa med de yi
NK034(ngi)006:1015: phyir na rtags kyi yi ge 'di 'gyur med sra
NK034(ngi)006:1016: ba'i gzer chen btab pa bzhin 'khrul med snying gi
NK034(ngi)006:1017: thog tu phebs pa'o kye ma rjes su 'jug pa
NK034(ngi)006:1018: rigs kyi bu rnams kyis 'di ltar yid ches par
NK034(ngi)006:1019: bya'o rgyud lung bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsungs kyang
NK034(ngi)006:1020: nyams su len pa'i skal ldan rnams kyis 'di ltar
NK034(ngi)006:1021: rig par bya'o 'khrul pa rang gis rang gzings par
NK034(ngi)006:1022: 'gyur ba'i rtags dang gnad thog tu ma phebs pa
NK034(ngi)006:1023: nges pa med pa'i rtags dang rig pa mngon sum
NK034(ngi)006:1024: du ma zin na bdud kyi bar chod kyi rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1025: dang mngon sum rang thog tu phebs pas 'gyur ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1026: sa med pa ma 'gyur ba'i rtags dang bzhir rig
NK034(ngi)006:1027: par bya'o 'gyur ba'i rtags ni nyams su ma blangs
NK034(ngi)006:1028: pa'i skyes bu rnams la yang 'byung ba yod pas
NK034(ngi)006:1029: 'gyur te don mi 'byung bya dang yi dwags dud
NK034(ngi)006:1030: 'gro rnams la yang 'byung ba yod de 'di ni
NK034(ngi)006:1031: rgyu'i rtags zhes bya ste don mi 'byung nges pa
NK034(ngi)006:1032: yin no nges pa med pa'i rtags brgya dang bcu
NK034(ngi)006:1033: drug yod de sku gdung 'bar ba la sogs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1034: rgyud kyi nang nas ston pa yin te 'dir yi
NK034(ngi)006:1035: ge mang bas ma bris so de ni lam gyi
NK034(ngi)006:1036: rtags yin pas 'gyur mi 'gyur cha med pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:1037: no bar chod kyi rtags ni lus sna tshogs su
NK034(ngi)006:1038: sprul pa la sogs pa dang lus la 'od yod
NK034(ngi)006:1039: pa la sogs pa dang dgra dang gzhan la nus
NK034(ngi)006:1040: pa 'jug pa la sogs pa 'jig rten pa'i yid
NK034(ngi)006:1041: dang mthun pa rnams yin no de yang rtags gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1042: po de gang la byung ba'i skyes bu la gnad
NK034(ngi)006:1043: kyi man ngag gsum po 'di dang mi ldan na
NK034(ngi)006:1044: don med rkyang pa yin no 'gyur ba'i rtags byung
NK034(ngi)006:1045: ba'i skyes bu des skabs su chu'i dkyil du bsdad
NK034(ngi)006:1046: cing mjing pa gnyis shing gi byang bu sor bcu
NK034(ngi)006:1047: drug pa'i bar du ltems te lus la tsan+dana gyi
NK034(ngi)006:1048: mar khu rtag tu byugs nas phyi nang thams cad
NK034(ngi)006:1049: dngos por rags pa bsgoms na 'bras bu chud mi
NK034(ngi)006:1050: za ba yin no rtags ni de dag la man
NK034(ngi)006:1051: ngag de lta bu med na ngal ba don med
NK034(ngi)006:1052: yin no de lta bu byung ba'i mi de la
NK034(ngi)006:1053: ni gzhan gyi man ngag de nyid byas na yang
NK034(ngi)006:1054: 'bras bu chud mi za'o 'di dag ni bye brag
NK034(ngi)006:1055: gi man ngag rnams nas bshad pa yod do 'dir
NK034(ngi)006:1056: dgos pa med cing yi ge mang bas ma bris
NK034(ngi)006:1057: so 'di ltar 'gyur ba'i rtags brgya dang lnga yod
NK034(ngi)006:1058: pa yin no // nges pa med pa'i rtags byung
NK034(ngi)006:1059: ba'i skyes bus ni lus la bsil ba'i gos gyon
NK034(ngi)006:1060: cing kha zas kyang bsil bar bza' ngag tu a'i
NK034(ngi)006:1061: rnam pa bzlas shing sems kyis nam mkha' la sangs
NK034(ngi)006:1062: rgyas kyi sku mang po bsgoms pas phal cher nges
NK034(ngi)006:1063: pa can gyi rtags su 'gro ba yin no bye
NK034(ngi)006:1064: brag gi man ngag brgya dang bcu drug po ni
NK034(ngi)006:1065: 'dir dgos pa med pas ma bris man ngag 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1066: lta bu dang mi ldan na ngal ba don med
NK034(ngi)006:1067: yin pas de'i phyir na gnad kyi man ngag 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1068: lta bu gces so bar chod kyi rtags la bye
NK034(ngi)006:1069: brag gi man ngag rab tu gces pa yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1070: skyes bu gang dag nyams su blangs kyang rung la
NK034(ngi)006:1071: ma blangs kyang rung ste de'i lus sna tshogs su
NK034(ngi)006:1072: sprul nus pa 'byung yang bdud kyis byin gyis brlabs
NK034(ngi)006:1073: pa yin te de nyid rab tu brtags na gzugs
NK034(ngi)006:1074: brnyan gnyis par snang bas de ltar gnyis su ma
NK034(ngi)006:1075: mthong na lus gu gul nag po dang nim pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1076: chus mgo mjug la byug cing yan lag lnga la
NK034(ngi)006:1077: lder so rnying pa'i sa 'dag gis byugs na de'i
NK034(ngi)006:1078: lus khra bor 'ong ba yin te de ltar byung
NK034(ngi)006:1079: na lus la de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1080: khrus chab kyis bkru zhing ngag tu phata kyi rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1081: pa bzla zhing sems kyis phyi nang thams cad stong
NK034(ngi)006:1082: pa nyid du bsgom pa ni man ngag yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1083: 'di lta bu'i man ngag dang mi ldan na ngal
NK034(ngi)006:1084: ba don med yin gal te gong rtags med na
NK034(ngi)006:1085: yang dag pa yin no 'od ni dkar ba gleg
NK034(ngi)006:1086: gleg pa'am dmar breng breng ba'am ser lhab lhab rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1087: bar chad kyi rtags yin yang dag pa'i rtags ni
NK034(ngi)006:1088: kha dog lnga rang gsal du yod pa yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1089: de ltar byung ba'i skyes bu la ni lus glang
NK034(ngi)006:1090: po che ltar bya ngag h+aum gi rnam pa rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1091: bzlas sems ni nam mkha'i dkyil du gtad cing bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:1092: mo man ngag 'di lta bu dang mi ldan na
NK034(ngi)006:1093: don med 'chal pa yin no sgra ni steng gi
NK034(ngi)006:1094: phyogs su bshad pa'i sgra byung na yang dag pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1095: sgra byung ba yin lhag ma gang yang bar chod
NK034(ngi)006:1096: yin pas de la ni lus skyes bu'i brgyang stabs
NK034(ngi)006:1097: bya ngag tu e'i rnam pa rnams bzlas shing sems
NK034(ngi)006:1098: kyis lha'i sku dpag tu med pa rnams bsgom par
NK034(ngi)006:1099: bya'o yang rten cing 'brel ba zab mo dang gsang
NK034(ngi)006:1100: sngags la ma brten pa'i byin brlabs 'byung ba yang
NK034(ngi)006:1101: yod de 'di la chos sna tshogs kyi tshig rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1102: rang rdol du 'byung ba yin te de kun la
NK034(ngi)006:1103: yang lus ni stag mo mchongs pa ltar bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:1104: dang ngag tu i'i rnam pa rnams bzlas pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:1105: sems snying gi dkyil du sbas te bsgom par bya'o
NK034(ngi)006:1106: yang na 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra don ma bslabs par
NK034(ngi)006:1107: mi ma yin pa'i gzugs sna tshogs mthong zhing de
NK034(ngi)006:1108: dag gi brda' skad go ba dag 'byung ste de
NK034(ngi)006:1109: dag la lus 'dab chags lding ba ltar bya zhing
NK034(ngi)006:1110: ngag tu u'i rnam pa rnams bzlas pa dang sems
NK034(ngi)006:1111: kyis phyi nang thams cad stong pa nyid du bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:1112: par bya'o yang mkha' 'gro la sogs pa'i cha byad
NK034(ngi)006:1113: kyis lung ston pa dang chos smra ba dag skabs
NK034(ngi)006:1114: su 'ong zhing skabs su mi snang la gzugs de
NK034(ngi)006:1115: cig char snang la rtag tu spyod yul thams cad
NK034(ngi)006:1116: du snang ba ma yin de las lus khro bo'i
NK034(ngi)006:1117: 'gyings thabs su bya zhing ngag tu h+r+aihrnamasa bzlas sems
NK034(ngi)006:1118: kyis lha'i sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams rtag
NK034(ngi)006:1119: tu bsgom zhing de nyid spro bsdu'i rnam pa ltar
NK034(ngi)006:1120: byas nas man ngag dam par 'gyur ba yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1121: man ngag de lta bu dang mi ldan pa la
NK034(ngi)006:1122: ni bar du gcod pa'am bdud kyis bslus te khyad
NK034(ngi)006:1123: par du yi dwags kyi skye gnas su sems kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1124: snang bar 'gyur ba yin no des na gnad kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1125: man ngag de lta bu rab tu gces so de
NK034(ngi)006:1126: yang theg pa thun mong pa rnams la rtags 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1127: ba yin la rig pa mngon sum gyi don mthong
NK034(ngi)006:1128: zhing nyams su len pa'i skal ldan rnams la de
NK034(ngi)006:1129: ltar 'byung ba ma yin no de dngos po mthong
NK034(ngi)006:1130: ba'i khyad par gyis rab tu phyes pa'o mi 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1131: ba'i rtags ni gsum du rig par bya ste rang
NK034(ngi)006:1132: gis mthong la gzhan gyis mi mthong ba'i rtags dang
NK034(ngi)006:1133: gzhan gyis mngon la rang gis mi mngon pa'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1134: dang rang gzhan gnyis kas mthong ba'i rtags dang gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1135: du rig par bya'o de la gzhan gyis mthong ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1136: rtags ni 'di rnams yin te 'di dag ni rig
NK034(ngi)006:1137: pa mngon sum gyi rang gnad gzir ba tsam las
NK034(ngi)006:1138: 'byung ba ma yin no lus snum zhing skra dkar
NK034(ngi)006:1139: dang gnyer ma med pa rnams dang skra dang sen
NK034(ngi)006:1140: mo skye ba med cing lus la srog chags skye
NK034(ngi)006:1141: mi srid pa rnams dang rab tu mgyogs shing lus
NK034(ngi)006:1142: la sangs rgyas kyi phyag mtshan gyi rtags yod pa
NK034(ngi)006:1143: dang nam mkha' la 'phur zhing chu la bying ba
NK034(ngi)006:1144: med pa dang ri brag rnams la zang thal zhing
NK034(ngi)006:1145: 'byung bas mi tshugs pa rnams ni lus rtags gzhan
NK034(ngi)006:1146: gyis mthong ba yin no lus rtags rang gis tshor
NK034(ngi)006:1147: la gzhan gyis mi tshor ba rnams ni lus shing
NK034(ngi)006:1148: bal gyi 'dab ma ltar yang ba dang de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1149: zhag lnga na dbugs 'gyu ba mi tshor ba dang
NK034(ngi)006:1150: de nas zhag bcu gcig na dngos po gang la
NK034(ngi)006:1151: bltas pa 'jug nus pa dang de nas zhag nyi
NK034(ngi)006:1152: shu rtsa gcig na rang gi lus zang thal du
NK034(ngi)006:1153: mthong ba dag 'byung ba yin no rang gzhan gnyis
NK034(ngi)006:1154: kas mthong ba la ni yid la ji ltar 'gyus
NK034(ngi)006:1155: pa'i rten 'brel gyis phan thogs pa dang lus la
NK034(ngi)006:1156: sha mtshan ngo mtshar can 'byung ba dang chu la
NK034(ngi)006:1157: bying ba med pa rnams yin no de ni lus
NK034(ngi)006:1158: kyi rtags rnams te mngon sum lus kyi gnad gzir
NK034(ngi)006:1159: ba tsam las 'byung ba yin no phyi'i rtags 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1160: dag kyang mang du yod kyang phal cher nges pa
NK034(ngi)006:1161: med pa rnams yin no gal te nges pa can
NK034(ngi)006:1162: 'ga' zhig ni rang gis mi mngon pa'i khongs su
NK034(ngi)006:1163: 'du ba yin no de ni lus kyi rtags so
NK034(ngi)006:1164: gzhan gyis mthong ba'i ngag gi rtags ni tshig ci
NK034(ngi)006:1165: smras pa thams cad gzhan la phan pa dang 'khrul
NK034(ngi)006:1166: pa'i tshig mi 'byung ba dang de nas yun 'ga'
NK034(ngi)006:1167: na lkugs pa lta bur 'gyur ba dang de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1168: yun 'ga' na chos sna tshogs kyi tshig rang rdol
NK034(ngi)006:1169: ba 'di dag ni gzhan gyis tshor ba'i ngag rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1170: so rang gis tshor ba ni gtam rgyud sna tshogs
NK034(ngi)006:1171: shes pa dang de nas zhag dgu na sgra mi
NK034(ngi)006:1172: mthun pa sna tshogs shes pa dang de nas zla
NK034(ngi)006:1173: ba phyed na grub mtha'i chos sna tshogs shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:1174: dang de nas zhag bcu gcig na yid chos 'dzin
NK034(ngi)006:1175: pa'i lta ba sna tshogs shes pa dang de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1176: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig na lha la sogs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1177: rigs drug gi skad shes pa dang de nas zla
NK034(ngi)006:1178: ba phyed na bem po rnams kyi skad shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:1179: dang de nas zhag bdun nas nyan thos dang rang
NK034(ngi)006:1180: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi gsung
NK034(ngi)006:1181: nyi ma gsum du rim pa bzhin du shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:1182: ni ngag gi rtags so da ni rang gzhan gnyis
NK034(ngi)006:1183: kyis mthong ba'i rtags ni de yang gzhan gyis mthong
NK034(ngi)006:1184: ba la chu la bying ba med pa dang nam
NK034(ngi)006:1185: mkha' la 'phur ba dang 'di gnyis ni sems kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1186: rtags lus la shar ba yin no rang gis mthong
NK034(ngi)006:1187: zhing tshor ba ni snying rje chen po rgyun du
NK034(ngi)006:1188: skye ba dang de nas zla ba gcig na gang
NK034(ngi)006:1189: du bsam pa'i yul der phyin pa ni sems rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1190: lus la shar ba yin te de nas zla ba
NK034(ngi)006:1191: drug na mngon shes drug 'char ba ni rang gis
NK034(ngi)006:1192: mthong ba'i sems rtags yin no de dag ni phyi'i
NK034(ngi)006:1193: rtags zhes bya ste rgyun du snang ba ma yin
NK034(ngi)006:1194: pas gcig nub cing gcig shar ba yin no gzhan
NK034(ngi)006:1195: gyis mthong ba'i rtags su ni lus kyi rtags su
NK034(ngi)006:1196: pad+ma dang 'khor lo dang rdo rje la sogs pa
NK034(ngi)006:1197: rnams gzhan gyis mthong ba dang so'u skye ba 'ong
NK034(ngi)006:1198: ba dang skra mdog dkar po las nag por 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1199: zhing gnyer ma med pa dang lus kyi shun pa
NK034(ngi)006:1200: rnams sbrul gyi lpags pa barjesa pa ltar 'gyur ba
NK034(ngi)006:1201: dang lus po byis pa lo brgyad pa'i rnam pa
NK034(ngi)006:1202: ltar 'gyur ba dang 'di rnams lus kyi rtags yin
NK034(ngi)006:1203: no ngag ni 'jam pa dang lhang lhang po dang
NK034(ngi)006:1204: gsong po dang drang po dang rang brtol ba de
NK034(ngi)006:1205: dag ni ngag gi rtags yin no sems ni zas
NK034(ngi)006:1206: mi 'dod pa dang gos mi dgos pa dang gnyis
NK034(ngi)006:1207: ni sems rtags lus la shar ba yin no mnyam
NK034(ngi)006:1208: bzhag la zhag dang zla ba'i bar du gnas pa
NK034(ngi)006:1209: dang rlung gar 'dod par 'drongs pa ni gzhan gyis
NK034(ngi)006:1210: mthong ba'i rtags yin no 'di dag kyang rim pas
NK034(ngi)006:1211: 'byung ba yin no de dag ni rtags yin te
NK034(ngi)006:1212: rim gyis snang ba yin no rang gis mthong ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1213: rtags ni rnam pa gnyis su rig par bya ste
NK034(ngi)006:1214: sngon du lus ngag yid kyis spyod pa byas pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1215: rtags dang nyams su blangs pa dngos gzhi yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1216: de la sngon du lus ngag yid kyi rtags ni
NK034(ngi)006:1217: lus ngag gi zhen pa ma log na sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)006:1218: kyi 'bras bu thob pa'i re ba gtan med do
NK034(ngi)006:1219: de'i phyir na lus ngag yid gsum gyi ru shan
NK034(ngi)006:1220: 'byed pa'i spyod pa brtsam dgos te de nyid ru
NK034(ngi)006:1221: shan phyed pa'i rtags ni lus kyi rtags su spyod
NK034(ngi)006:1222: pa byas pa'i 'og tu gzhan gyis gsod pa'i gshed
NK034(ngi)006:1223: ma byung yang de la 'jigs pa'i sems mi 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:1224: ba'o de nas zhag dgu nas lus kyi bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:1225: dge ba la sogs pa gang la yang mi 'jug
NK034(ngi)006:1226: pa dang de nas zhag bcu gcig na 'dod chags
NK034(ngi)006:1227: kyi zhen pa skye ba med pa yang 'byung ngo
NK034(ngi)006:1228: de nas zhag nyi shu rtsa lnga la rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:1229: lus yod du mi tshor ba 'ong ngo de rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1230: ni lus kyi zhen pa log pa'i rtags yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1231: ngag gi zhen pa log pa'i rtags ni gzhan gyis
NK034(ngi)006:1232: brjod pa'i tshig la zhen cing gdung ba dang bral
NK034(ngi)006:1233: ba dang de nas zhag lnga na nang gi 'khrul
NK034(ngi)006:1234: pa'i rtags rnams dag pa dang de nas zhag bcu
NK034(ngi)006:1235: nas sngar ma thos pa'i chos kyi gtam rnams kyis
NK034(ngi)006:1236: tshig rang byung ba dang de nas zhag bdun na
NK034(ngi)006:1237: ngo mtshar can gyi gtam rnams shes pa dang de
NK034(ngi)006:1238: nas zhag bcu dgu nas sngar ma mthong ba'i gzhung
NK034(ngi)006:1239: gi tshig rnams 'byung ba dang de kun gyis yid
NK034(ngi)006:1240: dpyod kyi don rnams 'char ba ni ngag gi zhen
NK034(ngi)006:1241: pa log pa'i rtags rnams so de nas sems kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1242: spyod pa brtsams pas sems ru shun phyed pa'i rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1243: ni sngar zhen pa'i byung tshor dang phyi ma dang
NK034(ngi)006:1244: da ltar gyi byung tshor rnams 'gag pa dang de
NK034(ngi)006:1245: nas zla ba phyed na phyi nang gi 'khor 'das
NK034(ngi)006:1246: kyi zhen pa rang log pa dang de nas zhag
NK034(ngi)006:1247: dgu na dbugs phyi nang du 'gyu mi nus pa
NK034(ngi)006:1248: dang de nas zhag gsum na gzhan gyis gnod pa
NK034(ngi)006:1249: ci byas kyang sems khro ba med pa dang de
NK034(ngi)006:1250: nas nyi ma gnyis nas 'khrul pa'i sems mi 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:1251: ba dang de rnams ni sems kyi zhen pa log
NK034(ngi)006:1252: pa'i rtags yin no de rnams ni lus ngag yid
NK034(ngi)006:1253: gsum sngon du 'byong ba'i rtags yin no de dag
