NK034(ngi)006:1254: ni don gyi tha mal pa'i rtags zhes bya ste
NK034(ngi)006:1255: sangs rgya ba la rdul tsam yang phan pa med
NK034(ngi)006:1256: do yang dag pa'i rtags mchog tu gyur pa rin
NK034(ngi)006:1257: po che'i rtags ma yin zhes bya rig pa mngon
NK034(ngi)006:1258: sum gyi rtags rang la byung ba mngon sum du
NK034(ngi)006:1259: snang ba'i rtags bya ba 'di dag ni nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:1260: blangs pas dngos gzhi'i rtags rang gis mthong zhing gzhan
NK034(ngi)006:1261: gyis mthong ba med pa'i rtags 'di dag rnams yin
NK034(ngi)006:1262: no de yang thog mar lus kyi gnad ma gcun
NK034(ngi)006:1263: na sku gsum snang ba lam du mi 'char bas
NK034(ngi)006:1264: lus kyi gnad rab tu gces so de nas mig
NK034(ngi)006:1265: gi gzigs stangs ma gzir na snang ba gong du
NK034(ngi)006:1266: mi 'phel bas mig gis lta ba gal che'o de
NK034(ngi)006:1267: la de ltar byas pa'i skyes bu la 'di dag
NK034(ngi)006:1268: rnams lam du snang ba yin te nyams su blangs
NK034(ngi)006:1269: pa dngos gzhi la zhugs nas dbang po rab bzla
NK034(ngi)006:1270: ba phyed 'bring gsum tha ma zla ba bcu na
NK034(ngi)006:1271: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma nyid skyes bu'i mtheb
NK034(ngi)006:1272: mdzub kyis rtsol ba ma byas par snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1273: no de yang res snang res mi snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1274: no de yang zla ba bdun dang bcu gcig na
NK034(ngi)006:1275: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma nyid smin mtshams
NK034(ngi)006:1276: nas bral te snang ba yin te de yang nam
NK034(ngi)006:1277: mkha' dwangs pa la nyi ma'i phyogs tsam gtad de
NK034(ngi)006:1278: nyams su blangs pas thog mar dkar po lang long
NK034(ngi)006:1279: las 'od lngar snang ba dum bur snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1280: no de nas dbang po'i khyad kyis zhag gsum mam
NK034(ngi)006:1281: lnga'am bdun na 'od lnga'i snang ba gyen la 'greng
NK034(ngi)006:1282: ba dang rtsibs la shar ba dang mdung rtse'i rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1283: pa lta bur re lde tsam du snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1284: no de nas zhag dgu dang zla ba phyed dang
NK034(ngi)006:1285: nyi shu rtsa gcig na dbyings de nyid kyang kha
NK034(ngi)006:1286: dog sna tshogs su snang ba yin no de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1287: zla ba dgu dang bcu dang bco lnga'am bco brgyad
NK034(ngi)006:1288: na dbyings kyi snang ba mthong ma thag tu dkar
NK034(ngi)006:1289: po lang long dang ban bun las yul gru tsam
NK034(ngi)006:1290: du snang ba yin no de nas zhag bco brgyad
NK034(ngi)006:1291: dang nyi shu rtsa gcig dang sum cu rtsa gnyis
NK034(ngi)006:1292: na dbyings dang rig pa la nyin mo mtshan mo
NK034(ngi)006:1293: med par snang ba yin no de dag ni dbyings
NK034(ngi)006:1294: kyi 'phel yin no de nas zla ba gsum dang
NK034(ngi)006:1295: drug dang bcu gnyis na snang ba thig ler snang
NK034(ngi)006:1296: ba yin te nyung 'abru'am sran ma'i 'bru gu tsam
NK034(ngi)006:1297: du snang ste 'di dag gi dus na 'gro 'ong
NK034(ngi)006:1298: du snang ba yin no de'i tshe phyi lus ngag
NK034(ngi)006:1299: kyang 'di lta bu'i rtags dang ldan pa'i phyir snang
NK034(ngi)006:1300: ba yin te bya ba gzhan gang la yang 'jug
NK034(ngi)006:1301: mi 'dod pa dang sems can rnams la snying rje
NK034(ngi)006:1302: chen po rang bzhin gyis 'char ba yin no de
NK034(ngi)006:1303: nas yang dbang po'i khyad par gyis zla ba bdun
NK034(ngi)006:1304: dang zla ba dgu dang zla ba bcu bdun na
NK034(ngi)006:1305: rang gi mdun du mtho phyi rnams su me long
NK034(ngi)006:1306: gi rnam pa lta bu 'char zhing 'od zer ni
NK034(ngi)006:1307: rtsibs 'khyugs su 'char ba yin no de dag ni
NK034(ngi)006:1308: rig pa zin pa'i rtags yin no de'i tshe phyi
NK034(ngi)006:1309: lus ngag la yang rtags 'di rnams lta bu 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:1310: ba yin no lus yang zhing lus kyi srog chags
NK034(ngi)006:1311: rnams mi 'byung ba dang las dge sdig gi rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1312: pa gang la yang 'jug snying mi 'dod pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:1313: lus rang bzhin gyis gzhon sha chags shing snum bag
NK034(ngi)006:1314: dang ldan pa dag 'ong ngo de nas zla ba
NK034(ngi)006:1315: gsum dang lnga dang dgu na thig le de dag
NK034(ngi)006:1316: dbang po'i khyad kyis kham phor ram 'khar gzhong ngam
NK034(ngi)006:1317: bse phub kyi rnam pa tsam du snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1318: no 'od kyang yul gru tsam du snang ngo rig
NK034(ngi)006:1319: pa ni ri dwags rgyug pa'i lus kyi rang bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:1320: du 'gyur ro de'i tshe phyi'i rtags 'di lta bu
NK034(ngi)006:1321: dag 'byung ba yin no lus la gnyer ma med
NK034(ngi)006:1322: cing zas skom yang yid la mi 'dod pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:1323: rang gi snang ba de las 'bral mi phod pa
NK034(ngi)006:1324: dang bar snang la 'gro ba snyam byed cing mi
NK034(ngi)006:1325: dang 'phrad snying mi 'dod pa dang 'khrul ba'i gtam
NK034(ngi)006:1326: mi 'byung zhing rtag tu lkugs pa ltar 'agro'o de
NK034(ngi)006:1327: nas yang zla ba gsum dang lnga dang bdun na
NK034(ngi)006:1328: thig le de dag yul khams tsam du 'char te
NK034(ngi)006:1329: de yang mu khyud lnga zlum por snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1330: no de'i tshe phyi rtags kyang 'di lta bu yin
NK034(ngi)006:1331: no rang la rang rgod bro ba dang sngar mi
NK034(ngi)006:1332: shes pa'i chos mang po rgyud la char ba dang
NK034(ngi)006:1333: ci smras thams cad chos kyi tshig tu 'gyur ba
NK034(ngi)006:1334: dang rang gi bla ma la mchog tu gdung ba
NK034(ngi)006:1335: skye ba dang dgra gnyen gyi 'khrul pa 'byung mi
NK034(ngi)006:1336: srid do de nas yang zla ba gcig dang gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1337: dang lnga na thig le de dag re re'i nang
NK034(ngi)006:1338: du yang rdo rje sems dpa'i sku rkyang pa re
NK034(ngi)006:1339: re snang ba yin no 'di dus na phyi'i snang
NK034(ngi)006:1340: ba rnams rang 'gags pa'i rtags su 'byung ba lnga'i
NK034(ngi)006:1341: gnod pa dang bral ba la sogs pa rtags dgu
NK034(ngi)006:1342: 'ong ba de yin no de nyid kyi dus na
NK034(ngi)006:1343: rig pa yang 'gul ba ma yin no de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1344: zla ba gsum dang lnga dang dgu na thig le
NK034(ngi)006:1345: re re'i nang du sku lnga lnga snang ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1346: no 'di'i dus su snang ba 'gul mi srid do
NK034(ngi)006:1347: 'di'i dus na 'byung ba'i phung po snang ba rang
NK034(ngi)006:1348: 'gags nas gdos bcas sha khrag gi lus su snang
NK034(ngi)006:1350: skabs su rang gi lag pa'i sor mo rnams 'od
NK034(ngi)006:1351: du snang ba yin no 'di dag rnams rdzogs nas
NK034(ngi)006:1352: rtags rnams kyang skye med kyi klong du mya ngan
NK034(ngi)006:1353: las 'das pa yin te 'di las gzhan du rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1354: zad pa yin no de ltar skyes bu gcig la
NK034(ngi)006:1355: rtags de rnams rdzogs nas sangs rgya ba la the
NK034(ngi)006:1356: tshom yod mi srid do 'byung ba rnams 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)006:1357: la dag nas phung po lhag med du sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)006:1358: ba yin no 'di'i dus na skye ba la rang
NK034(ngi)006:1359: dbang thob pa dang 'jug pa la rang dbang thob
NK034(ngi)006:1360: par 'dod na rang gi lag pa'i sor mo la
NK034(ngi)006:1361: gtad cing bltas pas snang ba de kun rang ldog
NK034(ngi)006:1362: ste mi lus thob pa'i sems can sum stong la
NK034(ngi)006:1363: rang gi rig pa bcug pas de kun yang 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:1364: ba dag nas 'di nyid la sangs rgya ba la
NK034(ngi)006:1365: the tshom med do 'di'i dus na rig pa nyid
NK034(ngi)006:1366: bem po rnams la bcug kyang de nyid 'gul ba
NK034(ngi)006:1367: dang skad 'byin nus pa 'ong ba yin no 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1368: ltar sum stong grol ba ni rig pa nyid gcig
NK034(ngi)006:1369: pa'i phyir ro 'di tshe 'pho ba'i dus na rig
NK034(ngi)006:1370: pa nyid bcug na mtshams med pa lnga'i las byas
NK034(ngi)006:1371: pa yang rang dang mnyam nyid du 'gyur te las
NK034(ngi)006:1372: la bzang ngan med pa'i gnad kyis so 'di ni
NK034(ngi)006:1373: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i rtags yin pas 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1374: ba med do skyes bu mchog tu gyur pa rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1375: ni rtags 'di kun ma rdzogs par chos nyid zad
NK034(ngi)006:1376: pa'i sar rang grol ba'ang yod do 'dir zla ba
NK034(ngi)006:1377: bye brag tu byas nas lo bdun dang zla ba
NK034(ngi)006:1378: bcu gcig po 'di dag ni tha mal pa'i gang
NK034(ngi)006:1379: zag rnams yin no 'di la mi grol mi srid
NK034(ngi)006:1380: do dbang po 'bring po rnams ni 'di ltar lo
NK034(ngi)006:1381: bzhi zla ba lnga zhag drug na 'byung ba rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1382: rang sar yal nas 'gro ba la the tshom med
NK034(ngi)006:1383: do dbang po rab rnams ni lo gsum dang zla
NK034(ngi)006:1384: ba gsum dang zhag nyer gcig na grol ba yin
NK034(ngi)006:1385: no 'di ni rtags nges pa'i rnal 'byor pa la
NK034(ngi)006:1386: lam du snang bar byed pa'i rtags yig gsang ba
NK034(ngi)006:1387: chen po slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes mdzad pa
NK034(ngi)006:1388: nyams su len pa rnams kyi rtags yig bsdus pa
NK034(ngi)006:1389: rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya rgya gar gyi mkhan po
NK034(ngi)006:1390: bi ma las sgra mi mthun pa gsum las bsgyur
NK034(ngi)006:1391: ba lags so 'di med gzhan la spyod pa'i sgom
NK034(ngi)006:1392: chen yi re chad de'i phyir na gsang ba rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1393: kyi yi ge zhes 'di la gsang ba'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:1394: mchog tu gces pa'i yi ge 'di zung zhig rab
NK034(ngi)006:1395: tu gsang ba'i man ngag zangs yig las rtags kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1396: yi ge 'di med yug po yin yi ge gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1397: dang 'brel na rnal 'byor don chen 'grub 'di gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1398: med na bsgrubs kyang don med 'gyangs de yi phyir
NK034(ngi)006:1399: na bkol ba'i yi ge gsum sems kyi dkyil du
NK034(ngi)006:1400: phur cig sa ma ya nyams su blangs pa'i man
NK034(ngi)006:1401: ngag zangs yig can rab tu zab pas su la
NK034(ngi)006:1402: yang ster re kan dung yig can gyis sprul pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1403: sku yang 'grub mkha' 'gro mdzod kyis thun mong dngos
NK034(ngi)006:1404: grub 'grub bstan pa'i bu gcig med na bsgrub kyang
NK034(ngi)006:1405: don mi 'grub 'di kun med par rgyud la bden
NK034(ngi)006:1406: 'dzin na don med 'chal bas rang don bslu bar
NK034(ngi)006:1407: mchi'o de yi phyir na 'di tsho rab tu gces
NK034(ngi)006:1408: zhes bi ma las gsungs so sngags kyi srung mas
NK034(ngi)006:1409: srungs shig skal ldan gcig dang 'phrad par shog sa
NK034(ngi)006:1410: ma ya rgya rgya rgya bu rang gi lag ngar
NK034(ngi)006:1411: gyen du bslangs te bsgoms pas de nyid zang thal
NK034(ngi)006:1412: du snang ba yin no 'di ni mngon sum du
NK034(ngi)006:1413: 'char ba'i rtags yin no 'byung ba 'di dag rang
NK034(ngi)006:1414: gi lus 'od lngar rtogs pa'i rtags su mig gi
NK034(ngi)006:1415: rtsa rang gi mtheb mdzub kyis gtems pas 'od lnga'i
NK034(ngi)006:1416: thig le 'char ba yin no de'i phyir mngon sum
NK034(ngi)006:1417: 'char ba'i rtags gsum gyis yid ches par bstan pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:1418: +thii rgya rgya rgya dpal sngags kyi srung mas srungs
NK034(ngi)006:1419: shig gsang ba chen po'i tshad kyi yi ge bzhugs
NK034(ngi)006:1420: so rgya gar skad du gu h+ya a k+sha ra
NK034(ngi)006:1421: pra ma na ma h+aa n+aa ma bod skad du
NK034(ngi)006:1422: gsang ba chen po tshad kyi yi ge zhes bya
NK034(ngi)006:1423: ba bcom ldan 'das 'bras bu'i mnga' bdag gang yin
NK034(ngi)006:1424: pa de la phyag 'tshal lo sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1425: bka' gsang rgya che las snying po'i don kun yang
NK034(ngi)006:1426: dang yang bsdus pa dad ldan sems kyi bu rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1427: 'jug don du yang bcud snying thig zangs kyi yi
NK034(ngi)006:1428: ge'i gnad nges pa'i rtags dang smin pa'i tshad rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1429: kyis yid ches gding chen blo la dus bzung phyir
NK034(ngi)006:1430: tshad rnams bsdus nas nges pa'i lung mngon par yi
NK034(ngi)006:1431: ge 'di dag skal ldan don du bri sa bon
NK034(ngi)006:1432: las ni lo 'bras dus smin bzhin nyams blangs dus
NK034(ngi)006:1433: tshod nges pa'i tshad 'di nyid bud med sbrum ma
NK034(ngi)006:1434: zla rdzogs nas btsas te gsos te phyi nas lus
NK034(ngi)006:1435: yongs rdzogs pa ltar bla ma la brten mngon sum
NK034(ngi)006:1436: gnad gzir nas nyams su blangs pas rig pa tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1437: la phebs de nyid srang la 'degs par byed pa
NK034(ngi)006:1438: yi yi ge 'di la ltos shig rigs kyi bu
NK034(ngi)006:1439: rig pa mngon sum gyi don mthong ba las byung
NK034(ngi)006:1440: ba'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis mdo rgyud dpag tu med
NK034(ngi)006:1441: pa gsungs kyang nges pa'i don mngon sum du gtan
NK034(ngi)006:1442: la phab ste bstan cing gsungs pa ni bstan pa
NK034(ngi)006:1443: 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi pa yin zer yang
NK034(ngi)006:1444: de dag tshig gi lta ba 'ba' zhig tu bstan
NK034(ngi)006:1445: pa yin te 'di dag las rab tu bsdus na
NK034(ngi)006:1446: rgyud kyi yan lag bzhir gsungs kyang nges pa'i 'bras
NK034(ngi)006:1447: bu mngon sum gyi rang gnad la phyogs tsam reg
NK034(ngi)006:1448: pa med do de bzhi las kyang gsang ba bla
NK034(ngi)006:1449: na med pa'i rgyud bcu bdun pa yin te 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1450: rnams la mngon sum gyi gnad re na lung stong
NK034(ngi)006:1451: gi rlung po dang 'dra ste don kha g.yel de'i
NK034(ngi)006:1452: phyir na snying thig zangs kyi yi ge can ni
NK034(ngi)006:1453: rab tu zab pa'i yang zab yin pas 'di'i don
NK034(ngi)006:1454: gyi man ngag med pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams ni
NK034(ngi)006:1455: ngal ba don med yin pas des na rab tu
NK034(ngi)006:1456: gces pa'i yi ge ma ru nyams su len pa
NK034(ngi)006:1457: la tshad kyi yi ge shin tu gces pas 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1458: la ltos shig s+aa m+aa y+aa rtags kyi rgyud la
NK034(ngi)006:1459: sogs pa rab tu mang bar bshad de de'i don
NK034(ngi)006:1460: bsdus pa rtags tshad kyi yi ge 'adi'o 'di'i dus
NK034(ngi)006:1461: su nges pa'i tshad ni 'di dag rnams yin te
NK034(ngi)006:1462: 'di rab tu gsang ba'i yang gsang yang bcud gser
NK034(ngi)006:1463: gyi snying po can zhes pa yin pas skal ldan
NK034(ngi)006:1464: rnams kyi snying bcud do de yang skal ldan rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1465: kyis nyams su len pa la rab tu brtson par
NK034(ngi)006:1466: bya ste de ltar byas pas thig le stong pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1467: sgron ma shar ba'i dus na rdzogs pa chen po
NK034(ngi)006:1468: rtsol sgrub dang bral ba'i tshad yin te de yang
NK034(ngi)006:1469: 'di nyid rang gzhan gyi rtsol sgrub las ma byung
NK034(ngi)006:1470: ba'i gnad kyis so 'di'i dus na nyams su len
NK034(ngi)006:1471: pa la bar chad nas tshe'i dus byas kyang skye
NK034(ngi)006:1472: ba gnyis brgyud nas tha ma 'di nyid dang phrad
NK034(ngi)006:1473: nas sangs rgya ba la the tshom med do dbyings
NK034(ngi)006:1474: kyi sgron ma rang gi smin mtshams dang bral ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1475: dus na 'khor 'das gnyis rgyab gyes pa yin pas
NK034(ngi)006:1476: phyis mngal gyi grong khyer du mi 'jug pa'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1477: yin te de yang 'di nyid dbang po dngos dang
NK034(ngi)006:1478: ma bral ba'i gnad kyis so 'di'i dus na nyams
NK034(ngi)006:1479: len dang bral yang 'gro ba rigs drug gi mngal
NK034(ngi)006:1480: du 'jug mi srid de rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing
NK034(ngi)006:1481: khams su rdzus nas skyes te lo lnga brgya na
NK034(ngi)006:1482: sangs rgya ba la the tshom med do 'od lnga'i
NK034(ngi)006:1483: snang ba gyen la 'greng ba dang rtsibs la shar
NK034(ngi)006:1484: ba dang mdung rtse lta bu dang re lde'i rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1485: pa tsam du gyur pa'i gnas skabs na dbyings la
NK034(ngi)006:1486: rig pa 'dus pa'i tshad yin te tshe 'di la
NK034(ngi)006:1487: bar chod kyang bar do la sangs rgya ba la
NK034(ngi)006:1488: the tshom med do de yang snang ba sna tshogs
NK034(ngi)006:1489: su snang ba ste rang gi mdun phyogs tsam gzhal
NK034(ngi)006:1490: yas khang du shar ba'i gnad kyis so de'i phyir
NK034(ngi)006:1491: na 'di nyid bar do gsum pa lhun grub kyis
NK034(ngi)006:1492: snang ba la sangs rgya ba la the tshom med
NK034(ngi)006:1493: do chos rnams sna tshogs su shar ba'i tshad sus
NK034(ngi)006:1494: kyang dgag par nus pa ma yin no dbyings kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1495: snang ba de la rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang
NK034(ngi)006:1496: d+r+wa ba phyed pa dang mig mngas ris dang mig
NK034(ngi)006:1497: tshags kyi rnam pa lta bu dang za 'og gi
NK034(ngi)006:1498: gur khyim lta bu dang mchod rten dang lcags kyu
NK034(ngi)006:1499: dang mdung rtse dang mda' dang nya mig gi rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1500: pa lta bu shar ba'i dus na dbyings kyi rgyan
NK034(ngi)006:1501: rdzogs pa'i tshad yin te chos nyid la srid pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1502: bar do rang log po zhes bya ba ste 'di'i
NK034(ngi)006:1503: nyams len dang bral kyang skye shi gnyis kyi mtshams
NK034(ngi)006:1504: su 'jug mi srid pas 'di nyid kyi tshe zad
NK034(ngi)006:1505: ma thag tu bar do med par sangs rgyas la
NK034(ngi)006:1506: the tshom med do de yang dbyings rnam par dag
NK034(ngi)006:1507: pa'i sgron ma rang gnad la phebs pa'i gnad kyis
NK034(ngi)006:1508: so dbyings kyi snang ba dkar po lang long las
NK034(ngi)006:1509: de brtags pas kha dog gsal ba'i 'od la rang
NK034(ngi)006:1510: gnas pa'i lung pa de nyid mi snang bar shar
NK034(ngi)006:1511: ba'i dus na rnam rtog yul gyi zhen pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:1512: bral bas bem po'i 'khrul pa rnams bral ba'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1513: yin te dbyings kyi snang bas yul grol ba'i gnad
NK034(ngi)006:1514: kyis 'di nyid kyang bar do la mi 'jug par
NK034(ngi)006:1515: sangs rgya bar la the tshom med do dbyings dang
NK034(ngi)006:1516: rig pa nyid la nyin mtshan med par snang ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1517: dus na 'khor 'das gnyis su med par zhes bya
NK034(ngi)006:1518: ba 'khor ba nyid myang 'das su grol ba'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1519: yin te de yang mtshan mo 'khor ba'i cha nyin
NK034(ngi)006:1520: mo myang 'das kyi cha yin pas mtshan mo'i snang
NK034(ngi)006:1521: ba nub pa'i tshad kyis so nyams su blangs pa
NK034(ngi)006:1522: la 'di yang bar do mi snang zhing de ltar
NK034(ngi)006:1523: byung na lo lnga na phung po lhag ma dang
NK034(ngi)006:1524: bcas nas sangs rgya ba la the tshom med do
NK034(ngi)006:1525: thig le'i snang ba nyung 'bru tsam sran rdog tsam
NK034(ngi)006:1526: snang ba'i dus na dbyings kyi ra bar rig pa
NK034(ngi)006:1527: nyid chud pa zhes bya ste snying po'i bcud du
NK034(ngi)006:1528: dril ba'i tshad yin pas 'di man chad kyi rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1529: ma rdzogs par nyams len pa bar chad na sprul
NK034(ngi)006:1530: pa mi 'byung phung po bor nas phyi yi rtags
NK034(ngi)006:1531: rnams ston nas sangs rgya ba la the tshom med
NK034(ngi)006:1532: do thig le me long gi rnam pa tsam du
NK034(ngi)006:1533: snang zhing thig le de kun kyang rtsibs rgyugs su
NK034(ngi)006:1534: snang ba'i dus na thig le nyag gcig bcud du
NK034(ngi)006:1535: smin pa zhes bya ste 'od dang 'od khyim smin
NK034(ngi)006:1536: pa'i tshad yin no de nas thig le nyid dbang
NK034(ngi)006:1537: po tha ma la kham phor tsam du snang 'bring
NK034(ngi)006:1538: la 'khar gzhong tsam du snang rab la bse phub
NK034(ngi)006:1539: tsam du snang ba'i dus na rig pa nyid rlung
NK034(ngi)006:1540: dang bral du nye ba zhes bya ste thig le
NK034(ngi)006:1541: tshad du phyin pa yin pas 'di las cher 'gro
NK034(ngi)006:1542: ba'i nges pa med do de nas thig le de
NK034(ngi)006:1543: dag rab tu mang ba che chung gong ma tsam
NK034(ngi)006:1544: las yul khams gang ste de re re 'od lnga
NK034(ngi)006:1545: lnga'i mu khyud rab tu bskor ba'i dus na ni
NK034(ngi)006:1546: snod nyid bcud du smin pa zhes bya ste thig
NK034(ngi)006:1547: le'i nang na sku rkyang ba re re snang ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1548: dus na bcud nyid snying po dril ba zhes bya'o
NK034(ngi)006:1549: rig pa nyid dbyings kyi gzer thebs pas na lam
NK034(ngi)006:1550: smin pa'i tshad yin te sku gsum lam du byas
NK034(ngi)006:1551: pa'i gnad kyis so de nas thig le re re'i
NK034(ngi)006:1552: nang du sku lnga lnga shar ba'i dus na sku'i
NK034(ngi)006:1553: zhen pa rang chod pa zhes bya ste sku gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1554: lam du rdzogs pa'i tshad yin pas rang gi lus
NK034(ngi)006:1555: 'od gsal du grol ba'i gnad kyis 'di nyid la
NK034(ngi)006:1556: 'byung ba rang dag la song ba de yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1557: de nyid kyi tshad rang gi mtshan nyid bcu gcig
NK034(ngi)006:1558: tu rigs par bya ste de yang 'di lta ste
NK034(ngi)006:1559: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i rtsol sgrub dang bral
NK034(ngi)006:1560: ba'i tshad dang mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun gcod pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1561: tshad dang chos rnams sna tshogs su shar ba'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1562: dang snang srid thams cad gdams ngag tu shes nas
NK034(ngi)006:1563: 'khrul ba rang thog tu ngo shes pa'i tshad dang
NK034(ngi)006:1564: yul rkyen du ma 'gags pa'i tshad dang 'khor 'das
NK034(ngi)006:1565: mnyam nyid gnas pa'i tshad dang rig pa las 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1566: ba med pa'i tshad dang nyag gcig gral du tshud
NK034(ngi)006:1567: pa'i tshad dang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po thig
NK034(ngi)006:1568: le nyag gcig mngon sum du gtan la phebs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1569: tshad dang sku rnams kyi zhen pa bzlog pas phyi'i
NK034(ngi)006:1570: snang ba 'di nyid grol ba'i tshad dang gdos bcas
NK034(ngi)006:1571: rang 'gags te 'byung ba rnams rang sar dengs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1572: tshad dang bcu gcig gi rnal 'byor pas chos thams
NK034(ngi)006:1573: cad zad pa'i snang ba nyid mthong ba yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1574: de yang tshad de dag gis de ltar nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:1575: len pa dang ma bral na sus kyang dgag par
NK034(ngi)006:1576: mi nus kyi mi 'dod kyang shugs kyis lam du
NK034(ngi)006:1577: snang nges pa yin no dper na bud med sbrum
NK034(ngi)006:1578: ma zla ba rdzogs nas sus kyang dgag par mi
NK034(ngi)006:1579: nus te lto ba stong par gnas pa bzhin no
NK034(ngi)006:1580: de yang cig car du skye ba ma yin te
NK034(ngi)006:1581: rim gyis lus nas skyes nas skye ba dang mtshungs
NK034(ngi)006:1582: so de yang zhag bdun tshan dang po la mer
NK034(ngi)006:1583: mer po dang tar tar po la sogs pa bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:1584: te rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po rtsol sgrub dang
NK034(ngi)006:1585: bral ba'i tshad med na theg pa thun mong pa
NK034(ngi)006:1586: dang khyad par med pas 'di'i dus na las dge
NK034(ngi)006:1587: sdig ci byas kyang phan gnod dang bral ba dge
NK034(ngi)006:1588: sdig ji ltar byas kyang ngan song du lhung mi
NK034(ngi)006:1589: srid pa'i gdeng thob pa'o mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun
NK034(ngi)006:1590: gcod pa'i tshad med na 'gro drug gi g.yang sa
NK034(ngi)006:1591: mi chod de tshe gcig la sangs rgya ba dang
NK034(ngi)006:1592: 'gal te 'di dus na sngar byas pa'i bag chags
NK034(ngi)006:1593: rnams kyis rdul tsam yang mi gos te dmyal ba
NK034(ngi)006:1594: dang sangs rgyas khyad med pa'i gdeng thob pa'o chos
NK034(ngi)006:1595: rnams sna tshogs su shar ba'i tshad med na yid
NK034(ngi)006:1596: dpyod 'dzin pa'i lta ba rnams dang khyad par cung
NK034(ngi)006:1597: zad med pas 'di'i dus na phyi rol gyi yul
NK034(ngi)006:1598: rkyen du ma byung yang phan gnod dang bral te
NK034(ngi)006:1599: mngon sum gyi snang ba rkyen gyis mi shigs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1600: gding thob pa'o snang srid thams cad gdams ngag tu
NK034(ngi)006:1601: shes nas 'khrul pa rang thog tu chod pa'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1602: med na tshig gi rjes su 'brangs pa'i skyes bu
NK034(ngi)006:1603: rnams dang khyad med pas 'di'i dus na brjod bya
NK034(ngi)006:1604: thams cad mthong snang du shar bas tshig gi spros
NK034(ngi)006:1605: pa thams cad nye bar zhi ba'i gding thob pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:1606: yul rkyen du ma 'gags pa'i tshad med na tha
NK034(ngi)006:1607: mal pa'i snang ba dang khyad med pas 'di'i dus
NK034(ngi)006:1608: na de be ma rig gnyis 'dzin gyi shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:1609: dang bral te rags pa'i 'byung ba rnams kyis gnod
NK034(ngi)006:1610: ma bskyal ba'i gding thob pa'o 'khor 'das mnyam pa
NK034(ngi)006:1611: nyid du gnas pa'i tshad med na grub mtha' 'dzin
NK034(ngi)006:1612: pa'i skyes bu rnams dang khyad med pas 'di'i dus
NK034(ngi)006:1613: na lta ba'i zhen 'dod rnams dang bral te nyams
NK034(ngi)006:1614: len la yengs pa med pa'i gding thob pa'o rig
NK034(ngi)006:1615: pa la 'gyur ba med pa'i tshad med na las
NK034(ngi)006:1616: kyi rlung dang khyad med pas 'di'i dus na rig
NK034(ngi)006:1617: pa nyid ye shes kyi rlung dang 'dres pas 'gyu
NK034(ngi)006:1618: ba rnams rang sar grol ba'i gding thob pa'o nyag
NK034(ngi)006:1619: gcig gral du tshud pa'i tshad med na theg pa
NK034(ngi)006:1620: sna tshogs kyi skad dang khyad med pas 'di'i dus
NK034(ngi)006:1621: na lta sgom gyi spros pa rang chod pa'i gding
NK034(ngi)006:1622: thob pa'o rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po thig le
NK034(ngi)006:1623: nyag gcig mngon sum du gtan la phebs pa'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1624: med na chad pa mu stegs pa rnams dang khyad
NK034(ngi)006:1625: med pas 'di'i dus na gol sa thams cad rang
NK034(ngi)006:1626: thog tu chod pa'i gding rnyed pa yin no sku
NK034(ngi)006:1627: rnams kyi zhen pa'i snang ba bzlog pas phyi'i snang
NK034(ngi)006:1628: ba 'di nyid las grol ba'i tshad med na sku
NK034(ngi)006:1629: gsum 'bras bu rang 'dod pa rnams dang khyad med
NK034(ngi)006:1630: pas 'di'i dus su snang ba dang ngo bo lam
NK034(ngi)006:1631: du byas pas sku gsum du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa
NK034(ngi)006:1632: rang log pas gding thob pa'o gdos bcas 'gags te
NK034(ngi)006:1633: 'byung ba rang sar dengs pa'i tshad med na phung
NK034(ngi)006:1634: po bdag med du 'dod pa rnams dang khyad mes
NK034(ngi)006:1635: pas 'di'i dus na phyi nang gi 'byung ba lngas
NK034(ngi)006:1636: bcings pa las rang log ste zag pa rnams rang
NK034(ngi)006:1637: zad ba'i gding thob pa'o de nas zla gcig gam
NK034(ngi)006:1638: zla ba dagu'am zla ba bdun na chos nyid zad
NK034(ngi)006:1639: pa'i snang ba dang 'du 'bral med par 'gyur ba
NK034(ngi)006:1640: la the tshom med do de'i phyir na ma'i mngal
NK034(ngi)006:1641: du zhugs te lus rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang zhag
NK034(ngi)006:1642: rnams mtshungs so de ltar nyams su len pa'i sngon
NK034(ngi)006:1643: du lus ngag yid gsum sbyangs pa'i man ngag rab
NK034(ngi)006:1644: tu gces so sngon du lus ngag ma sbyangs par
NK034(ngi)006:1645: rig pa mngon sum gyi gnad gzir yang 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)006:1646: du 'byung ba rang zad la 'gro mi srid do
NK034(ngi)006:1647: de'i phyir na 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyad
NK034(ngi)006:1648: pa rab tu zab bo de nas lus kyi 'dug
NK034(ngi)006:1649: stangs rnams ma gzir na sku gsum gyi zhen pa
NK034(ngi)006:1650: lam du mi chod pas chos nyid zad pa ngo
NK034(ngi)006:1651: mi shes des na rtag tu ngag ma bcad na
NK034(ngi)006:1652: brjod med kyi don mi mthong bas thig le nyag
NK034(ngi)006:1653: gcig mngon du mi snang ngo mig gi lta stangs
NK034(ngi)006:1654: kyis rig pa ma gcun na rig pa mngon sum
NK034(ngi)006:1655: du mi snang bas sems dang ye shes mi phyed
NK034(ngi)006:1656: do de'i phyir na gdams ngag 'di rnams rim gyis
NK034(ngi)006:1657: byas pas snang ba rim gyis 'phel ba la the
NK034(ngi)006:1658: tshom med do de'i phyir na 'byung ba dwangs snyigs
NK034(ngi)006:1659: phyed pa'i tshad phyi'i 'byung ba lnga 'gags te 'od
NK034(ngi)006:1660: du snang ba'i dus na yin no chos can dang
NK034(ngi)006:1661: chos nyid phyed pa'i tshad dbyings smin mtshams dang bral
NK034(ngi)006:1662: ba'i dus na yin no sems dang ye shes phyed
NK034(ngi)006:1663: pa'i tshad rig pa nyin mtshan med pa'i dus na
NK034(ngi)006:1664: yin no kun gzhi dang chos sku phyed pa'i tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1665: rang gi gdos bcas mi snang ba'i dus na yin
NK034(ngi)006:1666: no yid dang shes rab phyed pa'i tshad ni snang
NK034(ngi)006:1667: ba sna tshogs su shar ba'i dus na yin no
NK034(ngi)006:1668: de'i phyir na rig pa tshad la ma pheb na
NK034(ngi)006:1669: 'bras bu la thug pa med de ngal ba don
NK034(ngi)006:1670: med no tshad la phab pas don 'gyur mi srid
NK034(ngi)006:1671: do de yang 'di nyid sku gsum lam du byed
NK034(ngi)006:1672: pa ni lus ngag yid kyi gnad bstan nas sprul
NK034(ngi)006:1673: pa sku'i sgro 'dogs lam du chod do de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1674: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma lam du shar nas
NK034(ngi)006:1675: thig le la sku lnga shar ba phan chod ni
NK034(ngi)006:1676: longs sku'i sgro 'dogs lam du chod pa'o stong ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1677: thig le 'di'i snang ba med par snang ba gong
NK034(ngi)006:1678: du 'phel ba yang yod de rang gi lus mi
NK034(ngi)006:1679: snang bar skabs su 'od kyi sor mo snang ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1680: dus na chos sku'i sgro 'dogs lam du chod pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:1681: thabs sna tshogs la bslab pa'i rig pa mang du
NK034(ngi)006:1682: bshad nas yod kyang las kyi kha tshar du ma
NK034(ngi)006:1683: ste sems mi gnas pa gnas par byed pa tsam
NK034(ngi)006:1684: las sangs rgya ba la rdul gyi cha tsam yang
NK034(ngi)006:1685: phan pa med do de'i phyir na man ngag gi
NK034(ngi)006:1686: rgyal po zangs yig can med na gzhan ma kun
NK034(ngi)006:1687: stong yug yin pas 'di dang bral na rang gzhan
NK034(ngi)006:1688: ga nyis ka'i don 'grub pa ma yin no man
NK034(ngi)006:1689: ngag 'di nyid rtags dang tshad 'brel bas rin chen
NK034(ngi)006:1690: gser la g.yu'i phra bkod 'dra de yi phyir na
NK034(ngi)006:1691: rtags kyi yi ge la tshad kyi yi ge 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1692: med stong yug yin de yi phyir na man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:1693: zangs yig can gsum po 'brel na rnal 'byor don
NK034(ngi)006:1694: chen 'grub 'di gsum med na bsgrubs kyang don med
NK034(ngi)006:1695: 'gyang sprul pa'i sa bon bstan pa'i bu gcig po
NK034(ngi)006:1696: 'di med bsgrubs kyang 'bras bu smin pa min 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1697: bcangs pa yis sprul sku'i yon tan rdzogs des na
NK034(ngi)006:1698: bstan pa kun gyi rang btsas 'di mkha' las char
NK034(ngi)006:1699: babs rtsi thog rgyas pa bzhin 'di nyid bcangs pa
NK034(ngi)006:1700: tsam gyis 'bras bu smin man ngag snying po yang
NK034(ngi)006:1701: gsang thugs kyi bcud yi ge ma ru snying gi
NK034(ngi)006:1702: snying tig chos 'di nyid yod na rig pa'i gtan
NK034(ngi)006:1703: srid yin phung po nyid dang bcas te sems la
NK034(ngi)006:1704: sbos de yi yon tan brjod kyis langs pa min
NK034(ngi)006:1705: de yi gsang ba yi ge ma bu rnams rab
NK034(ngi)006:1706: tu gces pas mchog tu rgyas btab bo gzhan la
NK034(ngi)006:1707: spel bar byed pa 'di nyid min gsang sngags kun
NK034(ngi)006:1708: gyi yang zhun rig pa'i gnad 'di ru bsdus te
NK034(ngi)006:1709: snying po sems la brlan rin chen gser ltar rtag
NK034(ngi)006:1710: tu spyan na brin gsang ba'i yi ge de yang
NK034(ngi)006:1711: de dang mtshungs de yi phyir na de yi man
NK034(ngi)006:1712: ngag gzer rtags kyi yi ge 'di med 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)006:1713: rnams bskyal ba'i sa med thug pa med par 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1714: de phyir tshad rnams nges pa'i yi ge 'dis dus
NK034(ngi)006:1715: tshod nges bar rab tu bstan par bya'o snying po
NK034(ngi)006:1716: mchog gi thabs 'di nges par gsang tshad la slebs
NK034(ngi)006:1717: par pheb nas mngon du byas gsang ba'i yang gsang
NK034(ngi)006:1718: snying po'i bcud du dril bcud rnams bsdus nas snying
NK034(ngi)006:1719: po lam du byas des na yi ge 'di dag
NK034(ngi)006:1720: rab tu dkon dam pa'i don du nges par gzung
NK034(ngi)006:1721: bar bya rab tu bsdus pa'i snying tig mchog tu
NK034(ngi)006:1722: gces spros bcas blo yi yul du tshad 'di rnams
NK034(ngi)006:1723: spros te rgyas pa'i don du gzung bar bya chos
NK034(ngi)006:1724: nyid tshad ni mnyam par gnas pa yin shes rab
NK034(ngi)006:1725: tshad ni snyems byed med pa yin ye shes tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1726: ni rang gsal kha dog lnga dbyings kyi tshad ni
NK034(ngi)006:1727: gong ltar snang ba yin rig pa'i tshad ni 'phel
NK034(ngi)006:1728: 'grib med pa yin 'od kyi tshad ni phyi nang
NK034(ngi)006:1729: 'gags pa yin thig le'i tshad ni sku lnga rang
NK034(ngi)006:1730: gsal yin gzhi yi tshad ni 'phel dang bcas pa
NK034(ngi)006:1731: yin lam gyi tshad ni gdos bcas nub pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:1732: 'bras bu'i tshad ni zad sar 'khyol ba yin sku
NK034(ngi)006:1733: yi tshad ni rang rkyang sems dpa' yin 'di dag
NK034(ngi)006:1734: rnams kyang snying po nges pa'i tshad phyis kyi tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1735: ni 'di yin sems kyi bu 'od kyi tshad ni
NK034(ngi)006:1736: 'od du snang ba yin thig le'i tshad ni gdangs
NK034(ngi)006:1737: kyi yang dag yin rlung gi tshad ni phyi nas
NK034(ngi)006:1738: de bzhin sgra dbyings kyi tshad ni sa rnams g.yo
NK034(ngi)006:1739: ba yin sku yi tshad ni phyi nas de bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:1740: sku 'di rnams kyang ni rig pa'i yon tan yin
NK034(ngi)006:1741: tshad la ma phebs don gnyis shes pa min tshad
NK034(ngi)006:1742: dang ldan pa'i nyams len chud mi za des na
NK034(ngi)006:1743: tshad kyi yi ge 'di gces so nyams su len
NK034(ngi)006:1744: pa rnams kyi tshad kyi yi ge zhes bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:1745: sprul pa po dga' rab rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs
NK034(ngi)006:1746: so rgya rgya rgya sngags kyi srung ma rnams kyis
NK034(ngi)006:1747: srungs shig i ti dge'o mngon sum snying thig gsang
NK034(ngi)006:1748: ba'i yi ge dmar ru'i rgyab yig bzhugs so kha
NK034(ngi)006:1749: tham rgyab yig gi stod cha dpal kun tu bzang
NK034(ngi)006:1750: po la phyag 'tshal lo mngon sum snying thig gsang
NK034(ngi)006:1751: ba'i yi ge dmar ru'i rgyab yig 'di nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:1752: len pa'i skal ldan slob ma des sngon du bla
NK034(ngi)006:1753: ma la gser rang lus tsam phul la lo gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1754: gyi gong nas zhu ba 'bul las spyod pa'i thabs
NK034(ngi)006:1755: sna tshogs bya'o de nas dben pa'i gnas su spros
NK034(ngi)006:1756: bcas kyi dbang dang spros med shin tu spros med
NK034(ngi)006:1757: rab tu spros pa med pa rnams kyis smin par
NK034(ngi)006:1758: byed pa gal che'o de nas grol bar byed pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1759: gdams ngag le lo can ma bsgoms par sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)006:1760: ba dang brtson 'grus can bsgoms nas tshe 'dir sangs
NK034(ngi)006:1761: rgya ba'i gdams ngag bstan te de yang kun tu
NK034(ngi)006:1762: bzang po gzhi thog ma nas sangs rgyas sems can
NK034(ngi)006:1763: gyis ma rtogs te 'khor bar 'khyams de gang gis
NK034(ngi)006:1764: len na ma rig pas len te de la rlung
NK034(ngi)006:1765: bzhi 'od bzhi 'byung ba bzhi la sogs par 'khrul
NK034(ngi)006:1766: te 'byung ba bzhi las mi'u rigs bzhir byung ngo
NK034(ngi)006:1767: de ltar rtogs pa dang byed pa'i las kyang byung
NK034(ngi)006:1768: ngo de ltar blo yi rtsal la che chung byung
NK034(ngi)006:1769: bas de la chu'i mi ni lus zlum la leb
NK034(ngi)006:1770: pa dang skra shad de ba dang ngag dal ba
NK034(ngi)006:1771: lus kyang mnyen pa dang nyal ba dang dal ba
NK034(ngi)006:1772: shas che ba de'i dbang gis 'phyor che ba mo
NK034(ngi)006:1773: la sred pa kha 'jam la gti mug pa byi
NK034(ngi)006:1774: la'i spyod pa dang 'dra'o de la dbang yang spros
NK034(ngi)006:1775: bcas bskur gdams ngag kyang spros bcas sems 'dzin gyi
NK034(ngi)006:1776: skor bstan sems lung sdom khrigs la sogs pa'i rgyu
NK034(ngi)006:1777: 'bras gtso che ba la blo khrid spros med blos
NK034(ngi)006:1778: mi chun pa'i phyir ro de mngon du byung ba
NK034(ngi)006:1779: dang gsang ba bla med bstan la nyams su len
NK034(ngi)006:1780: du gzhug pas 'di la sangs ma rgyas kyang tshe
NK034(ngi)006:1781: 'phos pa dang mngal gyi grong khyer mi 'grim ste
NK034(ngi)006:1782: sprul pa sku'i zhing khams su sangs rgya ba la
NK034(ngi)006:1783: the tshom med do sa'i mi ni lus gru bzhi
NK034(ngi)006:1784: sgeg pa skra mtshams dma' ba kha spu yod pa
NK034(ngi)006:1785: gtam nyung zhing brda mi gsal ba sdod tshan che
NK034(ngi)006:1786: ba spros pa la mi dga' bas dbang yang spros
NK034(ngi)006:1787: med bskur gdams ngag kyang sgom bcas sgom med dbyer
NK034(ngi)006:1788: med du sems sde dang man ngag gi sde dbyer
NK034(ngi)006:1789: med du spel ba gdab mjug tu bla med bstan
NK034(ngi)006:1790: 'di la sangs ma rgyas kyang 'chi kha bar do
NK034(ngi)006:1791: la sangs rgya ba la the tshom med do me
NK034(ngi)006:1792: yi mi ni lus gru gsum la dmar zhing sna
NK034(ngi)006:1793: rno skom dad che spro thung zhe sdang dang nga
NK034(ngi)006:1794: rgyal che shes rab che bas spros med shin tu
NK034(ngi)006:1795: spros med bskur gdams ngag kyang klong sde sgom med
NK034(ngi)006:1796: bstan te de nas mjug bla med dang 'phrad ma
NK034(ngi)006:1797: thag tu rtags tshad mthar phyin nas lo lnga'am bdun
NK034(ngi)006:1798: du sangs rgya ba la the tshom med do rlung
NK034(ngi)006:1799: gi mi ni lus yang zhing mgyogs kha zla gam
NK034(ngi)006:1800: du mngon pa dang sdod mi tshugs pa dang phrag
NK034(ngi)006:1801: dog che rdzun che blo yangs shes rab che bas
NK034(ngi)006:1802: dbang yang rab tu spros pa med pa bskur gdams
NK034(ngi)006:1803: pa'ang spros med zang thal don rgyud rnams bstan no
NK034(ngi)006:1804: mjug tu bla med bstan pas lo gsum na tshe
NK034(ngi)006:1805: 'di rang la zag bcas mi snang bar sangs rgya'o
NK034(ngi)006:1806: g.yu yig can du shes so de ltar gang 'phrod
NK034(ngi)006:1807: bltas la sbyin no de yang sems lung sgom khrims
NK034(ngi)006:1808: las ma mthong yul de blta 'dod na yul de
NK034(ngi)006:1809: yid la ma byed par lam de yid la gyis
NK034(ngi)006:1810: la song zhes pas dad pa dang ldan pa'i slob
NK034(ngi)006:1811: ma de dur khrod dam dben par sngon du rang
NK034(ngi)006:1812: gi bla ma mnyes par byas te tshogs bsag pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1813: sbyor ba bya de nas bla mas gdams pa gdab
NK034(ngi)006:1814: par bya'o de la shes rab rnam pa gsum la
NK034(ngi)006:1815: blo thag bcad nas tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)006:1816: dgos te 'dir ma grol na yid dpyod 'dzin pa
NK034(ngi)006:1817: dang khyad par med do de la spyod pa la
NK034(ngi)006:1818: rgyun du byed pa dang sgom pa rgyun du byed
NK034(ngi)006:1819: pa dang lta ba la rgyun du byed pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:1820: 'bras bu la rgyun du byed pa'o de yang spyod
NK034(ngi)006:1821: pa la rgyun du byas nas sangs rgya ba ni
NK034(ngi)006:1822: 'khor 'dus ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa dang brtul
NK034(ngi)006:1823: zhugs grangs 'dzin gyis spyod pa dang snang ba rang
NK034(ngi)006:1824: sar grol ba rig pa rnal tu 'bebs pa'i spyod
NK034(ngi)006:1825: pa rnams dbang du gsal lo sgom pa la rgyun
NK034(ngi)006:1826: du byed pa ni de la rang bzhin gyi bsam
NK034(ngi)006:1827: gtan dang bcos ma'i bsam gtan no rang bzhin ni
NK034(ngi)006:1828: lha mi phal dang khra tshang na nyal ba dang
NK034(ngi)006:1829: ri bong gi mig dang bu chung gi mig dang
NK034(ngi)006:1830: mda' srang gi mig dang de rnams la yod do
NK034(ngi)006:1831: lung du ma bstan pa'i lha dang mi la bsam
NK034(ngi)006:1832: gtan bcas pa yang yod do bcos ma'i bsam gtan
NK034(ngi)006:1833: ni rnal 'byor pa la gnod pa gnyis yod de
NK034(ngi)006:1834: 'phral du zas dang dgos phugs su rmi lam dang
NK034(ngi)006:1835: bag chags gnyis so de la bsam gtan gyi thun
NK034(ngi)006:1836: bzhi yin te bcud len la brten nas zas kyi
NK034(ngi)006:1837: zhen pa bcad pa'i bsam gtan gyi thun dang rlung
NK034(ngi)006:1838: dang rten 'brel la brten nas gos kyi zhen pa
NK034(ngi)006:1839: bcad pa'i bsam gtan dang gnyid kyi gdams ngag gis
NK034(ngi)006:1840: rmi lam gyi zhen pa bcad pa'i bsam gtan dang
NK034(ngi)006:1841: rtse gcig gi bsam gtan la brten nas bag chags
NK034(ngi)006:1842: kyi zhen pa bcad pa'i bsam gtan no de la
NK034(ngi)006:1843: gsum po logs su shes so 'dir rtse gcig gi
NK034(ngi)006:1844: bsam gtan la dmigs pa rgyud la bslab pa logs
NK034(ngi)006:1845: su shes 'dir rten med la bslab pa ston no
NK034(ngi)006:1846: sgom pa la rgyun du byed na lha dang mi
NK034(ngi)006:1847: yi sems 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa'i bsam gtan
NK034(ngi)006:1848: dang bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa'o de la lha
NK034(ngi)006:1849: dang mi yi sems 'dzin ni dben pa'i gnas su
NK034(ngi)006:1850: bsod nams kyi tshogs sngon du song bas lus skyil
NK034(ngi)006:1851: krung du bcas la rang gi sna rtse a dkar
NK034(ngi)006:1853: rang gi rlung phar la song ba'i dus su a
NK034(ngi)006:1854: de phar la rgyangs rgyangs song ba la blo gnas
NK034(ngi)006:1855: par bya rlung nang du rdub pa'i tshe dkar hri
NK034(ngi)006:1856: li li tshur sna rtse la gnas pa la bya'o
NK034(ngi)006:1857: rang gi lus la tshad pa'i nad yod na a
NK034(ngi)006:1858: de grang reg dang ldan par bsgoms grang ba yod
NK034(ngi)006:1859: na tsha reg dang ldan par bsgom de ltar thun
NK034(ngi)006:1860: chung la grangs mang bar nyin mtshan bar ma chad
NK034(ngi)006:1861: par bsgoms pas skye med bsam ngo dang bral ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:1862: nyams myong mi skye mi srid do gang zag gcig
NK034(ngi)006:1863: gi cha rkyen rdzogs so de nas yang bar chod
NK034(ngi)006:1864: sel ba'i yi ge phata drag po la sems bzung
NK034(ngi)006:1865: ba ni sngon du bla ma mnyes par byas la
NK034(ngi)006:1866: gong ltar lus bcos la lhod cing rlung rang song
NK034(ngi)006:1867: bzhag der sems yongs su bcug la rab tu drag
NK034(ngi)006:1868: pos phata brjod pas dus de nyid du shes pa
NK034(ngi)006:1869: gtad med du 'ong ste de'i dus su sems bzung
NK034(ngi)006:1870: zhing yang dang yang du phata kyis shes pa la
NK034(ngi)006:1871: gsal bar bya ste de nas nyin mtshan med par
NK034(ngi)006:1872: nyams su blangs pas rang bzhin yongs su dag pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1873: nyams su myong ba mi skye mi srid do des
NK034(ngi)006:1874: gang zag gcig gi cha rkyen thal nas yang khro
NK034(ngi)006:1875: bo dgyes pa'i gad mo la sems bzung ba ni
NK034(ngi)006:1876: sngon du bla ma yon gyis mnyes par byas te
NK034(ngi)006:1877: lus gnad gong bzhin byas la ngag tu zhes drag
NK034(ngi)006:1878: la thung bar brjod shes pa ha la gtad rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1879: rtog la sogs pa'i mi bde ba ci byung dus
NK034(ngi)006:1880: su ha drag tu brjod cing rlung dang bsre ba
NK034(ngi)006:1881: gnad yin no de ltar dus thams cad du bsgoms
NK034(ngi)006:1882: pas chos nyid yang dag pa ngos bzung dang bral
NK034(ngi)006:1883: ba'i nyams myong mi skye mi srid do des gang
NK034(ngi)006:1884: zag gcig gi cha rkyen thal yang lha ma yin
NK034(ngi)006:1885: rtsod pa 'gyed pa la sems 'dzin pa ni dben
NK034(ngi)006:1886: pa'i gnas su bla ma mnyes pa dang lus gnad
NK034(ngi)006:1887: ri mthon po'i khar tsog pur 'dug la mgo dang
NK034(ngi)006:1888: po dal gyis bsgril lus kyang dang po bsgul bskyod
NK034(ngi)006:1889: dal bar bya de las brel ba gsum gsum bzhi
NK034(ngi)006:1890: bzhi tsam bya de nas mgo la sogs pa drag
NK034(ngi)006:1891: tu bsgril bas dus gcig tsam na phyi yi snang
NK034(ngi)006:1892: ba dmar khrug khrug pa dang ser breng breng ba
NK034(ngi)006:1893: dang sngo yal yul dang nag thabs thibs dang de
NK034(ngi)006:1894: nas skya sang nge 'byung ngo de ltar yun ring
NK034(ngi)006:1895: du byas pas phyi sa rdo ri brag gi snang
NK034(ngi)006:1896: ba ci'i ngo bor yang grub pa med do 'di'i
NK034(ngi)006:1897: dus na mthong snang rang grol nas snang ba 'od
NK034(ngi)006:1898: gsal du mthong ba'i nyams myong mi skye mi srid
NK034(ngi)006:1899: do 'di'i dus na rlung la shis pa'i kha zas
NK034(ngi)006:1900: bsten par bya'o lte bar yi ge ram la sems
NK034(ngi)006:1901: gtad pa ni gnad yin no gang zag gcig gi
NK034(ngi)006:1902: cha rkyen thal lo yang rnam par rtog pa h+aum
NK034(ngi)006:1903: gis ded pa la sems bzung ba ni de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1904: sngon bzhin bla ma mnyes par byas la dben pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1905: gnas su lus ngag khong lhod ngag tu h+aum zhes
NK034(ngi)006:1906: ring por dbyangs dang bcas pas brjod de rlung sems
NK034(ngi)006:1907: dang bsre ba ni gnad yin no yang h+aum zhes
NK034(ngi)006:1908: nam mkha'i khams su 'phang ba dang sdud pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:1909: lus la 'jug pa dang sa rdo ri brag la
NK034(ngi)006:1910: sogs pa zang thal ba la sogs pa bar ma
NK034(ngi)006:1911: chad par byas pas sems zin te gang du yang
NK034(ngi)006:1912: sems g.yeng ba med pa 'byung ngo rtog pa chos
NK034(ngi)006:1913: nyid 'bar ba'i nyams myong mi skye mi srid do
NK034(ngi)006:1914: da ni skal ldan lam du 'jug pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:1915: la bla ma mnyes pa la sogs pa'i go rim
NK034(ngi)006:1916: gong ltar byas la rang stan bde ba la 'dug
NK034(ngi)006:1917: ste stong pa nyid rim gyis la sems bzung ba
NK034(ngi)006:1918: ni dang po lus bye brag mang por bsil la
NK034(ngi)006:1919: mgo gcig pu rang la yang ming mang ngo mig
NK034(ngi)006:1920: rna ba sna lce la sogs pa dpag tu med
NK034(ngi)006:1921: par gsal bas ming la don brtags pas mgo'i dbang
NK034(ngi)006:1922: po grub pa med par shes pa dang de nas
NK034(ngi)006:1923: lus spyi la brtags kyang grub pa ma rnyed de
NK034(ngi)006:1924: nas phyi rol gyi dngos po thams cad la de
NK034(ngi)006:1925: ltar ming don du mas btsal bas kyang ma rnyed
NK034(ngi)006:1926: de ltar ming gis btags pa thams cad stong par
NK034(ngi)006:1927: go bas dngos po yang 'gyur te stong par 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1928: ba 'ong ngo des ni chos nyid stong pa nyid
NK034(ngi)006:1929: du mi grol mi srid do de nas mig tu
NK034(ngi)006:1930: snang tshad dang dran tshad la shes pa bcug cing
NK034(ngi)006:1931: de nyid skad cig la stong par song ba la
NK034(ngi)006:1932: blo gnas par byas pas dus tshod cig na gang
NK034(ngi)006:1933: la bltas pa stong par khrol khrol 'gro ba dag
NK034(ngi)006:1934: 'byung ngo de ltar yun ring du bsgoms pas snang
NK034(ngi)006:1935: ba thams cad me long la has btab pa ltar
NK034(ngi)006:1936: stong sang gi mi sgrol mi srid do de yang
NK034(ngi)006:1937: dang po snang la de nas gnyis pa stong la
NK034(ngi)006:1938: gsum pa snang stong gang du'ang ma grub pa'o 'di
NK034(ngi)006:1939: tsho'i sdom yang dag la brten pa'i bsam gtan bzhi'i
NK034(ngi)006:1940: dus su shes pa rna bar gzhug cing ngag gi
NK034(ngi)006:1941: brjod pa ma nyams pa gal che lus la brten
NK034(ngi)006:1942: pa'i bsam gtan lha ma yin rtsod pa 'gyed pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1943: dus su lus kyi sgul bskyod ma bshig pa gnad
NK034(ngi)006:1944: yin no lhag ma sems kyi bsam gtan gnyis po'i
NK034(ngi)006:1945: dus su sems kyi gtad sa ma nor zhing ma
NK034(ngi)006:1946: yengs pa gnad yin no de la ming du btags
NK034(ngi)006:1947: na nyin mtshan kha sbyor gyi sgom pa zhes bya'o
NK034(ngi)006:1948: dmigs pa rten med la bslab pa'i bsam gtan no
NK034(ngi)006:1949: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i bsam gtan
NK034(ngi)006:1950: ni sa dang po'i bden pa mthong ba nas yon
NK034(ngi)006:1951: tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis gnyis pa la nyi shu
NK034(ngi)006:1952: rtsa bzhi de ltar rim pa bzhin sa bcu rgyun
NK034(ngi)006:1953: gyi ting nge 'dzin tshud tshad la'o bde bar gshegs
NK034(ngi)006:1954: pa'i dgongs pa ni thun mtshams las 'das te ma
NK034(ngi)006:1955: bcos rang bzhag gnas lugs te ji ltar de la
NK034(ngi)006:1956: 'gyur med pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:1957: zhes pas gnad ni rgya mtsho cog bzhag ste gang
NK034(ngi)006:1958: bsgoms kyang mig ma 'khrul bar rang sor bzhag pa
NK034(ngi)006:1959: gnad yin lta ba la rgyun du byed pa la
NK034(ngi)006:1960: lnga ste lta ba grong khyer rgyun gcod man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:1961: ri bo cog bzhag dgongs pa khams gsum yongs grol
NK034(ngi)006:1962: nyon mongs pa gnas dag gang zag zad pa'o dang
NK034(ngi)006:1963: po ni gsum phyi chos can dum bu ba la
NK034(ngi)006:1964: rdo rje'i mig gis cog bzhag tu bltas pas phyi
NK034(ngi)006:1965: chos can gyi rnam pa snang la rang bzhin med
NK034(ngi)006:1966: par gzugs brnyan nam rmi lam sgyu ma lta bur
NK034(ngi)006:1967: mthong bas 'khrul pa la yang dag tu grub pa
NK034(ngi)006:1968: med par rtogs pas khams gsum du ldog pa med
NK034(ngi)006:1969: pas blo bde ba'o nang chos can gyi bye brag
NK034(ngi)006:1970: pa la rtogs pa'i tshul gyis shes rab kyi mig
NK034(ngi)006:1971: gis rang bzhin du bltas pas kun rdzob kyi rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1972: pa rnams med pa'i rang bzhin sgyu ma lta bu
NK034(ngi)006:1973: mthong bas 'khrul pa rang dag tu grub pa med
NK034(ngi)006:1974: par rtogs pas rig pa la bag chags med pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:1975: blo bade'o gsang ba bu chung gi mig gis rnam
NK034(ngi)006:1976: par dag pa la cer bzhag tu bltas te de
NK034(ngi)006:1977: yang gnad gsum dang ma bral bar bltas pas dbyings
NK034(ngi)006:1978: rig 'du 'bral med par mngon sum du mthong bas
NK034(ngi)006:1979: blo bade'o de yang brtson 'grus rab tshe 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)006:1980: la zag bcas mi snang bar sangs rgya'o 'bring ngo
NK034(ngi)006:1981: 'phrod nas dum re nyams su blangs de nas thams
NK034(ngi)006:1982: cad nyams su blang longs ma byung ba la ni
NK034(ngi)006:1983: bar do la rang gi chos nyid stobs su gyur
NK034(ngi)006:1984: nas sangs rgya'o tha ma gdams ngag zhus nas nyams
NK034(ngi)006:1985: su blang longs ma byung ba ni chos nyid bden
NK034(ngi)006:1986: pa'i byin rlabs kyis sprul sku'i zhing khams su bardzusa
NK034(ngi)006:1987: te skyes nas mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun chad nas
NK034(ngi)006:1988: sangs rgya'o de la man ngag ri bo cog bzhag
NK034(ngi)006:1989: ni theg pa thams cad kyi lta ba mthong rang
NK034(ngi)006:1990: gi chos nyid mi 'gyur bar gnas par ri bo
NK034(ngi)006:1991: cog bzhag go de ltar rtogs pa'i tshe na 'gro
NK034(ngi)006:1992: drug rang sar grol te 'khrul pa mi gnas par
NK034(ngi)006:1993: rtogs pa'o nyon mongs pa gnas dag ni nyon mongs
NK034(ngi)006:1994: pa rnams rang byung rang dag tu rtogs pa'i dus
NK034(ngi)006:1995: so chos zad pa ni yid la byed pa'i chos
NK034(ngi)006:1996: thams cad rang sar dag nas bya rgyu med pa'o
NK034(ngi)006:1997: 'bras bu la rgyun du byed pa ni 'di'i man
NK034(ngi)006:1998: ngag tu ri bo cog bzhag dgongs pa srid gsum
NK034(ngi)006:1999: ka dag nyon mongs rang grol gang zag chos las
NK034(ngi)006:2000: grol ba'o de yang ngo sprod kyi gnad la goms
NK034(ngi)006:2001: pas chos nyid mngon sum gyi snang ba ni yul
NK034(ngi)006:2002: nam mkha' stong pa 'di nyid la rnam rtog gang
NK034(ngi)006:2003: gis kyang ma bslad par mthong ba de nyid do
NK034(ngi)006:2004: de nyid la rig pa cog bzhag tu bzhag nas
NK034(ngi)006:2005: nyams su blangs pas dus tshod gcig tsa na thig
NK034(ngi)006:2006: le stong pa'i sgron ma rtsol ba med par shar
NK034(ngi)006:2007: nas 'ong ngo de nas ye shes kyi thig le
NK034(ngi)006:2008: phyed sku dang bcas pa tshun chad nyams gong 'phel
NK034(ngi)006:2009: gyi snang ba'o de nas 'od lnga gyen 'greng dang
NK034(ngi)006:2010: rtsibs shar dang mchod rten brtsegs pa lta bu dang
NK034(ngi)006:2011: d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa dang mig mngas
NK034(ngi)006:2012: ris dang yul gru tsam pa rnams 'ong ngo re
NK034(ngi)006:2013: re yang sku lngar snang ba'i dus na rig pa
NK034(ngi)006:2014: tshad la phebs te dper na bre tshad dang srang
NK034(ngi)006:2015: tshad la phebs pa lta bu'o 'di'i dus na nyams
NK034(ngi)006:2016: su ma blangs kyang chog go de nas der cher
NK034(ngi)006:2017: 'phel ba med pas de dag gi 'phel zad nas
NK034(ngi)006:2018: chos nyid la sogs pa snang ba'i nyams de dag
NK034(ngi)006:2019: gang du'ang snang ba'i ngo bo med pa ni chos
NK034(ngi)006:2020: nyid zad pa'i snang ba zhes tha snyad du byas
NK034(ngi)006:2021: so de ltar dang po dbang dang dam tshig dang
NK034(ngi)006:2022: sdom pa zhus nas bla mas rigs kyi bu 'dug
NK034(ngi)006:2023: gyis dang 'di ltar 'ong gis zhes gdams pa bstan
NK034(ngi)006:2024: nas nyams su blangs pas dang po chos nyid mngon
NK034(ngi)006:2025: sum gyi snang ba 'char de nas nyams gong 'phel
NK034(ngi)006:2026: gyi snang ba 'char de nas rig pa tshad phebs
NK034(ngi)006:2027: kyi snang ba 'char de nas chos nyid zad pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2028: snang ba 'char te de ltar snang ba bzhi mthar
NK034(ngi)006:2029: phyin pa'i dus na skal ldan de zag pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:2030: bcas pa'i phung po mi snang bar sangs rgya'o +thii
NK034(ngi)006:2031: gu h+ya phra yig can zangs yig can gyi snang
NK034(ngi)006:2032: byed sgron ma bzhugs so rgyab yig gi smad cha
NK034(ngi)006:2033: dpal bde byed chen po'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo
NK034(ngi)006:2034: gsang ba'i yi ge ma ru'i dgongs pa'i gnad rnams
NK034(ngi)006:2035: ni sbas shing gab pa'i tshig kun gsal bar ni
NK034(ngi)006:2036: spyi yi don rnams 'di ru snang bar yang snang
NK034(ngi)006:2037: byed sgron ma'i yi ge 'di la ltos sgron ma
NK034(ngi)006:2038: yis ni mun pa snang ba ltar yi ge 'di
NK034(ngi)006:2039: yis tshig gi don rnams ni rnam par snang bar
NK034(ngi)006:2040: bdag gis bkod nas bstan 'di nyid tshig la the
NK034(ngi)006:2041: tshom ma za bar 'di don nyams su longs shig
NK034(ngi)006:2042: rigs kyi bu gal te gsang mchog man ngag 'di
NK034(ngi)006:2043: rnyed nas nyams su ma blangs 'khor bar g.yengs byas
NK034(ngi)006:2044: na bskal pa bye ba drug 'bum nyid du yang
NK034(ngi)006:2045: sangs rgyas nyid dang 'phrad par 'gyur re kan de
NK034(ngi)006:2046: bas 'di la goms shing tshad la phab gsang ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:2047: yi ge ma ru'i gzhung gi tshig rnams phye nas
NK034(ngi)006:2048: gnad kyi yi ge gsal ba'i lde mig 'di dgos
NK034(ngi)006:2049: pas 'di la nan tan bya spros pa gcod pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2050: sgron ma 'byung ba lnga rang dengs kyi man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:2051: 'di la 'byung ba lnga cham la 'bebs pa'i man
NK034(ngi)006:2052: ngag gis yi ge a rnam pa lnga dbugs gcig
NK034(ngi)006:2053: la brtsegs mar bsgoms pas 'byung ba lngar gnad la
NK034(ngi)006:2054: phebs par a rnam pa lnga'i don skye med du
NK034(ngi)006:2055: rgyas btab la rig pa'i ngo bo a'i rang bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:2056: du nya mas su blang rlung chu me'i sa bon
NK034(ngi)006:2057: gsum gyi yi ges lus kyi 'byung ba 'khrugs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2058: dus na gnas gsum du bzhag ste shes pa der
NK034(ngi)006:2059: gtad nas bsgom zhing rlung yang der gtad nas bsgoms
NK034(ngi)006:2060: pa nad rnams dag par byed pa'i 'byung ba'i gnad
NK034(ngi)006:2061: yin nam mkha' rnam par dag par byed pa a
NK034(ngi)006:2062: ganya sa brtseg gi gdams ngag gis sems bar snang
NK034(ngi)006:2063: la +aa la gtad pas a sems kyi dri ma
NK034(ngi)006:2064: rang zad la gtong ba'i gnad yin rlung rnam par
NK034(ngi)006:2065: dag par byed pa la a sum brtseg gi gdams
NK034(ngi)006:2066: ngag gis dbugs phyi nang du rgyu ba'i tshe dran
NK034(ngi)006:2067: pa rnams rang yal du gtong ba ni snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2068: skye med du gtad pa ni +aaa&a&a&a la dbugs gtad
NK034(ngi)006:2069: pas dbugs nang du rgyu ba'i tshe dri ma rnams
NK034(ngi)006:2070: zad cing stongs pa'i gnad yin chu rnam par dag
NK034(ngi)006:2071: par byed pa a bzhi brtsegs gi man ngag gis
NK034(ngi)006:2072: 'dzin pa rnam par dag pa byed pa ni yi
NK034(ngi)006:2073: ge +aa+aa &&& la sems gtad pas sdud byed dri
NK034(ngi)006:2074: ma rnams rang sar dag nas mig 'di rnam shes
NK034(ngi)006:2075: rang rgyud du 'dzin pa dag par byas pa'i gnad
NK034(ngi)006:2076: yin me rnam par dag par byed pa a lnga
NK034(ngi)006:2077: brtseg gi man ngag gis gzung ba mched pa'i dri
NK034(ngi)006:2078: ma rang sar dag pa byed pa mig gi bar
NK034(ngi)006:2079: snang la yi ge +aa+aaa &&&la sems gtad pas sgo
NK034(ngi)006:2080: lnga'i rang rgyud bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod pa'i gnad
NK034(ngi)006:2081: yin no 'di'i gnad kyi man ngag la ni ka
NK034(ngi)006:2082: kha ga nga ca ni 'byung ba lnga'i rtsa ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:2083: man ngag yin yig smad gcig tu bsdus pas 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:2084: ba gcig dril ba'i man ngag la ni ki khi
NK034(ngi)006:2085: gi ngi ci 'byung ba gong ma 'byed pa'i lde
NK034(ngi)006:2086: mig yin zhabs kyus lnga po de yang 'byed pa
NK034(ngi)006:2087: yin de tshom bu sdebs pas 'byung ba lnga'i lus
NK034(ngi)006:2088: bzung ba de yang rnam par zad par bya ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:2089: yi ge 'di dgos pas de'i man ngag gnad du
NK034(ngi)006:2090: 'di ltar 'gro des ni 'byung ba zad par byed
NK034(ngi)006:2091: pa'i gnad yin no +thii spyir man ngag sdebs pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2092: yi ge 'di kun la rtsa ba nyid dang de
NK034(ngi)006:2093: 'byed lde mig dang yang 'byed dang ni de yi
NK034(ngi)006:2094: t+aika la ka rkyang kha rkyang la sogs rtsa bar
NK034(ngi)006:2095: shes par bya de rjes gu gu rnams ni 'byed
NK034(ngi)006:2096: pa'i lde mig yin de mthun zhabs kyu rnams ni
NK034(ngi)006:2097: yang 'byed yin de bzhin de'i 'og rnams ni t+ai
NK034(ngi)006:2098: ka yang t+aika yin mdo mdud dang ni yang rtsa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2099: gnad yin no de ltar ka kha ma bu'i sdebs
NK034(ngi)006:2100: kyis ni 'di'i 'grel dang yang 'grel 'byed pa'i lde
NK034(ngi)006:2101: mig rnams su shes par bya'o de ltar goms pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2102: gnad kyi man ngag tshig drug la ka kha ma
NK034(ngi)006:2103: bu sdebs nas ni drug tshan drug gis rtsa ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:2104: don rnams gtan la phab 'di ltar tshig ni sum
NK034(ngi)006:2105: cu so drug gis goms pa'i gnad kyi man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:2106: tu ni 'di 'gyur nas 'dis ni rdo rje sems
NK034(ngi)006:2107: dpa'i zhal ni mngon du mthong de'i gnad kyi yi
NK034(ngi)006:2108: ger 'di bstan pa'o sems sbyong ba sngon du 'gro
NK034(ngi)006:2109: ba'i rig pa'i thabs kyi gnad yig gsal ba ni
NK034(ngi)006:2110: 'di ltar skal ldan rnams kyis byang chub sems sbyong
NK034(ngi)006:2111: ba'i man ngag tu bstan pa yin sprul pa'i sgo
NK034(ngi)006:2112: nas gzhan gyi don bya bar bstan pa'i phyir gdams
NK034(ngi)006:2113: pa rnams kyi sems sbyong ba'i man ngag ni bla
NK034(ngi)006:2114: mas slob ma de dad pa drag po rgyud la
NK034(ngi)006:2115: skyes pas 'khor ba las blo ldog pa'i dgos pa
NK034(ngi)006:2116: yod pa'i phyir grong khyer chen po'i dbus su khrid
NK034(ngi)006:2117: de slob ma de la sems sbyong ba'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:2118: rnams bslabs te mi rtag rgyud la goms su gzhug
NK034(ngi)006:2119: go de'i skabs su sangs rgyas kyi yon tan mdo
NK034(ngi)006:2120: longs su bshad cing skabs su grong khyer gyi mi
NK034(ngi)006:2121: de yang mi rtag par 'dug ang snyam pa rgyud
NK034(ngi)006:2122: la 'dris su gzhug bla mas skabs su 'khor ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:2123: nyes dmigs kyang bshad par bya'o de ltar zhag du
NK034(ngi)006:2124: ma goms su bcug pas dad pa drag po de'i
NK034(ngi)006:2125: rgyud la ma skyes na gsang sngags kyi snod du
NK034(ngi)006:2126: mi rung bas las rgyu 'bras la blo sbyong du
NK034(ngi)006:2127: gzhug pa gces so de nas dad pa nam skyes
NK034(ngi)006:2128: pa na rig pa mngon sum la nges pa thob
NK034(ngi)006:2129: par bya ba'i phyir 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa
NK034(ngi)006:2130: la sogs pa la blo dbab par bya ba'am 'khor
NK034(ngi)006:2131: 'das ru shan yang na de ltar yang ma yin
NK034(ngi)006:2132: te de ltar sngon du byang chub sems 'byongs pa
NK034(ngi)006:2133: de la de nyid brtan par bya ba'i phyir rtsa
NK034(ngi)006:2134: rlung la sems gnas shing brtan par bya ba'i phyir
NK034(ngi)006:2135: rtsa rlung gi man ngag rnams bla mas bstan te
NK034(ngi)006:2136: sgom du gzhug go rtsa rlung gi man ngag bsgom
NK034(ngi)006:2137: pa la ni gnad yig med do pra khrid nas
NK034(ngi)006:2138: gsal bas mi dgos so sems sbyong ba la sogs
NK034(ngi)006:2139: pa'i man ngag sna mang po bstan pa ni rang
NK034(ngi)006:2140: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po 'di thabs sla ba dang
NK034(ngi)006:2141: thabs myur ba dang thabs mang ba yin pa'i phyir
NK034(ngi)006:2142: gsungs te de'i phyir rdzogs pa chen po ni tshogs
NK034(ngi)006:2143: drug lhug pa yin no zhes tshig tsam bstan nas
NK034(ngi)006:2144: yod de de kun ni gnad med pa'i tshig bral
NK034(ngi)006:2145: ba yin te gnad du 'gro ba'i man ngag gis
NK034(ngi)006:2146: 'di ltar tshogs drug ma spangs par sangs rgya bar
NK034(ngi)006:2147: byed pa'i thabs 'di nas ston par byed pa'i gnad
NK034(ngi)006:2148: du sgra thams cad la brten nas zag pa med
NK034(ngi)006:2149: pa'i nyams myong skye bar bstan pa dang de bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:2150: du dri la brten nas skye bar bstan pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:2151: de bzhin du gzugs dang ro dang reg dang chos
NK034(ngi)006:2152: la brten nas zag pa med pa'i nyams skye bar
NK034(ngi)006:2153: bstan pa dang sgra'i de bzhin nyid shes na chos
NK034(ngi)006:2154: thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa shes pa'i gnad
NK034(ngi)006:2155: ni gling bu'i sgra la brten te sems sbyang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2156: dang pi wang gi rgyud la brten te sems sbyong
NK034(ngi)006:2157: ba dang bum ldir gyi sgra la brten te sems
NK034(ngi)006:2158: sbyong ba dang rnga d+r+wa ba rgyud mngas la brten
NK034(ngi)006:2159: pa dang rdza rnga kha mngas la brten pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:2160: drag po rnams la sbyong ba ni pi wang gi
NK034(ngi)006:2161: rgyud la brten pa dang cha lang gi rgyud la
NK034(ngi)006:2162: brten pa dang dril bu'i sing la brten pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:2163: dung gi dung la brten nas sems sbyong ba la
NK034(ngi)006:2164: sogs pa gsungs te sems sbyangs nas dag par ma
NK034(ngi)006:2165: byas na rig pa sngon du gtan la mi phebs
NK034(ngi)006:2166: pa'i phyir ro gzugs la brten te sems sbyangs pas
NK034(ngi)006:2167: zag pa med pa'i nyams skye ba ni dpe du
NK034(ngi)006:2168: ma la brten pa dang rten 'brel du ma la
NK034(ngi)006:2169: brten pa dang brda' du ma la brten pa la
NK034(ngi)006:2170: sogs pa gsungs pas so dri ni tsan+dana dang ga
NK034(ngi)006:2171: bur la sogs pa yid la thun pa'i dri rnams
NK034(ngi)006:2172: la brten nas sems sbyangs pas zag pa med pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2173: nyams skye ba dang nim pa dang tsan+dana dmar po
NK034(ngi)006:2174: dang shing ka la ki ta la sogs pa yid
NK034(ngi)006:2175: dang mthun pa rnams la brten nas sems sbyangs pas
NK034(ngi)006:2176: zag pa med pa'i nyams skye ba ni thabs kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2177: yan lag tu bstan pa'o ro la bu ram drug
NK034(ngi)006:2178: ldan dang shing gi rgyal po ma ra ta zhes
NK034(ngi)006:2179: bya ba'i 'bras bu'i rdog ma drug cha tsam skyes
NK034(ngi)006:2180: bu gang gis myong ba de ni nyi ma lnga'am
NK034(ngi)006:2181: bdun nam dgu'i bar du dran pa gzhan la mi
NK034(ngi)006:2182: 'jug cing lus g.yo ba med cing sems rang gsal
NK034(ngi)006:2183: ba dang sems bde lugs su gnas shing sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)006:2184: kyi yon tan rjes su 'dzin par 'gyur ba yod
NK034(ngi)006:2185: do reg ni rtsi'i rgyal po ma sa li bya
NK034(ngi)006:2186: ba'i sdong po'i shing yod de de'i lo ma g.yas
NK034(ngi)006:2187: su 'khyil ba zhig yod pa de blangs nas de'i
NK034(ngi)006:2188: 'dab ma su'i snying kha la reg pas ni sems
NK034(ngi)006:2189: rang bzhin gyis bsam gtan la gnas te 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)006:2190: ji ltar reg pa la bsam gtan du 'gyur ba
NK034(ngi)006:2191: yod do chos ni bla ma'i gdams ngag rnams yin
NK034(ngi)006:2192: no de bzhin du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK034(ngi)006:2193: rnal 'byor pas 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs
NK034(ngi)006:2194: par longs spyod sangs rgyas la yod pa'i yon tan
NK034(ngi)006:2195: de ltar bstan pa ni rdzogs pa chen po thabs
NK034(ngi)006:2196: mang ba yin no de'i phyir sems la goms shing
NK034(ngi)006:2197: 'byongs pas rig pa nyid mngon sum du gtan la
NK034(ngi)006:2198: phebs pa'i dgos pa yod par bstan pa'o spyad par
NK034(ngi)006:2199: bya ba byang chub sems kyi gnad yig yang 'byed
NK034(ngi)006:2200: sbas pa'i lde mig gsang ba'o +thii mi 'gyur rang
NK034(ngi)006:2201: snang gi lta ba chen po la phyag 'tshal lo
NK034(ngi)006:2202: de ltar sems rtsa rlung gis phab ste lta sgom
NK034(ngi)006:2203: spyod pa rnams kyi man ngag gis rang bzhin gyi
NK034(ngi)006:2204: 'jug sgo gsal bar bya ba'i phyir 'di kun tshig
NK034(ngi)006:2205: gis gtan la phab pas tshig gi zhen pa chod
NK034(ngi)006:2206: nas rig pa mngon sum la gding du gnas pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2207: dgos pa yod de yang spyod pa thams cad kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2208: gnad du lus yin pas spyod pa rab tu gces
NK034(ngi)006:2209: so sgom pa thams cad kyi gnad du dal ba
NK034(ngi)006:2210: yin pas lus ngag sems dal ba gtso che'o lta
NK034(ngi)006:2211: ba thams cad kyi gnad du mig yin pas mig
NK034(ngi)006:2212: gsal bar bya ba'i rtsa bso zhing bsku mnye bya
NK034(ngi)006:2213: ba dang 'o ma bya nag mo'i sgo nga'i ser
NK034(ngi)006:2214: po dang skyer pa'i bar shun gyi phyi ma dang
NK034(ngi)006:2215: gzi rnying pa nag khra brdungs pa'i phye ma dang
NK034(ngi)006:2216: 'di rnams sbyar te tshes gcig dang gnam stong nya'i
NK034(ngi)006:2217: nang par tho rangs la sngon du chu grang mos
NK034(ngi)006:2218: mig dang gdong pa dag par bkrus te de nas
NK034(ngi)006:2219: de kun gyi lde gu mig la bkus nas de'i
NK034(ngi)006:2220: nang par bzhin ba gsar pa'i 'o ma bkol ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:2221: nang du shing mngar btab ste 'thung na mig 'grib
NK034(ngi)006:2222: par mi 'gyur ro de ltar byas pas rig pa
NK034(ngi)006:2223: mngon sum la lta ba dang mi 'bral ba'i gnad
NK034(ngi)006:2224: du 'gyur ba yin no 'bras bu thams cad kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2225: gnad du dbyings dang rig pa tshad la phab pa
NK034(ngi)006:2226: gces pa yin no de yang spyod pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)006:2227: ni snang ba rang sar bzhag pa dang snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2228: ci nas bsgyur ba gnyis las 'gro sa med do
NK034(ngi)006:2229: snang ba rang sar bzhag pa ni 'khrul pa rang
NK034(ngi)006:2230: dag tu 'gro ba'i dgos pa yin no snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2231: bsgyur bas ni nyon mongs pa ngos zin pa'i dgos
NK034(ngi)006:2232: pa yin no bsgom pa'i man ngag thams cad du
NK034(ngi)006:2233: ni sems sbyong ba dang rig pa brtan par bya
NK034(ngi)006:2234: ba las 'gro sa med do sems sbyangs pas ni
NK034(ngi)006:2235: sems kyi byung tshor mi skye ba'i dgos pa yod
NK034(ngi)006:2236: pa yin no rig pa brtan pas ni snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2237: la rang byan tshud par bya ba'i dgos pa yod
NK034(ngi)006:2238: pa yin no lta ba'i man ngag tu ni khregs
NK034(ngi)006:2239: chod dang thod rgal las 'gro sa med do khregs
NK034(ngi)006:2240: chod ni cig car ba'i don yin te 'bad pa
NK034(ngi)006:2241: med par rang gis rang grol bar bstan pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:2242: te 'di ni sngon sbyangs pa'i gang zag gi spyod
NK034(ngi)006:2243: yul yin gyi da lta ni nyams su len dgos
NK034(ngi)006:2244: so nyams su ma blangs na snang ba 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)006:2245: la rig pa mngon du mi phyin rig pa mngon
NK034(ngi)006:2246: du ma phyin na rig pa tshad la mi phebs
NK034(ngi)006:2247: rig pa nyid tshad la ma phab na chos nyid
NK034(ngi)006:2248: zad sar mi skyol chos nyid zad sar ma skyol
NK034(ngi)006:2249: na phung po zag med du sangs mi rgya zag
NK034(ngi)006:2250: med kyi phung po lhag med du sangs ma rgyas
NK034(ngi)006:2251: na theg pa thun mong pa rnams dang khyad par
NK034(ngi)006:2252: ci yang mi rnyed pas de'i gnad kyis nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:2253: len dgos 'di ltar bstan pa 'di ni gang zag
NK034(ngi)006:2254: le lo can rnams la 'bad mi dgos par grol
NK034(ngi)006:2255: ba yod do byas nas 'jug par bya ba'i phyir
NK034(ngi)006:2256: gsungs pa yin gyis 'bras bu gcig car rang du
NK034(ngi)006:2257: min no de'i phyir na khregs chod du bstan pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2258: dgos pa ni 'di ltar don du bstan pa la
NK034(ngi)006:2259: nyams su myong ba'i shes pa ni ga la srid
NK034(ngi)006:2260: 'di mi srid pas des na gzod kyis 'di la
NK034(ngi)006:2261: nyams su myong bas 'dir 'jug pa'i don du gsungs
NK034(ngi)006:2262: pa'o thod rgal ni rim gyis rig pa'i ye shes
NK034(ngi)006:2263: rnal 'byor pas nyams su myong zhing yid dpyod ni
NK034(ngi)006:2264: ma yin te dbang po'i rnam shes rnams kyi spyod
NK034(ngi)006:2265: yul du mthong bas so de yang thod rgal zhes
NK034(ngi)006:2266: bya ba ni 'di nyid mngon sum mthong bas thod
NK034(ngi)006:2267: rgal zhes bstan pa'o de'i phyir na gzhan dag gis
NK034(ngi)006:2268: ni lta ba'i don ngo shes pa ni shes rab
NK034(ngi)006:2269: mngon sum du yod cing snang ba yin gyis dbang
NK034(ngi)006:2270: po la ni gal srid ces ston pa yin te
NK034(ngi)006:2271: 'dir lta ba'i don de la lta ba'i mthar thug
NK034(ngi)006:2272: pa mig gis lta ba yin te lta ba zhes
NK034(ngi)006:2273: bya thig le'i skor ni thig le ni stong pa
NK034(ngi)006:2274: chos kyi dbyings so nyag cig ni cha phra ste
NK034(ngi)006:2275: gab pa'o zhes gsungs te thig le'i don te gtan
NK034(ngi)006:2276: la phab nas gab cing bsgribs te ming bstan yang
NK034(ngi)006:2277: ngo sprod ma bstan te 'di ltar lta ba'i mig
NK034(ngi)006:2278: med do 'dir lta ba'i don de la dbang po'i
NK034(ngi)006:2279: mngon sum du med na da res phung po khams
NK034(ngi)006:2280: dang skye mched rnams zad par byed cing snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2281: 'di zad par byed cing nyon mongs pa rnams zad
NK034(ngi)006:2282: par byed pa'i don du bstan pa yin pas shes
NK034(ngi)006:2283: rab kyis ni 'di dag zad par mi nus pa
NK034(ngi)006:2284: mngon du gsal 'di dag ma zad par sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)006:2285: yi zhe na rigs drug spyi dang khyad par cung
NK034(ngi)006:2286: zad kyang mi rnyed do de'i phyir na snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2287: mngon sum pa 'di rig pa mngon sum gyis zad
NK034(ngi)006:2288: par ma byas na shes rab kyis ni zad par
NK034(ngi)006:2289: nus pa ga la srid 'di ltar 'dod pa ni
NK034(ngi)006:2290: yid dpyod kyi shes pa ste 'di ni yang dag
NK034(ngi)006:2291: pa ma yin no de'i phyir thod rgal gyi lta
NK034(ngi)006:2292: bas rig pa ye shes rim gyis rtogs par byas
NK034(ngi)006:2293: nas 'di ltar snang ba rang zad du gtong bas
NK034(ngi)006:2294: ni lus ngag gi spyod pas 'khor 'das ru shan
NK034(ngi)006:2295: 'byed pa la sogs pa'i man ngag rnams kyis rim
NK034(ngi)006:2296: gyis nyams su myong ba dang mthong rtags kyi rim
NK034(ngi)006:2297: pa 'dii ltar gtan la phab nas phung po lhag
NK034(ngi)006:2298: med du sangs rgyas pa'o phung po lhag med ces
NK034(ngi)006:2299: bya ba'i go ba ni 'di ltar nyams su blangs
NK034(ngi)006:2300: pas 'byung ba lnga rang sar dengs nas lus kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2301: 'dzin pa rang 'gags te sha khrag rang dgar mi
NK034(ngi)006:2302: snang phyi'i 'byung ba lnga 'gags pas sa rdo'i snang
NK034(ngi)006:2303: ba rags pa mi snang ba las lhag ma med
NK034(ngi)006:2304: pa'o sha khrag rang ga ma'i gzugs dang bcas te
NK034(ngi)006:2305: song zhing 'gro ba'i sa yod pa ma yin no
NK034(ngi)006:2306: 'bras bu'i man ngag ni 'bras bu'i tshad can dang
NK034(ngi)006:2307: tshad med gnyis las 'gro sa med do tshad can
NK034(ngi)006:2308: ji ltar bsgoms shing grub pa'i mtha' 'bras bu sku
NK034(ngi)006:2309: gsum du 'dod pa ste de yang chos sku'i skabs
NK034(ngi)006:2310: su mthar thug gi 'bras bur 'dod de 'di ni
NK034(ngi)006:2311: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan 'char tshul lam rtsal gyis
NK034(ngi)006:2312: sangs rgya bar 'dod pa yin no 'di ltar 'bras
NK034(ngi)006:2313: bur 'dod pa ni snang ba la stong par khas
NK034(ngi)006:2314: blangs nas 'bras bu la mtshan mar 'dod pa yin
NK034(ngi)006:2315: no sku yod phan chad lus yod pas 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)006:2316: ma yin no tshad med ni 'di ltar nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:2317: blangs pas sku gsum gyi snang ba 'di nyid la
NK034(ngi)006:2318: gtan la phab nas chos nyid zad pa'i sa la
NK034(ngi)006:2319: bskyal bas lus su 'dzin pa'i zhen pa las grol
NK034(ngi)006:2320: ba'i dus na 'di ltar rang gi rna ba la'ang
NK034(ngi)006:2321: mi snang bas sku gsum gyi zhen pa rang sar
NK034(ngi)006:2322: dag ste mthar thug la chos kyi sku'i snang ba
NK034(ngi)006:2323: 'char ba'am de nyid du 'dzin pa'am snang ba'i mngon
NK034(ngi)006:2324: zhen rang log pa ni lus med ces chos kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2325: sku'i zhen pa las blo ldog lus te zhes 'byung
NK034(ngi)006:2326: ste sprul sku'i zhen pa las ldog lus kyi mchog
NK034(ngi)006:2327: ces longs sku'i zhen pa las log pas lus kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2328: mtha' rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa zhes bya ste lus
NK034(ngi)006:2329: kyi zhen pa thams cad dang rang bral ba'o lta
NK034(ngi)006:2330: sgom spyod pa 'bras bu'i gnad yig yang 'byed +thii
NK034(ngi)006:2331: yid ches mi 'gyur ba don gyi lha la phyag
NK034(ngi)006:2332: 'tshal lo +aa yang 'byed gsal ba'i sgron me rig
NK034(ngi)006:2333: pa'i rgyab rten gyi gnad yig chen po la snang
NK034(ngi)006:2334: ba la rig pa nyid mngon sum du snang ba'i
NK034(ngi)006:2335: thabs ni thog lta bu'i man ngag yin te 'di
NK034(ngi)006:2336: ni rags pa'i 'byung bas ma bsgribs par thogs pa
NK034(ngi)006:2337: med par snang ba'i tshe dbyings kyi sgron ma la
NK034(ngi)006:2338: yid ches ma skyes na 'bras bu gtan brlag nas
NK034(ngi)006:2339: sangs rgya ba re ba med do de'i phyir na
NK034(ngi)006:2340: rig pa thogs pa med pa thog lta bu'i don
NK034(ngi)006:2341: gyi man ngag gis phyir mi ldog par bya ba
NK034(ngi)006:2342: ni mchog tu gces so de ltar phyir mi ldog
NK034(ngi)006:2343: par byas nas dbyings dang rig pa rang gi ngo
NK034(ngi)006:2344: bor mi 'gyur bar bya ba ni mi 'gyur gzer
NK034(ngi)006:2345: lta bu'i man ngag gis sa'i 'char sgo la yid
NK034(ngi)006:2346: ches par bya ste rang gi mig gis de bzhin
NK034(ngi)006:2347: nyid la yid ma ches na mthong byed don gyi
NK034(ngi)006:2348: lta ba gtan brlag ste 'khrul pa'i snang ba chod
NK034(ngi)006:2349: mi srid do 'khrul ba'i snang ba ma chod na
NK034(ngi)006:2350: 'bras bu sangs rgyas la re ba med do de
NK034(ngi)006:2351: ltar rig pa rang gi ngo bo mi 'gyur bar
NK034(ngi)006:2352: byas nas rig pa nyid mkha' la mngon sum du
NK034(ngi)006:2353: bstan pa ni 'phral du bcos pa ma yin te
NK034(ngi)006:2354: ye nas de ltar gnas shing snang ba yin te
NK034(ngi)006:2355: mngon du snang mi srid do snyam pa'i snyem byed
NK034(ngi)006:2356: kyis rten la yid ma ches na rig pa nyid
NK034(ngi)006:2357: ji srid du gtan la phebs par mi 'gyur te
NK034(ngi)006:2358: 'di nyid la ma phebs na 'bras bu sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)006:2359: ba ga la srid pas de'i phyir na skar mda'
NK034(ngi)006:2360: lta bu'i man ngag gis rig pa mkha' la dbyung
NK034(ngi)006:2361: ba rab tu gces so de ltar rig pa man
NK034(ngi)006:2362: ngag gsum la yid ches pas rig pa de nyid
NK034(ngi)006:2363: 'khor ba la mi ldog pa yin de yang rig
NK034(ngi)006:2364: pa rang gi ngo bo la yid ches pa'i stobs
NK034(ngi)006:2365: kyis phyir mi ldog pa ni de'i phyir na rig
NK034(ngi)006:2366: pa phyir mi ldog pa'i man ngag dpag chen gyi
NK034(ngi)006:2367: mda' lta bu'i man ngag gis rig pa rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:2368: ngo bo la yid ches pa rab tu gces so
NK034(ngi)006:2369: des na man ngag 'di dag ni rang gi ngo
NK034(ngi)006:2370: bo rang gis gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir na nyams
NK034(ngi)006:2371: su len pa'i dus na rig pa dang dbyings gnyis
NK034(ngi)006:2372: la gtad sa'i 'ben ma bcas na snang ba mngon
NK034(ngi)006:2373: sum du gtan la mi phebs pas dbyings rig ni
NK034(ngi)006:2374: man ngag bla mas mngon du gtan la 'bebs pa
NK034(ngi)006:2375: gces so de lta bu'i dbyings dang rig pa gnyis
NK034(ngi)006:2376: las dang po pas rang gi smin phrag tu gtad
NK034(ngi)006:2377: pa ni rdeg pa'i dmigs gsal ba'i man ngag ste
NK034(ngi)006:2378: 'di nyid du shes pa ma gtad na dbyings kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2379: snang ba mi zin pas 'dir shes pa gtad pas
NK034(ngi)006:2380: dbyings las ye shes skye'o de ltar bla mas bstan
NK034(ngi)006:2381: pa de la rab tu goms par ma byas na
NK034(ngi)006:2382: rig pa'i rang snang gtan la mi phebs pas rtag
NK034(ngi)006:2383: tu goms pas nyams gong nas gong du 'phel bas
NK034(ngi)006:2384: na rig pa 'phel ba'i sa bon gdab pa zhes
NK034(ngi)006:2385: bya ste snang ba mi 'dra ba 'char ba'i tshe
NK034(ngi)006:2386: rang gi snang ba gcig nas gcig tu tshad la
NK034(ngi)006:2387: ma pheb na rig pa thug pa med pas don
NK034(ngi)006:2388: gcig du skye mi srid pas 'di la goms pa
NK034(ngi)006:2389: ni rab tu gces pa yin no de ltar rang
NK034(ngi)006:2390: gi rig pa de tshad la pheb pas na mi
NK034(ngi)006:2391: 'gyur ba'i lus rnyed par byed pas snang ba'i 'phel
NK034(ngi)006:2392: ba 'ba' zhig la bltas nas byed pas bsam gtan
NK034(ngi)006:2393: gyi lha'i skye gnas las mi grol ba'i phyir na
NK034(ngi)006:2394: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba la ci yang ma
NK034(ngi)006:2395: yin par gtan la ma phab na de nyid du
NK034(ngi)006:2396: 'gyur bas rgya che ba'i nam mkha' la sbar gyis
NK034(ngi)006:2397: bzung ba'i man ngag gis snang ba ci'i ngo bor
NK034(ngi)006:2398: yang grub rgyu med par snang ba ni 'phral du
NK034(ngi)006:2399: song ba ma yin te ye nas de nyid kyi
NK034(ngi)006:2400: ngo bor bzhugs pa'o de'i phyir na sngon du dbyings
NK034(ngi)006:2401: rig gi snang ba ma bstan na nyams su blang
NK034(ngi)006:2402: bya'i don mi shes de nas nyams gong nas gong
NK034(ngi)006:2403: du 'phel ba'i snang bas rig pa'i tshad ma bzung
NK034(ngi)006:2404: na sku gsum du 'dzin pa'i zhen yul 'gag tu
NK034(ngi)006:2405: mi btub pas de la goms par bya de nas
NK034(ngi)006:2406: rig pa tshad la ma phebs na chos sku la
NK034(ngi)006:2407: mthar 'dzin gyi zhen pa ldog tu mi btub pas
NK034(ngi)006:2408: tshad la dbab pa gces tha ma chos nyid zad
NK034(ngi)006:2409: sar ma bskyal na sku gsum rang rgyud du mi
NK034(ngi)006:2410: grol bas na ye nas de ltar bzhugs pa'o +thii
NK034(ngi)006:2411: 'gal ba bsdus pa'i gnad kyi yi ge thun mong
NK034(ngi)006:2412: gi theg pa rnams kyis rtsol sgrub ci byas tshad
NK034(ngi)006:2413: ma rig pa la sogs pa'i nyon mongs par 'gyur
NK034(ngi)006:2414: bas na rang gi lta ba rig pa mngon sum
NK034(ngi)006:2415: gyi man ngag la yid ches rang bzhin gyis skye
NK034(ngi)006:2416: bas de nyid la brtson par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa
NK034(ngi)006:2417: dang nyon mongs pa zhes logs su gdags bya gang
NK034(ngi)006:2418: yang med par yid ches nas rang gi ngo bo
NK034(ngi)006:2419: la rang 'jug pa'i dad pa brtan po sngon du
NK034(ngi)006:2420: skye ba dang man ngag 'di la yid rab tu
NK034(ngi)006:2421: ches pas gzhan la blo mi 'jug pa'i gding thob
NK034(ngi)006:2422: pa'o de'i phyir na grub mtha' mang po'i spros pa
NK034(ngi)006:2423: bcad nas bla ma'i man ngag tshig gsum la blo
NK034(ngi)006:2424: phebs te nyams su len pa la brtson pa dang
NK034(ngi)006:2425: tshig gi spros pa rab chod de rang gi don
NK034(ngi)006:2426: la yid ches skye ba dang rang gi rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2427: gnad gzir bas gnas lugs nyid nyams su myong ba
NK034(ngi)006:2428: dang rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo mthong bas tshig
NK034(ngi)006:2429: ji ltar brjod cing 'dug pa thams cad rang gi
NK034(ngi)006:2430: lta ba'i grogs su ma song ba gang yang med
NK034(ngi)006:2431: pas ye nas rang gi gnas lugs dang 'brel bar
NK034(ngi)006:2432: shes par bya'o +thii gzhan 'dod bsdus pa'i gnad yig
NK034(ngi)006:2433: rdzogs pa chen po la sogs theg pa'i chos rnams
NK034(ngi)006:2434: dang thig le skor gsum gyi lta ba 'di'i don
NK034(ngi)006:2435: la reg pa med pa'i gnad ni dngos po dbang
NK034(ngi)006:2436: po'i spyod yul du yod par ma shes te shes
NK034(ngi)006:2437: rab kyi spyod yul du 'dod pas shes rab kyis
NK034(ngi)006:2438: ni brtags na yang dag par na phung po'i gting
NK034(ngi)006:2439: yang mi rnyed na rig pa ni lta ci smos
NK034(ngi)006:2440: te de'i phyir na 'khor bar 'ching ba'i sgo nas
NK034(ngi)006:2441: mu stegs rtag chad dang theg pa rim dgu'i lta
NK034(ngi)006:2442: ba la khyad par rdul tsam yang med do bka'
NK034(ngi)006:2443: dang bstan bcos gzhung du bkod pa 'di kun thams
NK034(ngi)006:2444: cad ni shes bya'i chos yin gyi nyams su blang
NK034(ngi)006:2445: du btub pa ni rdul tsam yang med do 'di
NK034(ngi)006:2446: dag ni 'di ltar tshig rlabs po che smra ba
NK034(ngi)006:2447: yang yod de gnas lugs la nyams su blang rgyu
NK034(ngi)006:2448: byung na gnas lugs ma yin no zhes sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)006:2449: kyis gsungs pa'i tshig kyang yod de de ni nyams
NK034(ngi)006:2450: su blangs nas rang gi snang ba tshad la phebs
NK034(ngi)006:2451: pa'i dus na yin te gzhan du ni ma yin
NK034(ngi)006:2452: no 'dis ni bdag po ma yin par gzhan gyi
NK034(ngi)006:2453: nor grangs su 'debs pa'i skyes bu dang 'dra ste
NK034(ngi)006:2454: gazhi'am gnas lugs kyi yon tan la 'bras bur 'dod
NK034(ngi)006:2455: pa yin te 'di ni gang zag gzhan gyi yon
NK034(ngi)006:2456: tan la tshig gis brjod kyang de'i yon tan rang
NK034(ngi)006:2457: la gos su mi btub pa dang 'dra'o 'di dag
NK034(ngi)006:2458: rnams ni yid dpyod kyi shes pa las yang dag
NK034(ngi)006:2459: pa'i lta bas zin pa'i cha gang du yang med
NK034(ngi)006:2460: cing snang cha gang du yang ma 'gags pa rig
NK034(ngi)006:2461: pa mngon sum du ma shes pa'i gnad kyis de
NK034(ngi)006:2462: ltar 'gyur ba'o de ltar bsgoms shing bsgrubs pas lus
NK034(ngi)006:2463: ngag gi rtags 'ga' 'byung ba ni sngon du sbyangs
NK034(ngi)006:2464: pa'i bsod nams las 'byung ba yin gyis 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)006:2465: bstan pa las 'byung ba ma yin no lus ngag
NK034(ngi)006:2466: gi rtags ni mu stegs pa la yang 'byung ba
NK034(ngi)006:2467: yin te 'di yang sngon sbyangs pa bar chad pa
NK034(ngi)006:2468: las 'byung ba yin no gal te des sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)006:2469: ba dag byung na tha ma 'bras bu 'di dang
NK034(ngi)006:2470: phrad nas sangs rgya ba yin gzhan gyis de kho
NK034(ngi)006:2471: na ltar ma yin no bdag gis tshig de kun
NK034(ngi)006:2472: 'dod rgyal du bkod pa ma yin no las can
NK034(ngi)006:2473: gcig dang 'phrad par shog +thii rig pa bsdus pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2474: sgron ma'i gnad yig yang 'byed gsang ba'i rgyab yig
NK034(ngi)006:2475: rig pa'i ltos sa nam mkha' stong pa ltos gzhi
NK034(ngi)006:2476: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku chen po ltos
NK034(ngi)006:2477: sa ltos gzhi snang ba rang gi ngo bo la
NK034(ngi)006:2478: grub pa gcig kyang med sems can gyi mtshon tshul
NK034(ngi)006:2479: la gnyis su gtan la ma phab na don nyams
NK034(ngi)006:2480: su mi len te de'i phyir na rdo rje lu
NK034(ngi)006:2481: gu rgyud ni dbugs med pa'i 'gyu ba dang bcas
NK034(ngi)006:2482: pa ste gting du hrig chags pa la nyams su
NK034(ngi)006:2483: sing bag dang bcas pas ngo bo bzung ba dka'
NK034(ngi)006:2484: ba ltar 'dug kyang rang bzhin de la chags pa
NK034(ngi)006:2485: yin te gsal ba rang gis ngo bo la bltas
NK034(ngi)006:2486: na breng chags pas snang ba rgya ma chad pa'i
NK034(ngi)006:2487: rtags yin dngos po 'dug tshul la bltas na thig
NK034(ngi)006:2488: le'i snang ba rang shar te chos nyid spros pa
NK034(ngi)006:2489: dang bral ba'i rtags yin 'dug stangs 'gro 'ong gi
NK034(ngi)006:2490: ngo bo la bltas na 'gyu ba rang sgrin dang
NK034(ngi)006:2491: bcas par snang ste yid dpyod kyi shes rab ma
NK034(ngi)006:2492: yin par gshis la gnas pa'i shes rab gong nas
